\id LUK - Ekajuk New Testament 
\h Luk 
\toc1 Luk 
\toc2 Luk 
\mt2 NWER NYI 
\mt1 LUK 
\c 1  
\s1 Nsoo Teofailus,\f + \fr 1:1 \ft Elt 1:1\f* 
\p  
\v 1 Ane gbalee ebnyon nsol nyi ma lim go egahre ellong, nyi e kpo taame tv go etingitingi.  
\v 2 Bo nyono ana ane ba jolo go mbomannahb, ba nyehne nsol nyio go amahr tong-r, bo ji jolo alokeltum ba Alum Esowo. 
\p  
\v 3 Tib eji me n tob seb nsol nyio kpee kahn nob nob ana jolo go mbomannahb, owo wahng ka n tiri re, nꞌnob re, me n tob nyon nsol nyio go ntooranti ka-a,  
\v 4 eji a lꞌkahn re, nsol nyi bo tib-a no lohko li go etingitingi. 
\s1 Ana bo jele Jon ji nwohngalahb 
\p  
\v 5 Ngare nyi Herod jolo ntul go Judea, nlimajom awohng jolo o, no bo jo lung-e re Sekaraya. Á woomo go ellong abalimajom ba Abija jolo ntubesi abo mahne mahne. Nkal ewe, bo jo lung-e re Elisabet ji lohngo go etꞌtohngo ji Eron.  
\v 6 Bo ane abal abal jolo atingitingi ane go esamahr Esowo, ba jo bum atahm nya Jehova kpee nseenga nseenge.  
\v 7 Bo jelem mmon awohng awohng. Tibre Elisabet jolo ngum a nnenkal. Ngare nyio bobkul ane abal abal. 
\p  
\v 8 Efung abehng Sekaraya jo limi eltum njom alimi go etahk Esowo, tib jolo esennge ji ellong nꞌne.  
\v 9 Ana eljini ni abalimajom jolo no, owo bo kehm-e yehke re á kak agun go insens, jo teebe go ekpꞌkpa Esowo.  
\v 10 Ane baka kpee jolo ga elatahk, jo kak ero ngare nyi insens jo teebe. 
\p  
\v 11 Owo enjel nyi Esowo kehm lohngo ba kpir-e. Enjel nyio yiimi go ejang eboblum bi edi njom jio ji insens jo teebe.  
\v 12 Eji Sekaraya nyehn-e no, ala kehm-e teele, á kehme elfahle.  
\v 13 Owo enjel nyio kehm-e tongo re, “Sekaraya, ka kpe fahl! Esowo ebwuk ero eba. Elisabet nkal ewa bahke jele mmon no nlum ka-a. A bahk-e gungu mbing re Jon.  
\v 14 A bahke bele eyebatahng, fere jo geere. Ane gbalee, eltim bahke yebe bo, ń lꞌjel-e.  
\v 15 Tibre á bahke jolo njꞌjoka nne go esamahr bi Esowo.\f + \fr 1:15 \ft Mat 11:11\f* Á nehm jo wo amahm, a nsol elwoko nyehko nyi kpo lim nne. Bomo ngare nyi á wob nnyehn go ala, Etingi Etohko bahk-e ruru go atahng.  
\v 16 Á bahke feere abon Israel gbalee ba ka Esowo, Ntul abo.\f + \fr 1:16 \ft Mat 3:5-6\f* 
\v 17 Á bahk-e gboko mbang a etohko ji Elaija, a nsahm a nsahm enye,\f + \fr 1:17 \ft Mat 17:11-13\f* eji á lꞌsennge babnde ntim, bo fere jol ana abonse, fere sennge akpuuru ane ntim, bo fere bel elkahne ni atingitingi ane, fere toobo ane bum Esowo.” 
\p  
\v 18 Owo Sekaraya kehm bahbe enjel nyio re, “M bahke limi renan, kehm kahne, joare lohko li go etingitingi? Tibre me n kul, nkal ewame fvfo ebtob kul.” 
\p  
\v 19 Enjel nyio kehm-e faange re, “Me wo li Gebriel ji kpo yiimi go esamahr bi Esowo. Esowo bi tum-m no re me m ba bung a na, fere tiing-a nnoobo etib bia.\f + \fr 1:19 \ft Hib 1:14\f* 
\v 20 A bahke gboko ekamme. A nehm ma kpe bung tete rehng efung bi ejum jia bahke jolo, tib eji a ki taame tv alum enyame nya bahke jolo go etingitingi, ngare nyio lꞌbiingi.” 
\p  
\v 21 Ane ba jo sik Sekaraya jo kpo bo esi sehng, eji á ma laange ano go ekpꞌkpa Esowo.  
\v 22 Eji á lohngo go elatahk, á kpeem jo ma bung a bo. Owo bo kehm soro kahn re, yebnyehn nkpokosi ejum go ekpꞌkpa Esowo. Eji á ki ma jo bung go nnyo, á fere jo bung a bo go abo abo.  
\v 23 Eji afung nya á jo lim eltum go etahk Esowo ma mal, á kehm tahme kehnge. 
\p  
\v 24 Eji ma jol ano, Elisabet nkal ewe kehm sake ela, sa woomo ekpꞌkpa tete nnyahng elon. Á jo bungu re,  
\v 25 “Anv, eji m ma fili Jehova ndon, owo á ma-m kak ebo mbang nyia, eji á lꞌlim-m, n jo lub ane.” 
\s1 Etib bi enjel Gebriel tiingi Meri 
\p  
\v 26 Eji ma kang nnyahng erakera mi Elisabet sa ela, owo Esowo kehm tumu enjel Gebriel tv go ejahbe ajehng ji jolo go Galili, ji bo kpo lung re Nasaret.  
\v 27 Á ko etib ba a bi re á ba tiingi ngbahme anyehng nyi bo jo lung-e re Meri ji bo kala nꞌnoongo a ne. Nne awohng no bo jo lung-e re Josef ji lohng go etꞌtohngo ji ntul a Devid wo lame elbal a ne.\f + \fr 1:27 \ft Mat 1:18\f* 
\p  
\v 28 Enjel nyio kehm ba kpiri Meri, kehm-e tongo re, “M ma-a kak nnyo, wo ji Esowo ma-a fuulu. Jehova li a na.” 
\p  
\v 29 Owo ala kehm sahb tꞌteele Meri, eji á wuku etib bi enjel nyio tiing-e no. Á kehm kehme eltiiri bade ana nnyo akake mio lohngo no. 
\p  
\v 30 Enjel nyio kehm-e tongo re, “Meri, ka kpe fahl! Esowo ma-a fuulu.  
\v 31 A bahke sake ela, jel nnenlum no a bahk-e gungu mbing re Jisos.\f + \fr 1:31 \ft Mat 1:21-23\f* 
\v 32 Á bahke jolo njꞌjoka nne. Bo bahke jo lung-e re Mmon no Esowo bi gbale sehng. Jehova bahk-e jehke go eti etul ji nde Devid.  
\v 33 Á bahke fili abon Jekob go njinanjini. Etul ebe, esꞌkohlo nehm bel.” 
\p  
\v 34 Owo Meri kehm bahbe enjel nyio re, “Jia kehm jolo renan, eji n ki kpi nlum!” 
\p  
\v 35 Enjel nyio kehm-e faange re, “Etingi Etohko bahke jolo a na. Nsahm nyi Esowo bahk-a bulu.\f + \fr 1:35 \ft Mat 1:20\f* Owo bahke wahng ka mbarebara mmon no a bahke jele, bo bahke jo lung-e re Mmon no Esowo.  
\v 36 Nyehn Elisabet, nne a nnahb ewa, ji bo jo lung-e re ngum a nnenkal, yebsa ela bi á bahke jele nnenlum, nnyahng erakera mi a, jol eji á ma kꞌkul o.  
\v 37 Tibre Esowo, ejumjum limm, ji á kil jo ma lim.” 
\p  
\v 38 Owo Meri kehm bungu re, “Me n li nlokeltum no Esowo. Nong, jol ana a bungu no.” 
\p Enjel nyio kehm soro tahm. 
\s1 Ana Meri je song nyehn Elisabet 
\p  
\v 39 Jol gaam kang, Meri kehm toobo ebjing, foomo tahm song rehng go ejahbe ajehng ji jolo go ejang awong nya Judea.  
\v 40 Owo á kehm song yange go etahk Sekaraya, kehm song kak Elisabet nnyo. 
\p  
\v 41 Eji Elisabet wuku nnyo mi Meri kak-e no, mmon no woomo Elisabet go ala kehm nvvdv. Etingi Etohko kehm ruru Elisabet go atahng,  
\v 42 owo á kehm soro kehme elbungu wahre wahre re, “Wo wo, Esowo ma-a fuulu go ellong anebkal. Elfuulu li ka mmon no a bahke jele.  
\v 43 Jen ji wahnge elkohn nkpokosi ejum ana nyia ma lim re nnyehn ntul ewame ba nyehn-m?  
\v 44 Tibre n wuku kan nnyo mi a kak-m no, mmon no wob-m ga ala soro yuudu go eyebatahng.  
\v 45 Eyebatahng li a na, eji a ma taame tv etib bi Jehova tiing-a no. Tibre bahke lohko jol go etingitingi.” 
\s1 Ana Meri jo tehk Esowo 
\p  
\v 46 Owo Meri kehm bungu re, 
\q1 “Eltim ename kpꞌtehke Jehova. 
\q1  
\v 47 Etohko ejame kpꞌgeere kak Esowo, ntꞌtahre ewame, 
\q1  
\v 48 eji á ma-m buumu, me ji li nlokeltum ewe no li reed. 
\q1 Bomo anv asongo ane kpee bahk-m jo lung re, 
\q1 nne no Esowo m-e fuulu.\f + \fr 1:48 \ft Luk 11:27-28\f* 
\q1  
\v 49 Tibre Esowo bi gbale sehng ma-m rod, 
\q1 kpꞌlimi agburu nsol. 
\q1 Mbing enye li saang. 
\q1  
\v 50 Ndon enye li ka ane ba kp-e fahle, 
\q1 jol afi bo jini ngare anyi.\f + \fr 1:50 \ft Elt 10:34-45\f* 
\q1  
\v 51 Á tanne ebo ebe, fere tib nsahm enye, kam aneb elgeere raade, 
\q1 a ntir a ntir ebo. 
\q1  
\v 52 Á kpo radde ajꞌjok atul go bo a nti etul, 
\q1 fere mehl ane ba li rede rede wahre. 
\q1  
\v 53 Ane ba njal ma yam bo, 
\q1 á kpo ka bo anoobo nsol, 
\q1 bo li wohngo, 
\q1 fere yake afang ane, bo song abo abo. 
\q1  
\v 54 Esowo ebkak Israel, nlokeltum ewe, ebo, 
\q1 eji á ma buumu ndon enye, 
\q1  
\v 55 nyi li go njinanjini 
\q1 ana á bungu tong babnso ejahre, 
\q1 fere tong Ebraham, 
\q1 a abon ebe.” 
\p  
\v 56 Meri kange ejum nnyahng era a Elisabet, kehm feere kehnge. 
\s1 Ana bo jele Jon ji nwohngalahb 
\p  
\v 57 Ngare kehm rehnge nyi Elisabet yahke jel. Á kehm jele nnenlum.  
\v 58 Eji aneb nkontahk ebe, a ane ebe wuku ana Jehova m-e tib egburu ndon enye, bo kehm-e tobo elgeere. 
\p  
\v 59 Eji mmon ma kang nfung enehkeni, bo kehm tahme re bo song yehk-e nrur. Owo bo kehm-e gungu mbing nyi nde re Sekaraya. 
\p  
\v 60 Nnyehn kehm tene re, “Eꞌee, bo bahk-e jo lung re Jon.”\f + \fr 1:60 \ft Luk 1:13\f* 
\p  
\v 61 Bo kehm-e faange re, “Nne ewa awohng awohng limm, no kpi mbing nyio!” 
\p  
\v 62 Bo kehm bahbe nde go abo abo re, “Elkohn mbing anyi a bahke gungu mmon ewa?”  
\v 63 Sekaraya kehm bahbe re, bo ka-e nwer. 
\p Á kehm koko nyon re, “Mbing enye, bo bahke jo lung-e re Jon.” Ane kpee kehm kpoko bo esi. 
\p  
\v 64 Sekaraya kehm soro kpe kehme elbungu, fere jo tehk Esowo. 
\p  
\v 65 Kpee ane ba lene kohlo o kehm kehme elfahle. Eka jio kehm yeere go ejang bi ajahbe kpee nya jolo go awong nya Judea.  
\v 66 Ane kpee ba wuku no, kehm rodo kak go bo a ntim, fere jo bahb re, “Anv, mmon noa bahke jolo elkohn nne awo?” Tibre bo nyehne ana nsahm nyi Esowo jolo a ne. 
\s1 Ana Sekaraya nyehne amahr 
\p  
\v 67 Owo Etingi Etohko kehm ba rur Sekaraya, nde Jon, á kehme amahr nyehn re, 
\q1  
\v 68 “Nong, wahr tehken Esowo bi Israel, bi li Ntul ewahre. 
\q1 Yebba re á ba kak ane ebe ebo, 
\q1 fere fak bo yake. 
\q1  
\v 69 Á ma-r ka ntꞌtahre no kpi nsahm, no lohng go etꞌtohngo ji Devid, nlokeltum ewe. 
\q1  
\v 70 Ano wo Esowo bungu sehng go nnyo mi abarabare anyehnamahr ba jolo mahne mahne. 
\q1  
\v 71 Á tongo re, á bahk-r tahre yehke go abo nya anebekv ebahre, fere yehk-r go abo nya ane kpee ba ma-r ko ekv, 
\q1  
\v 72 fere tib babnso ejahre ndon enye, 
\q1 tob buumu mbarebare enyam ebe bi á nyame no, 
\q1  
\v 73 eji á tiri no, fere tong Ebraham, nso ejahre re, 
\q1  
\v 74-75 á bahk-r yehke go abo nya anebekv ebahre, 
\q1 eji e lꞌjol ejahre ejahre ka ye ye, fere li eno go ege esamahr,\f + \fr 1:74-75 \ft Rom 4:16\f* jo lok-e,\f + \fr 1:74-75 \ft 2 Kor 5:15\f* 
\q1 kꞌfahl afung kpee nya e li go elkpin.\f + \fr 1:74-75 \ft 1 Jon 4:18\f* 
\q1  
\v 76 Mmon ewame, bo bahk-a jo lung re, nnyehnamahr no Esowo bi gbale sehng. 
\q1 Tibre a bahke gboko Ntul mbang, song tuungu mbang enye bum-e,\f + \fr 1:76 \ft Mat 3:3\f* 
\q1  
\v 77 fere tong ane ebe re bo bahke bele eltahre, 
\q1 tib eji Esowo bahke tahme ka bo go bo abiafem. 
\q1  
\v 78 Tibre Esowo ebahre kpi egburu ndon nyi bahke lohngo go ero. 
\q1 Ellohngo ni bahke lohngo bahke jolo ana njul kpꞌyake tub-r, 
\q1  
\v 79 eji lꞌka ane ba jehk go ejannge ellennge, a ane ba nong go emel elkv, 
\q1 fere jo tib-r mbang nyi elkoono.” 
\p  
\v 80 Mmon noo kehm gbale, fere tahne go etohko. Á jolo go elka emahng tete efung bi á lohngo gbuul, Israel kehm-e nyehne.\f + \fr 1:80 \ft Mat 3:1\f* 
\c 2  
\s1 Ana bo jele Jisos 
\r (Mat 1:18-25) 
\p  
\v 1 Ngare nyio nyi ntul Agostos kehm jehke ntahm re, bo fange njini kpee, kak abing ebo go nwer.  
\v 2 Eji bo gbo mbang fange ane, Sirinus wo jolo ntubesi go Siria. 
\p  
\v 3 Nne awohng awohng kehm tahme go ege ejahbe re bo kak-e mbing go nwer.  
\v 4 Josef ji lene go Nasaret nyi Galili kehm tob tahm, song rehng go Betlehem ji Judea, ejahbe jio ji bo jele ntul a Devid. Tibre Josef lohng go etꞌtohngo ji Devid.  
\v 5 Á je ona re bo kak mbing enye go nwer, a Meri ji á tongo re á bahk-e koko, ye ji jolo ela.\f + \fr 2:5 \ft Luk 1:27\f* 
\p  
\v 6 Eji bo jolo o Betlehem, ngare kehm biingi nyi Meri yahke ba eljele.  
\v 7 Owo á kehm jele ngbokambang a mmon ewe no nlum, kpenng-e abomo, fere rod-e, bum go ejum ji bo jo kak efong nsol alehke. Tibre eyake jolem go ekpꞌkpa elkang ka bo. 
\s1 Ana babenjel song kpiri abaabebul 
\p  
\v 8 Abaabebul jolo ejang ejahbe jio, ba jo kang go emahng, jo baabe ebul ebo atv.  
\v 9 Enjel nyi Esowo kehm lohngo ba kpiri bo. Ellub ni Esowo kehm yake ana njul tub bo. Bo kehm kehme elfahle tete. 
\p  
\v 10 Owo enjel nyio kehm tongo bo re, “Kana kpe fahl! Tibre n ko nnoobo etib ba a bi, bi kpi egburu eyebatahng ka ane kpee.  
\v 11 Tibre lela bobjel ntꞌtahre ka-n go ejahbe ji Devid, no li Kraist ji Ntul.  
\v 12 A wo li elliingi ka-n. Ḿ bahke nyehne mmon elbili no bo m-e kpennge abomo, á nong go ejum ji bo kpo kak efong nsol alehke.” 
\p  
\v 13 Ellong enjel nyi ejahbetul Esowo gbalee kehm soro lohng ba kpiri enjel nyio, jo tehk Esowo re,  
\v 14 “Ellub jol a Esowo go ero. Elkoono jol a ane go njini, ba Esowo li a bo yebe yebe.” 
\p  
\v 15 Eji babenjel ma feere ebo fi go ejahbetul Esowo, abaabebul kehm bungu atemtem re, “Nong, wahr tahmen go Betlehem, song nyehnen ejum ji ma jol, ji Jehova ma-r tong.” 
\p  
\v 16 Owo bo kehm soro tahm elwaare, song nyehn Meri, a Josef, fere nyehn mmon nong go ejum ji bo kpo kak efong nsol alehke.  
\v 17 Bo nyehne kan ano me, bo kehm tahme, jo yannge, jo tooro tong ane ana enjel tongo bo bada mmon noo.  
\v 18 Ane kpee ba wuku ana abaabebul tongo bo, kehm kpoko bo esi. 
\p  
\v 19 Meri kehm kuuru nsol nyio kpee go ege eltim, fere jo tir bade.  
\v 20 Abaabebul bao kehm feere, jo ka Esowo ellub, fere jo tehk-e mbang mbang go nsol kpee nyi bo ma nyehn, fere wꞌwuk. Jolo na jol jang jang ana enjel tongo bo. 
\s1 Ana bo gungu Jisos mbing 
\p  
\v 21 Eji ma kang nfung enehkeni, nyi bo bahke mmon noo nrur yehke, owo bo kehm-e gungu mbing re Jisos, nyꞌnehm o nyi enjel tibi Meri, á kehm sake ela ebe.\f + \fr 2:21 \ft Luk 1:31\f* 
\s1 Ana bo ko Jisos song rehng a ne go etahk Esowo 
\p  
\v 22 Eji ngare biingi no nyi Meri bahke limi kpee, eji á lꞌkpe jol saang ana ntahm nyi Moses bungu no, owo Josef abola Meri kehm rodo mmon noo, tahm a ne go Jeusalem re bo song rod-e kak Jehova go ebo.  
\v 23 Ana wo bo nyono go ntahm nyi Jehova re, “Ngbokambang a mmon no nlum awohng awohng no lꞌjini, á bahke jolo ka Jehova.” 
\p  
\v 24 Bo kehm limi njom ana ntahm Esowo bungu no re, “Ane bao bahke kake etomtom ebbal, tohko jol ano mbehl ebal.”\f + \fr 2:24 \ft Gal 4:4\f* 
\p  
\v 25 Nne jolo go Jeusalem, no bo jo lung-e re Simeon. Á jolo nnooba nne no jo fahl Esowo, fere jo sik nkakeltim no bahke ba kak Israel eltim.\f + \fr 2:25 \ft Mak 15:43\f* Etingi Etohko jolo a ne.  
\v 26 Tibre Etingi Etohko lennge tong-e re, á nehm tiki waka kpo tete á nyehn Mesaya nyi Jehova bahke tumu. 
\p  
\v 27 Etohko ji Esowo kehm-e yehke re á je go etahk Esowo. Eji Josef, a Meri, bo ko Jisos, mmon abo, song yange a ne go etahk Esowo re bo song lim-e ana ntahm bungu no,  
\v 28 owo Simeon kehm taare mmon, fili go ebo, fere jo tehk Esowo re, 
\q1  
\v 29 “Ntul, woblim enyam eba, 
\q1 anv, nong, nlokeltum ewa kehm yake njini nyia abo, song go eyebatahng, 
\q1  
\v 30 tibre amahr enyame ebnyehn eltahre ena, 
\q1  
\v 31 ni a ma toobo bum go esamahr ane kpee. 
\q1  
\v 32 Eltahre nia li ellennge ni bahke wahnge ane baka baka nyehn mbang enya, 
\q1 ni bahke jolo ellub ni Israel, ane eba.” 
\q1  
\v 33 Eji nde, a nnyehn wuku ana Simeon bungu bada mmon noo, 
\q1 kehm kpoko bo esi. 
\p  
\v 34 Simeon kehm biri elfuulu ni Esowo tv bo, kehm tongo Meri nnyehn re, “Mmon noa, Esowo bi m-e yehke. Ye wo bahke limi ane gbalee go Israel gbo, fere lim ane gbalee mehl yiimi.\f + \fr 2:34 \ft 2 Kor 2:15-16; Luk 23:39-43\f* Ye wo li elliingi ni Esowo ma tib, ni ane bahke jo bung ebi bade,\f + \fr 2:34 \ft Jon 7:12\f* 
\v 35 eji ntir atahng nyi ane gbalee lꞌjol gbuul.\f + \fr 2:35 \ft Hib 4:12-13\f* Wofono antahng eltim ena bahke jolo, are bo jahm-a ekahngkahng.” 
\p  
\v 36 Nnenkal awohng tob jolo o, no bo jo lung-e re Ana. Á jolo nnyehnamahr. Nde, bo jo lung-e re Fanuel ji lohng go etꞌtohngo ji Aser. Ana sahb kꞌkul. Eji nlum ewe ko-e no, á ji elbal nnya esehma,  
\v 37 nlum ewe kehm-e kpoko sa, á fere jol nkalebun. Ngare nyia a, yebkang nnya atahl ani a nnya ani. Á joom tiki lohng go etahk Esowo, á jo kake Esowo, jo bade elne njal, fere jo kak ero atv a njul.  
\v 38 Á kehm soro ba ngare nyꞌnehm o, ba kehme Esowo tehk, fere jo bung tong ane bao bada mmon noo, bao ba ji, jo sik elforo ni Jeusalem bahke foro. 
\s1 Ana bo feere kehnge go Nasaret 
\p  
\v 39 Eji bo ma lim ejum ajehng ajehng mal ana ntahm nyi Jehova bungu no, owo bo kehm feere kehnge go Nasaret, ejahbe ebo ji li go Galili.  
\v 40 Mmon noo kehm gbale, fere tahne. Á gbale go elkahne. Elfuulu ni Esowo jolo a ne. 
\s1 Ana Jisos jolo go etahk Esowo ngare nyi á jolo mmonse 
\p  
\v 41 Elya anehng anehng nde Jisos, a nnyehn jo je elkak Pasova go Jeusalem.  
\v 42 Eji Jisos ma kang ewubu a nnya ebal, bo kehm kpe je go Jeusalem ana bo jo kono eljeke elkak nio. 
\p  
\v 43 Eji afung elkak nio ma mal, owo bo kehm feere kehnge. Jisos sa go Jeusalem. Nde, a nnyehn kahnem.  
\v 44 Bo jo tiri re, Jisos wob go ellong ane ba kpꞌkehnge. Eji bo ma jen efung kohro kohro, owo bo kehm-e kehme elsebe go ellong abonanyehn ebo, a atem ebo.  
\v 45 Eji bo ki-e nyehn, bo kehm feere go Jeusalem, song seb-e gona. 
\p  
\v 46 Eji ma kang nfung era, owo bo kehm song nyehn-e go etahk Esowo, á jehk no a atꞌtibi kpꞌwuungu atung, fere jo bahb bo abahbe.  
\v 47 Ane kpee ba wuk-e no, kehm jo kpo bo esi tib go ege elkahne, a afaange nya á jo faange bo.  
\v 48 Nde, a nnyehn, kpo bo esi sehng, eji bo nyehn-e no. Owo nnyehn kehm-e tongo re, “Mmon ewame, jen ji wahnge a kehm limi ejum ana jia? Nso, a me, e ma-a seb na seb seb seb.” 
\p  
\v 49 Owo á kehm faange bo re, “Jen ji wahnge ń jo seb-m? Ń nehme kahn re, m bahke tiki lim eltum ni Nsooa?”\f + \fr 2:49 \ft Jon 2:3-4; Mak 3:31-35\f* 
\p  
\v 50 Bo kahnem esꞌsi ejum ji á jo bꞌbung tong bo. 
\p  
\v 51 Owo Jisos kehm tahme toono bo, bo feere kehnge go Nasaret, á song woomo bo go elwo. Nnyehn kuuru nsol nyio kpee go ege eltim.  
\v 52 Jisos kehm gbale go elkahne, fere gbal agbal nya ngubjing. Elkoro ni á jo kor Esowo, fere jo kor ane jo kpe gbal na. 
\c 3  
\s1 Ana Jon ji nwohngalahb jo bung alum Esowo 
\r (Mat 3:1-12; Mak 1:1-8; Jon 1:19-28) 
\p  
\v 1 Eji ma kang nnya elku nyi Taibirius jolo ntul a Rom, ngare nyio nyi Pontus Pailet jolo ntubesi ejahbe go Judea, Herod jo fili Galili, Filip mmonannyehn jo fili Iturea, fere jo fili Trakonitis, Lisanias jo fili Abilene.  
\v 2 Annas abola Kayafas jolo atubesi abalimajom. 
\p Ngare nyio nyi ellum Esowo song kpiri Jon ji jolo mmon a Sekaraya go elka emahng.  
\v 3 Jon kehm tahme, jo yannge go ajahbe nya li kohlo Jodan, jo bung alum Esowo re, “Yaangen mbang enyahne, wahn bel ewohngalahb, Esowo bahke tahme ka-n go egahne abiafem.”  
\v 4 Ana nnyehnamahr Aisaya nyono kak go nwer re, 
\q1 “Nne noa, kpꞌrabe go elka emahng re, 
\q1 ‘Tuungen mbang nyi Ntul bum-e! 
\q1 Limen mbang tꞌtor nyi á bahke sehnge. 
\q1  
\v 5 Bo bahke kake ndi go edamme ajehng ajehng, fere jol bale bale, 
\q1 fere rene ewong ajehng ajehng gooro, fere jol bale bale.\f + \fr 3:5 \ft Mat 23:12\f* 
\q1 Ejum ji lꞌgalle, bo bahke limi, fere tor. 
\q1 Abang nya li akpuku akpuku, bo bahke fere gooro, jol gele gele. 
\q1  
\v 6 Nne awohng awohng bahke nyehne eltahre ni Esowo.’ ” 
\p  
\v 7 Ellong ane gbalee jo lꞌlohng, je goji Jon re á wohngo bo alahb. Jon kehm bungu tong bo re, “Wahn enyo bia,” nne awo tong-n re ḿ bahke foro go erakatahng ji Esowo ji kpꞌbake?  
\v 8 Jo limen eljini ni bahke jo tib re, wahn ebyaange mbang enyahne. Kana bom elbungu atemtem re, ‘Ebraham wo li nso ejahre.’ Tibre n kp-n tongo re, Esowo bahke ma ko atal nyaa, lim abon ka Ebraham.\f + \fr 3:8 \ft Jon 8:33,39\f* 
\p  
\v 9 “Bobtoobo elfuk bum, ni bo bahke kiimi alohk nti. Eti ajehng ajehng ji tohko kab akab nya nno, bo bahke gbahke tub, rod kak agun.” 
\p  
\v 10 Owo ane bao kehm-e bahbe re, “Anv, ejum aji e bahke limi me?”  
\v 11 Á kehm faange bo re, “Nne no lꞌbel nsubu ebal, nong, á yehke anyehng, ka nne no ki kpi. Nne no lꞌbel nsol alehke, nong, á tob lim ano.” 
\p  
\v 12 Abakokatak kehm tob ba re bo ba bel ewohngalahb. Owo bo kehm-e bahbe re, “Ntꞌtibi, ejum aji e bahke limi?” 
\p  
\v 13 Jon kehm faange bo re, “Kana kpe jo ko akpohko etak sehnge ana bo tong-n re wahn jo ko.” 
\p  
\v 14 Egom nsoja nyindiki kehm-e tob bahb re, “Wahr bahke limi renan?” 
\p Á kehm faange bo re, “Kana jo lim nne awohng awohng ejum go eko! Kana jo ka nne ebi mbol mbol! Nong, ana bo kp-n kpiki jo gbal-n.” 
\p  
\v 15 Owo ane kehm kehme ekpu kunu, fere jo tir go bo a ntim bada Jon re, fundiki ye Mesaya wo.\f + \fr 3:15 \ft Jon 1:19-28\f* 
\p  
\v 16 Owo Jon kehm bungu tong bo ane kpee re, “N kp-n wohngo alahb maka maka. Nne no kpꞌbake gbale sehnge me. Jol me n tohkem fꞌfuumu re me n fannge alehke akpaketa enye. Ye wo bahk-n wohngo alahb go Etingi Etohko, a agun.  
\v 17 Á fili edꞌda go ebo, kpꞌfebe arasi enye. Á bahke kpuku arasi enye, song kak go ege ekpꞌkpa, fere jahm awal go agun nya lꞌkꞌtiki lahme elahmelahme.” 
\p  
\v 18 Nsol nyehko kpe jol tvv, nyi Jon kpe jo rehke bo, eji á jo tiingi ane bao nnoobo etib. 
\p  
\v 19 Á tob ka ntul a Herod ebi, tib eji á taare Herodias, nkal a Filip mmonannyehn, kpe lim abi nsol nyako budu.\f + \fr 3:19 \ft Mak 6:17-18\f* 
\v 20 Herod kpe lim ebi jehko kpele, eji á bobo Jon kak ngbekobo. 
\s1 Ana Jisos bele ewohngalahb 
\r (Mat 3:13-17; Mak 1:9-11) 
\p  
\v 21 Eji ane bao kpee ma bel ewohngalahb, Jisos kehm tob bel ewohngalahb. Eji á jo kak ero, ejahbetul kehm lennge.  
\v 22 Etingi Etohko kehm badde go elfoongo ni ebbehl, ba jol a ne. Bo kehm wuku ellum go ejahbetul Esowo re, “Wo wo li akor-m mmon ewame, no kpo kor-m sꞌsehng.”\f + \fr 3:22 \ft Luk 9:35\f* 
\s1 Nwer nyi etꞌtohngo ji Jisos lohngo no 
\r (Mat 1:1-17) 
\p  
\v 23 Ngare nyio Jisos ebkang ejum eltahl a nnya ewubu. Ane jo tiri re, á jolo mmon a Josef,\f + \fr 3:23 \ft Luk 4:22\f* ji jolo mmon a Heli.  
\v 24 Heli jolo mmon a Matat. Matat jol mmon a Livai. Livai jol mmon a Melki. Melki jol mmon a Jannai. Jannai jol mmon a Josef.  
\v 25 Josef jol mmon a Matatias. Matatias jol mmon no Amos. Amos jol mmon a Nahum. Nahum jol mmon no Esli. Esli jol mmon a Naggai.  
\v 26 Naggai jol mmon a Maat. Maat jol mmon a Matatias. Matatias jol mmon a Semein. Semein jol mmon a Josek. Josek jol mmon a Joda.  
\v 27 Joda jol mmon a Joanan. Joanan jol mmon a Resa. Resa jol mmon a Serubabel. Serubabel jol mmon a Sealtiel. Sealtiel jol mmon a Neri.  
\v 28 Neri jol mmon a Melki. Melki jol mmon no Addi. Addi jol mmon a Kosam. Kosam jol mmon no Elmadam. Elmadam jol mmon no Er.  
\v 29 Er jol mmon a Josua. Josua jol mmon no Eliesa. Eliesa jol mmon a Jorim. Jorim jol mmon a Matat. Matat jol mmon a Livai.  
\v 30 Livai jol mmon a Simeon. Simeon jol mmon a Juda. Juda jol mmon a Josef. Josef jol mmon a Jonam. Jonam jol mmon no Eliakim.  
\v 31 Eliakim jol mmon a Melea. Melea jol mmon a Menna. Menna jol mmon a Matata. Matata jol mmon a Natan. Natan jol mmon a Devid.  
\v 32 Devid jol mmon a Jesi. Jesi jol mmon Obed. Obed jol mmon a Boas. Boas jol mmon a Sela. Sela jol mmon a Nason.  
\v 33 Nason jol mmon no Aminadab. Aminadab jol mmon no Admin. Admin jol mmon no Arni. Arni jol mmon a Hesron. Hesron jol mmon a Peres. Peres jol mmon a Juda.  
\v 34 Juda jol mmon a Jekob. Jekob jol mmon no Aisik. Aisik jol mmon no Ebraham. Ebraham jol mmon a Tera. Tera jol mmon a Nahor.  
\v 35 Nahor jol mmon a Serug. Serug jol mmon a Reu. Reu jol mmon a Peleg. Peleg jol mmon no Eber. Eber jol mmon a Sela.  
\v 36 Sela jol mmon a Kainan. Kainan jol mmon Arfasad. Arfasad jol mmon a Sem. Sem jol mmon a Noa. Noa jol mmon a Lamek.  
\v 37 Lamek jol mmon a Metusala. Metusala jol mmon no Enohk. Enohk jol mmon a Jared. Jared jol mmon no Mahalalel. Mahalalel jol mmon a Kainan.  
\v 38 Kainan jol mmon no Enos. Enos jol mmon a Set. Set jol mmon no Adam. Adam jol mmon Esowo. 
\c 4  
\s1 Ana nnehm gare Jisos 
\r (Mat 4:1-11; Mak 1:12-13) 
\p  
\v 1 Eji Jisos lohngo go Jodan, jo kehnge, Etingi Etohko rur-e go ege atahng. Etingi Etohko kehm-e rodo tahm a ne go elka emahng.  
\v 2 Owo nnehm gar-e no nfung atahl abal. Afung nyao kpee á tikem li ejumjum. Eji afung nyao ma biingi, njal kehm-e yame. 
\p  
\v 3 Owo nnehm kehm-e tongo re, “A lꞌjol Mmon Esowo, tong eltal nia siingi ebred.” 
\p  
\v 4 Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Nwer Esowo bungu re, ‘Abred nya nya sang wahnge nne kpo kpin. Á kpo tob bel elkpin go ellum Esowo anehng anehng.’ ”\f + \fr 4:4 \ft Jon 6:26-27\f* 
\p  
\v 5 Nnehm kehm-e rodo tahm a ne go nwahrewahre ewong, ko mmongare ana no nne bahke jehbe akpakamahr, tib-e ajahbe nya li go njini kpee,  
\v 6 kehm-e tongo re, “M bahk-a kake nsahm kpee nyi a bahke jo fili ajahbe nyao, fere ka-a ellub ebo. Tibre bobyake kpee kak-m go ebo, m bahke fere faake ka nne no kor-m no.  
\v 7 A lꞌsoro jꞌjamme alahng kak-m, nsol nyia kpee bahke fere jol nyꞌnya.” 
\p  
\v 8 Owo Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Nwer Esowo bungu re, ‘Kak Esowo Ntul ewa. Ye ntahngtahng wo a bahk-e loko.’ ”\f + \fr 4:8 \ft Jon 6:14-15\f* 
\p  
\v 9 Nnehm kehm-e koko tahm a ne go Jeusalem, song rod-e kunu go elkong etahk Esowo, kehm-e tongo re, “A lꞌfere jol Mmon Esowo, yehb gbo ndi.  
\v 10 Tibre nwer Esowo bungu re, ‘Esowo bahke tongo enjel enye, bo baab-a.’  
\v 11 Edi nwer Esowo jehko kpe bung re, ‘Bo bahk-a gbiiri go bo abo, eji a lꞌkꞌba jahre akpade go eltal.’ ” 
\p  
\v 12 Owo Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Nwer Esowo bungu re, ‘Ka gare Esowo Ntul ewa.’ ”\f + \fr 4:12 \ft Mat 12:39\f* 
\p  
\v 13 Eji nnehm m-e gare mal, á kehm-e tohko yake mmongare ntiil. 
\s1 Ana Jisos bomo eltibi go Galili 
\r (Mat 4:12-17; Mak 1:14-15) 
\p  
\v 14 Jisos kehm feere a nsahm Etingi Etohko, ba rehng go Galili. Owo elgahm ene kehm yeere ejang ejahbe jio kpee.  
\v 15 Á jo tibi go bo a ntahk ero. Ane kpee jo tehk-e tehk. 
\s1 Ana bo tene Jisos go Nasaret 
\r (Mat 13:53-58; Mak 6:1-6) 
\p  
\v 16 Jisos kehm jeke go Nasaret, edi ji bo le-e no, á gbal. Efung Esabat á kehm jeke go etahk ero ana á jo kono ellimi. Á kehm mehle yiimi re á lung edi nwer Esowo.  
\v 17 Bo kehm-e kake nwer nyi nnyehnamahr Aisaya. Eji á ma lennge nwer nyio, á kehm song nyehn edi ji bo nyono re, 
\q1  
\v 18 “Etohko ji Jehova jia, kun-m. 
\q1 Á ma-m tum re me n song tiingi etib bi bahke wahnge aneb agbekobo for, awakamahr nyehn. 
\q1 Á ma-m tum re me n song tahre ane ba kpꞌnyehne erem yehke bo go afemfem nya bo wob no, 
\q1  
\v 19 fere tong ane re, 
\q1 Elya eyebatahng ni Jehova ebrehng.” 
\p  
\v 20 Eji á ma bulu nwer nyio, á kehm feere a nyi ka nlokeltum, kehm jehke. Ane kpee ba woomo go ekpꞌkpa ero jio jo seeng-e na seenge too. 
\p  
\v 21 Owo á kehm kehme elbungu a bo re, “Edi nwer Esowo jia ebjol go etingitingi lela, eji ḿ ma wuk.” 
\p  
\v 22 Owo ane kpee kehm-e kehme eltehke. Anoobo alum nya lohng-e go nnyo jo kpo bo esi sehng. Bo kehm bahbe re, “Anv, mmon a Josef sang aa?”\f + \fr 4:22 \ft Jon 6:42\f* 
\p  
\v 23 Á kehm tongo bo re, “Etingitingi, ḿ bahk-m tubu elgan nia re, ‘Nlimakahm, lim elna, wo nob me!’ Fere bung re, ‘Nsol nyi e ma wuk re, woblim go Kapenium, tob lim a fvfo go ega ejahbe!’ ”\f + \fr 4:23 \ft Mat 4:13\f* 
\p  
\v 24 Owo Jisos kehm kpe bung re, “Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Nnyehnamahr awohng awohng limm, no bo kpo ko-e go ege ejahbe.”\f + \fr 4:24 \ft Jon 4:44\f* 
\p  
\v 25 Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Akalebun jolo gbalee go Israel ngare nyi Elaija, eji elahb ki kpe na go nnya era kunu ejang, owo egburu njal kehm bake go ndi nyio kpee.  
\v 26 Jol Esowo tumem Elaija tv nkalebun awohng awohng gona, sehngem nkalebun awohng no jolo go Sarefat ji Saidon wo, Esowo tumu Elaija tv-e. 
\p  
\v 27 “Aneb abili gbalee ba jolo go Israel ngare nyi nnyehnamahr Elisa. Bo, nne awohng awohng nobem abili enye, sehngem Neman ji jolo nne a Siria wo wo nobo.”\f + \fr 4:27 \ft Mat 12:21; Rom 9:30-31\f* 
\p  
\v 28 Eji ane ba woomo ekpꞌkpa ero jio wuku ano, atahng kehm rake bo tete.  
\v 29 Bo kehm-e tohngo yehke go ejahbe jio, song rehng a ne go nkpe ewong nyi bo si ejahbe jio kunu re bo gbul-e, á fooro go egbunggbung ewong ba gbo. 
\p  
\v 30 Á fere jene na, ba sehng go elka ane tahm eje. 
\s1 Nne no bele ebi etohko go ege atahng 
\r (Mak 1:21-28) 
\p  
\v 31 Owo Jisos kehm tahme, song rehng go Kapenium ji li go Galili, song kehme ane tib efung Esabat.  
\v 32 Jo kpo bo esi tib go ege eltibi ni á jo tib bo. Tibre alum nya á jo bung, á jo bungu ana nne no kpi nsahm.\f + \fr 4:32 \ft Mat 7:28; Jon 7:46\f* 
\p  
\v 33 Nne jolo o ekpꞌkpa ero jio, no bele esabsab etohko go ege atahng. Á kehm rabe tiim re,  
\v 34 “Yak-m! E li go nfem anyi awahr a na, Jisos ji Nasaret? A ba re wo ba ranng-ra? N kpꞌkahne nne no a li no. A li mbarebara nne Esowo!” 
\p  
\v 35 Owo Jisos kehm-e nyame re, “Behl ewok, wo lohng-e song!” Ebi etohko jio kehm yehke nne noo tub ndi go elka ane bao, soro lohng-e. Ejumjum we á limem. 
\p  
\v 36 Kehm kehme nne awohng awohng esi kpo, bo kehm kehme elbungu atemtem re, “Anv, elkohn alum anya a, nya á kpo bung go nsahm, tong asabsab atohko, bo jo lohng?” 
\p  
\v 37 Owo elgahm ni Jisos kehm yeere, rehng ejahbe ajehng ajehng ji jolo ejang bio. 
\s1 Ana Jisos limi ane tvv, bo nob ayam ebo 
\r (Mat 8:14-17; Mak 1:29-34) 
\p  
\v 38 Jisos kehm lohngo ekpꞌkpa ero jio, song rehng go etahk Saimon. Nnyehn nkal a Saimon, arumbum nyed-e sehng. Bo kehm-e gboongo ka-e.  
\v 39 Á kehm tahme song yiimi go ege a nkpe edilnong, kehm nyame arumbum nyao, nnenkal noo soro nob, kehm mehle tvtv, soro kehme bo loko. 
\p  
\v 40 Eji njul yahke ba ellahme, ane kpee ba bele aneb ayam, ba jo yam ajoobo ayam tvv, kehm koko bo, ba goji Jisos. Á kehm kunu bo abo, go nne awohng awohng, bo nob ane kpee.  
\v 41 Abi atohko tob lohngo ane gbalee, jo biingi tiim, fere jo bung re, “Wo wo li Mmon no Esowo!”\f + \fr 4:41 \ft Jems 2:19\f* 
\p Jisos jo nyame bo. Á joom taame re bo bung. Tibre bo jo kahne kpee re á li Mesaya.\f + \fr 4:41 \ft Mat 8:29; Mak 3:11-12\f* 
\s1 Ana Jisos bungu alum Esowo go Galili 
\r (Mak 1:35-39) 
\p  
\v 42 Efungfu behre behre Jisos kehm tahme ejahbe jio, song rehng go edi ji li soom. 
\p Ane kehm-e kehme elsebe. Eji bo nyehn-e no, bo kehm jo nok mbang anyehng anyehng, eji á lꞌkꞌtahm bo sa. 
\p  
\v 43 Owo á kehm tongo bo re, “M bahke tob tiingi nnoobo etib bi etul bi Esowo tong ajahbe nyako fvfo. Tibre ana wo wahnge Esowo tum-m no.” 
\p  
\v 44 Owo á kehm tahme, jo song bung alum Esowo go ntahk ero nyi jolo go Judea. 
\c 5  
\s1 Ana Jisos lungu agbokombang abatꞌtoono ebe 
\r (Mat 4:18-22; Mak 1:16-20) 
\p  
\v 1 Efung abehng eji Jisos yiimi go nkpe eto nyi Genesaret, ane kehm ba rur, jo fahd-e tv re bo wuk alum Esowo.  
\v 2 Owo á kehm nyehne agbang na abal go elga. Abasahre nsahre eblohng go agbang nyao, song kehme arim ebo faare.  
\v 3 Á kehm song yel egbang abehng bi jolo bi Saimon, kehm-e tongo re, á reenge egbang feere go elka alahb. Owo á kehm jehke go egbang, jo tib ane bao. 
\p  
\v 4 Eji á ma bung mal, owo á kehm tongo Saimon re, “Reenge egbang, song rehng edi ji kpꞌrahbe, wahn yake arim enyahne kak o, bob nsahre.”\f + \fr 5:4 \ft Jon 21:6\f* 
\p  
\v 5 Owo Saimon kehm-e faange re, “Nsoo, wahr eblim eltum atv atv maa ana tete, jol ejumjum e tikem bob. Wo, eji a ma bung ano, m bahke yake erim ebame kak.”\f + \fr 5:5 \ft Hib 11:1\f* 
\p  
\v 6 Eji bo ma lim ano, bo kehm bobo nsahre gbalee, erim kehm kehme elyare.  
\v 7 Owo bo kehm soro kehme atem ba woomo go egbang behko mahk re bo ba tob bo. Bo kehm bake, ba yehke nsahre nyio, ruru agbang abal abal, fere jol are agbang yahke ter. 
\p  
\v 8 Eji Saimon Pita nyehne ano, á kehm gboko jamme Jisos alahng, kehm bungu re, “Ntul, jeere song, tibre me nne abiafem wo.”\f + \fr 5:8 \ft Mat 8:8-10\f* 
\p  
\v 9 Tibre nkpokosi nyio jo kpo-e esi sehng, a ane bako kpee ba tob jolo a ne o, tib go elkohn nsahre nyi bo bobo no.  
\v 10 Ano wo fvfo, Jems a Jon ba jolo abon Sibidi, bo ji jo lim eltum ano a Pita, jo tob kpo bo esi. 
\p Owo Jisos kehm tongo Saimon re, “Ka kpe fahl! Bomo anv asongo, a bahke fere jo bim ane.”\f + \fr 5:10 \ft Mat 13:47; Mak 16:15-16\f* 
\p  
\v 11 Eji bo ma tohng agbang ebo kunu egbuk, bo kehm tahme ejum ajehng ajehng sa, tahm toono Jisos. 
\s1 Ana Jisos limi nne abili, á nob 
\r (Mat 8:1-4; Mak 1:40-45) 
\p  
\v 12 Efung abehng eji Jisos jolo ejahbe ajehng, nne jolo ona, no abili saab-e na saabe go ngubjing. Á nyehne kan Jisos, á kehm gboko, kohk esamahr ebe go ndi, fere jo gboong-e re, “Ntul, lꞌfere kor-a, a li-m ma lim, n nob.” 
\p  
\v 13 Jisos kehm soro tanne ebo ebe, koor-e, kehm bungu re, “Kor-m kor.\f + \fr 5:13 \ft 1 Tim 2:4\f* Wobnob!” Tvtv o á kehm soro nob abili nyao.  
\v 14 Owo Jisos kehm-e rehke re, á kꞌtong nne ne, fere tong-e re, “Song, wo song kpiri nlimajom, fere tib-e elna, fere lim njom ana Moses tongo no, tib eji a ma nob, eji lꞌjol ejum ntianse ka bo.” 
\p  
\v 15 Tvtv o elgahm ni Jisos kpe yeere na budu. Nlong ane gbalee kehm jo kam, jo ba re bo jo wuk-e, fere jo nob ayam ebo.  
\v 16 Jisos jo tahme, song rehng edi ji li soom, song kak ero. 
\s1 Ana Jisos limi mbanne, á nob 
\r (Mat 9:1-8; Mak 2:1-12) 
\p  
\v 17 Efung abehng eji Jisos jo tib, Bab Farisi, a atꞌtibi ba atahm tob ji ona, ba lohngo go ejahbe ajehng ajehng ji li go Galili, a Judea, fere tob lohng go Jeusalem ba. Nsahm nyi Esowo jolo a Jisos ona re á ko lim ane, bo nob ayam ebo. 
\p  
\v 18 Ane kehm koko mbanne ba a ne, nyi bo sol-e go edilnong. Bo jo gare re bo yel a ne go ekpꞌkpa, song bum-e go alata Jisos.  
\v 19 Bo tingem mbang anyehng anyehng nyi bo bahke sehnge a ne tib ellong ane bao. Owo bo kehm wahre a ne go ero etahk, kehm song lahm elbulu, kehm tahre alehke nya bo kanne go edilnong jio tete ba rehng go elka ane bao, edi ji Jisos jolo no. 
\p  
\v 20 Eji Jisos nyehne ana bo ma taame tv-e, owo á kehm bungu re, “Mbi, abiafem enya, me n tahm ka-a.” 
\p  
\v 21 Atꞌtibi ba atahm, a Bab Farisi kehm kehme elbungu atemtem re, “Anv, ye elkohn nne awo, no kpꞌbungu abꞌbi alum ana nyaa tob Esowo? Nne awo bahke ma tahm ka nne go ege abiafem? Esowo ntahngtahng bi bahke ma tahm ka nne go ege abiafem!” 
\p  
\v 22 Eji Jisos ma seb kahn ana bo jo tir, owo á kehm faange bo re, “Elkohn ntir anyi ń kpꞌtiri go egahna ntim?  
\v 23 Jen ji ga riidi, n lꞌtong nne noa re, ‘Abiafem enya me n tahm ka-a,’ afi n lꞌtong-e re, ‘Mehl yiimi, wo jen?’\f + \fr 5:23 \ft Jon 10:38\f* 
\v 24 M bahk-n tibi re, Mmon no nne kpi nsahm go njini nyia, nyi á bahke ma tahm ka nne go ege abiafem.” Owo á kehm tongo mbanne nyio re, “N kp-a tongo re, wo tahm, rod edilnong eja, song kehnge!” 
\p  
\v 25 Tvtv o nne noo kehm soro mehl yiimi go esamahr ane bao, rod edilnong ji á noongo no, tahm eje kehnge, jo tehk Esowo asongo. 
\p  
\v 26 Ane bao kpee kpo bo esi area. Bo kehm kehme Esowo tehk afahlafahle, fere jo bung re, “Wahr ebnyehn akpokosi nsol lela.” 
\s1 Ana Jisos lungu Livai 
\r (Mat 9:9-13; Mak 2:13-17) 
\p  
\v 27 Eji ma jol ano, Jisos kehm tahme, song nyehn nkokatak no bo jo lung-e re Livai jehk go ekpꞌkpa etak. Á kehm-e tongo re, “Tahm toon-m!” 
\p  
\v 28 Livai kehm tahme ejum ajehng ajehng sa, tahm toon-e.  
\v 29 Owo Livai kehm limi egburu elkak go ege etahk ka Jisos. Abakokatak gbalee tob jolo o, a ane bako fvfo, jo li nsol abo.\f + \fr 5:29 \ft Luk 15:1-2\f* 
\p  
\v 30 Bab Farisi, a atꞌtibi ba atahm ba woomo go ellong Farisis kehm kehme elmemme tob abatꞌtoono Jisos re, “Jen ji wahnge ń kpo li nsol alehke a abakokatak, go aneb abꞌbi?” 
\p  
\v 31 Owo Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Ane ba li nob nob kpehme seb nlimakahm, sehngem ane ba kpꞌyame ba kpꞌsebe.  
\v 32 M baam re me m ba lung anoobo ane, bo gbo ndon. M ba re me m ba lung abi ane.”\f + \fr 5:32 \ft Rom 3:9-10\f* 
\s1 Bada njal abade 
\r (Mat 9:14-15; Mak 2:18-20) 
\p  
\v 33 Egom ane bandiki kehm ba bahb Jisos re, “Jen ji wahnge abatꞌtoono Jon, a ba Farisis kpo bade elbo njal nkpel a nkpele, fere jo kak ero, abatꞌtoono eba kpo li na nsol, fere jo wꞌwo?” 
\p  
\v 34 Owo Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Ḿ bahke limi renan, kehm tongo ane ba bo ma tiingi bo elkak elbal re bo ji njal ngare nyi nlumanne kpeke li a bo?  
\v 35 Ngare kpꞌbake nyi bo bahke yehke nlumanne go bo ellong tahm a ne. Ngare nyio nyi bo bahke kehme elbo njal bade.”\f + \fr 5:35 \ft Elt 13:2-3; 14:23; 1 Kor 7:5\f* 
\s1 Eltibi ni mahne mahne lꞌli, eltibi ni Jisos lꞌli 
\r (Mat 9:16-17; Mak 2:21-22) 
\p  
\v 36 Jisos kehm kpe tub bo elgan re, “Nnene limm, no bahke koko mmojang mbomo no nfenfe, song baade nkꞌkula mbomo. Á lꞌlim ano, edi ji bo ko mmojang mbomo no nfenfe baade, bahke kpe kv na budu. Ejang mbomo nfenfe nehm fuumu a nkꞌkula mbomo.\f + \fr 5:36 \ft 2 Kor 5:17\f* 
\p  
\v 37 “Nnene limm fvfo, no bahke yaange amahm ma kpꞌfahle kak go nkꞌkohko eyahbe. Á lꞌlim ano, amahm mao ma kpꞌfahle bahke limi eyahbe jio bahnge, amahm sale, eyahbe rannge kpee.\f + \fr 5:37 \ft Hib 8:13\f* 
\v 38 Amahm ma kpꞌfahle, bo bahke jo kak go eyahbe nfenfe.  
\v 39 Nnene limm, no kpo wo akꞌkulu amahm, amahm ma kpꞌfahle kehm-e kpe kor. Á bahke bungu re, ‘Akꞌkulu amahm ma ga nob.’ ”\f + \fr 5:39 \ft Jon 9:28-29\f* 
\c 6  
\s1 Bade efung Esabat 
\r (Mat 12:1-8; Mak 2:23-28) 
\p  
\v 1 Efung Esabat abehng eji Jisos jo jen go emahng ji bo bahme nkohl, owo abatꞌtoono ebe kehm jo laade nkohl, fere monngo amohk tv go arahn, jo li. 
\p  
\v 2 Owo egom Farisi jindiki kehm bahbe bo re, “Jen ji wahnge ń kpꞌlimi ejum ji ntahm enyahre sahde re, nne kꞌjo lim efung Esabat?” 
\p  
\v 3 Jisos kehm faange re, “Ń ka tiki lung bade ana Devid limi no ngare nyi njal yam-e no, a ane ebea?  
\v 4 Á yele ekpꞌkpa Esowo, song rod abred nya bo limi bum go esamahr Esowo li, fere tob ka ane ebe ba jolo a ne, bo li, nya ki fuumu re nne awohng awohng li, sehngem abalimajom ba ba jo li.” 
\p  
\v 5 Owo Jisos kehm kpe tong bo re, “Mmon no nne tob li nfono Esabat.” 
\s1 Nne no ebo ebe lohngo no 
\r (Mat 12:9-14; Mak 3:1-6) 
\p  
\v 6 Efung Esabat bi Jisos kpe je go etahk ero song tib, nne awohng jolo o, no eboblum ebe lohngo no. 
\p  
\v 7 Atꞌtibi ba atahm, a Bab Farisi, bo jo baab-e,\f + \fr 6:7 \ft Luk 14:1\f* joare á bahke limi nne awohng awohng, á nob efung Esabat. 
\p  
\v 8 Jisos kꞌkahn ntir atahng ebo, owo á kehm tongo nne no ebo ebe lohngo no re, “Ba, wo ba yiimi ana!” 
\p Nne noo kehm mehle yiimi, jen song yiimi ona. 
\p  
\v 9 Owo Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “N kp-n bahbe re, Anv, ntahm enyahre bungu re wahr jo lim jen efung Esabat, wahr jo kak na nne ebo, afi wahr jo rannge na? Wahr jo tahre elkpin nne, afi wahr jo rannge elkpin nne?” 
\p  
\v 10 Eji á ma seenge bo, song jahm, owo á kehm tongo nne noo re, “Tanne ebo eba!” Á kehm limi ano. Ebo ebe kehm feere jol ana behko jang jang. 
\p  
\v 11 Atahng kehm rake bo tete, bo kehm kehme eltoobo bo bo, ji bo bahke limi Jisos. 
\s1 Ana Jisos yehke abatꞌtoono ebe, ewubu ane abal 
\r (Mat 10:1-4; Mak 3:13-19) 
\p  
\v 12 Ngare nyio Jisos kehm tahme go ewong re á song kak ero. Owo á kange no, jo kak ero ka Esowo.  
\v 13 Eji efungfu ma se, á kehm lungu abatꞌtoono ebe tv elne, kehm jake ewubu ane abal, ba á jo lung bo re abatiingetib.  
\v 14 A wo li ewubu ane abal ba á yehke no. Saimon ji Jisos ka-e mbing nyehko re Pita, a Andru mmonannyehn Pita, go Jems, Jon, Filip, Batolomi,  
\v 15 Matiu, Tomos, Jems ji mmon a Alfeus, a Saimon ji jo seb re ejahbe eje lohng go elwo ni aneb Rom,  
\v 16 go Judas ji mmon a Jems, a Judas Iskariot ji gungu Jisos.\f + \fr 6:16 \ft Jon 6:64,70; Elt 1:13\f* 
\s1 Ana Jisos jo tib, fere lim ane, bo nob ayam ebo 
\r (Mat 4:23-25) 
\p  
\v 17 Eji Jisos jo badde a bo go ewong, á kehm ba yiimi edi ji li bale bale, a ellong abatꞌtoono ebe gbalee, a ellong ane tvv, ba lohngo go Judea kpee, fere lohng go Jeusalem, a ba lohng go nkpe agburu aya, ejang bi Taya, a Saidon. Bo ba re bo ba wuk-e, fere nob ayam ebo.  
\v 18 Ane ba asabsab atohko jo gbiingi bo, bo nobo ane kpee.  
\v 19 Ellong ane bao kpee jo sebe re, bo koor-e, tibre nsahm jo lohng-e lohng.\f + \fr 6:19 \ft Mak 3:10; 5:27-28\f* Á fere lim bo, bo nob ane kpee. 
\s1 Eyebatahng, a ndon 
\r (Mat 5:1-12) 
\p  
\v 20 Owo Jisos kehm tabe esamahr ebe seenge abatꞌtoono ebe, kehm bungu re, 
\p “Elfuulu li ka wahn akpak, tibre etul bi Esowo bꞌbahne bi.\f + \fr 6:20 \ft Mat 19:27-28\f* 
\p  
\v 21 “Elfuulu li ka wahn ji njal kp-n yame anv, tibre ḿ bahke wohngo.”\f + \fr 6:21 \ft Jon 6:35\f* 
\p “Elfuulu li ka wahn ji kpꞌlingi anv, tibre ḿ bahke wolo asol.\f + \fr 6:21 \ft Ell 7:16-17\f* 
\p  
\v 22 “Elfuulu li ka wahn, ane lꞌko-n ekv tib go esi ji Mmon no nne, fere yab a nahne, jo su-n, fere jo bung re, wahn abi ane ba.\f + \fr 6:22 \ft 1 Pit 4:14-16\f* 
\p  
\v 23 “Jo belen eyebatahng, nsol ana nyio lꞌlim, wahn fere jo siiki. Tibre egburu eltuuru enahne nia, nong-n go ejahbetul Esowo.\f + \fr 6:23 \ft 2 Pit 3:13\f* Tibre nsol nyꞌnehm ona nyi babnde ebo jo lim abanyehnamahr Esowo. 
\p  
\v 24 “Eyuu a nahne, wahn afang ane, tibre wahn ebbel ejum ekakeltim ejahne.\f + \fr 6:24 \ft Jems 5:1-3\f* 
\p  
\v 25 “Eyuu a nahne, wahn ji kpꞌwohngo anv, tibre ḿ bahke jene njal njal. 
\p “Eyuu a nahne, wahn ji kpꞌwolo anv, tibre ḿ bahke jehke ndon ndon, fere jo ling. 
\p  
\v 26 “Eyuu a nahne, ane kpee lꞌjo tehk-n.\f + \fr 6:26 \ft Jems 4:4\f* Tibre ano wo babnde ebo tob jo tehk akimfahnge abanyehnamahr.” 
\s1 Ana nnekv ewa bahke jo kor-a 
\r (Mat 5:38-48) 
\p  
\v 27 “N kp-n tongo wahn ji kpꞌwuungu atung re, Anebekv ebahne jo kor-n. Jo limen nnoobo ka ane ba kpo ko-n ekv.\f + \fr 6:27 \ft Rom 12:20\f* 
\v 28 Jo biren nnoobo tv ane ba kpo su-n. Jo kaken ero ka ane ba kpo lim-n ebi.  
\v 29 Nne no lꞌrum-a elkpal, tob sennge ejang behko ka-e fvfo, á kpe-a rum. Nne no lꞌtaare nsubu enya, á lꞌkpe ba ewobo eja taare, tob yake ka-e.  
\v 30 Jo ka nne awohng awohng ejum, no bahb-a no. Nne no lꞌtaare ejum eja, k-e tong re á feere a ji.” 
\p  
\v 31 “Ejum ajehng ajehng ji ń kpꞌsebe re ane jo lim ka-n, wahn fvfo, tob jo limen ano ka bo.\f + \fr 6:31 \ft Mat 7:12\f* 
\v 32 Ane ba ń kpo kor bo, bo lꞌjo kor-n, eltuuru ani Esowo bahk-n tuuru? Tibre ane ba, aneb abiafem kpo kor bo, bo ba fvfo kpo tob kor aneb abiafem.  
\v 33 Ń lꞌjo lim nnoobo ka ane ba kpo lim nnoobo ka-n, eltuuru ani ḿ bahke bele? Tibre aneb abiafem kpo tob lim ano.  
\v 34 Ń lꞌjo bong ane akpohko, ba ń tiri re bo bahke tob bong-n, eltuuru ani ḿ bahke bele? Tibre aneb abiafem kpo bong aneb abiafem, eji bo lꞌtob lim jang jang ka bo.” 
\p  
\v 35 “Nong, anebekv ebahne jo kor-n, wahn jo lim nnoobo. Jo bongen ane akpohko, wahn kꞌjo kunu ekpu re bo feere a nya ka-n. Ń lꞌlim ano, eltuuru enahne bahke gbale. Owo ḿ bahke kehm jolo abon ba Esowo bi gbale sehng. Tibre Esowo kpo lim nnoobo ka ane ba kil jo kak saam, fere tob lim nnoobo ka abi ane. 
\p  
\v 36 “Nong, ane jo fil-n ndon, ana Nso ejahne, ane kpo fil-e ndon.” 
\s1 Kana jo lam ane bako 
\r (Mat 7:1-5) 
\p  
\v 37 “Kana jo lam ane bako, Esowo wahn nehm tob lam. Kana jo tong ane re, bobli ebi, Esowo wahn nehm tob tong re, wahn ebli ebi. Jo tahmen ka ane, Esowo bahke tob tahm ka-n.\f + \fr 6:37 \ft Mat 6:14\f* 
\v 38 Jo kaan, Esowo bahk-n tob ka. Á bahke gare go ebam ji nno a nno, gbehke, fere so, kak, rur wꞌwohng, fere yaange kak egahne abam. Ana ń gare no ka, ano wo fvfo Esowo bahke tob gare ka-n.”\f + \fr 6:38 \ft Mak 4:24\f* 
\p  
\v 39 Jisos kehm tob tub bo elgan re, “Anv, nwakamahr a nne bahke ma tib nwakamahr nyehko mbanga? Bo ane abal abal nehm song gbo yel go elbinga?\f + \fr 6:39 \ft Mat 15:14\f* 
\p  
\v 40 “Nne no kpꞌkpili kpehme gbal sehnge ntꞌtibi ewe. Nne awohng awohng no lꞌkpili mal, á bahke jolo ana ntꞌtibi ewe.\f + \fr 6:40 \ft Mat 10:24-25; Jon 15:20; Fil 1:29-30\f* 
\p  
\v 41 “Jen ji wahnge a kpꞌseenge mmolsahk no wob mmonanne go elmahr, a kil eltiri bada nkporti nyi wob go ega elmahr?  
\v 42 A bahke limi renan, kehm tongo mmonanne, re, ‘Nong, me n yehk-a mmolsahk no wob-a go elmahr,’ eji wofono antahng kil nyehne nkporti nyi wob-a go elmahr? Wobnob tane! Tohko gbo mbang yehke nkporti nyi wob go ega elmahr, eji a lꞌmal nyehn, yehke mmolsahk no wob mmonanne go elmahr.\f + \fr 6:42 \ft 1 Kor 9:27\f* 
\s1 Eti, a akab akab enye 
\r (Mat 7:16-20; 12:33-35) 
\p  
\v 43 “Tibre eti ji nno ajehng ajehng limm, ji kpo kab asabsab akab. Jol fvfo, esabsab eti ajehng ajehng limm, ji kpo kab anoobo akab.  
\v 44 Tibre eti ajehng ajehng, bo kpo liing-e go ege akab. Nnene limm, no kpo bong akab efig go asokonso, fere bong akab avain go egab. 
\p  
\v 45 “Nsol afang nyi wob nnooba nne go ege eltim, nyi nyi á kpo yehke, lohng a nyi. Abꞌbi nsol nya wob ebi nne go ege eltim, nya nya á kpo yehke, lohng a nya. Tibre ji ma rur nne go eltim, ji ji kpo lohng-e go nnyo. 
\s1 Ana ane abal si ntahk 
\r (Mat 7:24-27) 
\p  
\v 46 “Jen ji wahnge ń kpo lung-m re, ‘Ntul, Ntul!’ Ń kil jo lim nsol nyi n kpo tong-n re wahn lim? 
\p  
\v 47 “Nne awohng awohng no lꞌba go egame, ba wuk alum enyame, fere jo lim,\f + \fr 6:47 \ft Jems 1:22-26\f* m bahk-n tibi elkohn nne no á li no.  
\v 48 Á li ana nne no si etahk. Á kpa rꞌrahbe tete rehng go ekpartal,\f + \fr 6:48 \ft Elt 17:11\f* kehm bumu nnahb ekahme enye o. Eji nnyel yele no, alahb jo gbul etahk jio, tikem ma gbehke egbehkegbehke, tibre nnahb ekahme nyio kuumu go ekpartal. 
\p  
\v 49 “Nne no lꞌwuk alum enyame, fere ten go ellimi,\f + \fr 6:49 \ft Jems 2:17\f* á li ana nne no si na si etahk eje kunu go ndi, kꞌbum nnahb ekahme. Eji alahb jo gbul etahk jio, kehm soro gbo kpee rꞌrere rꞌrere.” 
\c 7  
\s1 Ana Jisos limi nlokeltum a nne a Rom, á nob 
\r (Mat 8:5-13) 
\p  
\v 1 Eji Jisos ma bung nsol nyia kpee mal, tong ane bao, á kehm tahme go Kapenium. 
\p  
\v 2 Ntubesi a nsoja awohng jolo o, no bele nlokeltum no jo sahb kor-e kor. Nlokeltum ewe noo jo yame, are á bahke kpoko.  
\v 3 Eji ntubesi a nsoja noo wuku bada Jisos, á kehm tumu anebkul Jus bandiki re bo song gboong-e, á ba lim nlokeltum ewe nob. 
\p  
\v 4 Eji bo ba rehng goji Jisos, bo kehm sahb gboong-e gboongo re, “Ntubesi noo, fꞌfuumu re wo kak-e ebo.  
\v 5 Tibre ejahbe ejahre kpo kor-e sehng. Yebsi etahk ero ka-r.”\f + \fr 7:5 \ft Elt 10:1-2\f* 
\p  
\v 6 Owo Jisos kehm tahme toono bo. Eji á ma kabbe etahk jio, ntubesi a nsoja noo kehm tumu ate ebe tv-e. 
\p Bo kehm-e song tong re, “Ntubesi re, wo kꞌkpe gbiingi elna mbol mbol, are ye fuumem re wo song yel ege ekpꞌkpa.  
\v 7 Jol á fuumem re á ba go ega.\f + \fr 7:7 \ft Luk 5:8\f* Are, wo lub bung ellum ellum, nlokeltum ewe bahke nobo.  
\v 8 Ntubesi re, á li nne no wob go elwo nne. Á tob kpi nsoja nyi tob wob-e go elwo. Á lꞌtong nne noko re, ‘Song!’ Tahm. Á lꞌtong nne noka re, ‘Ba!’ Á ba. Á lꞌtong nlokeltum ewe re, ‘Lim ejum jia!’ Á lim na lim.” 
\p  
\v 9 Jisos, esi kehm-e kpoko, eji á wuku ano. Á kehm keebe, kehm bungu tong ellong ane ba jo toon-e re, “N kp-n tongo re, Jol go Israel n ka tiki nyehn nne no kpi elkohn egburu eltaame ana nia.” 
\p  
\v 10 Eji ane ba ntubesi a nsoja noo tumu bo feere no, ba rehng ege etahk, bo ba nyehne nlokeltum noo ma lohko nob.\f + \fr 7:10 \ft Jon 4:47-54\f* 
\s1 Ana Jisos nyahme njangkun anyehng go elkv 
\p  
\v 11 Etoono efung behko Jisos kehm tahme go ejahbe ji bo jo lung re Nain. Abatꞌtoono ebe gbalee, a ellong ane tvv ba toon-e no je. 
\p  
\v 12 Eji á ma kabbe eti mbu ji jolo ejahbe jio, ane ba solo nkvne kehm lohngo ejahbe jio abake. Nne no kpo no jolo mmon mmon awohng no nnenkal no jolo nkalebun. Ellong ane gbalee jolo a nnenkal noo o, ba lohngo ejahbe jio. 
\p  
\v 13 Eji Ntul a Jisos nyehn-e no, ndon kehm-e gbale go ege eltim tib nnenkal noo. Owo á kehm-e tongo re, “Ka kpe ling!”  
\v 14 Á kehm jeere, song kooro ekpa ji bo gbade nkvne. Aneblum ba sol-e no kehm yiimi. Jisos kehm bungu re, “Njangkun, n kp-a tongo re wo mehl!”\f + \fr 7:14 \ft Luk 8:54; Jon 11:43-44\f* 
\p  
\v 15 Nne no kpo no kehm soro mehl ji, kehm kehme elbungu. Jisos kehm-e jabbe, kak nnyehn go ebo. 
\p  
\v 16 Owo nne awohng awohng kehm kehme elfahle, fere jo tehk Esowo re, “Egburu nnyehnamahr eblohng go egahre ellong.” Bo kpe bung re, “Esowo ebba re á ba tahre ane ebe.” 
\p  
\v 17 Eka jia bada Jisos kehm yeere go Judea kpee, a ajahbe nya jolo sennge Nain ka. 
\s1 Ane ba Jon ji nwohngalahb tumu no 
\r (Mat 11:2-19) 
\p  
\v 18 Abatꞌtoono Jon kehm song tong-e nsol nyio kpee.  
\v 19 Jon kehm lungu abatꞌtoono ebe na abal, tum bo tv Ntul a Jisos re bo song bahb-e re, “Wo wo li nne no kpꞌbake, afi wahr ji sik nne nondiki?”  
\v 20 Eji bo song kpiri Jisos, bo kehm-e tongo re, “Jon ji nwohngalahb wo ma-r tum tv-a re wahr ba bahb-a re, ‘Wo wo li nne no kpꞌbake, afi wahr ji sik nne nondiki?’ ”\f + \fr 7:20 \ft Mak 1:7-8\f* 
\p  
\v 21 Ngare nyio Jisos limi aneb ayam gbalee, bo nob go ajoobo ayam tvv, fere kam ane abi atohko yehke, tob lim awakamahr gbalee, bo nyehn. 
\p  
\v 22 Owo Jisos kehm faange ane ba Jon tumu no re, “Songen, wahn song tong Jon nsol nyi ḿ ma nyehn, fere wꞌwuk. Anv, awakamahr kpꞌnyehne, abanne ebtahm kpꞌjene, aneb abili kpꞌnobo, alakatung kpꞌwuku, akvne kpꞌnyahme go elkv. Akpak kpꞌwuku nnoobo etib. 
\p  
\v 23 “Elfuulu li ka nne no lꞌki-m sel gbo.” 
\p  
\v 24 Eji ane ba Jon tumu bo ma feere fi, owo Jisos kehm bomo elbungu bada Jon, tong ellong ane bao re, “Ń jo lohngo je elka emahng re wahn song nyehn jen? Eljele ni nfeb kpꞌlimi, kpꞌneenga?  
\v 25 Jen ji ń jo jꞌje re wahn song nyehn? Nne no liibi anoobo nsola? Etingitingi, elkohn ane ba kpo liibi ano, fere jo li ebno, bo kpo kono eljolo go ntahk atul.\f + \fr 7:25 \ft Mak 1:6\f* 
\v 26 Anv, ejum aji ń jo je re wahn song nyehn? Nnyehnamahra? 
\p “Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, wahn ebnyehn nne no gbale sehnge nnyehnamahr.  
\v 27 Tibre Jon wo li nne no nwer Esowo bungu no bada ne re, 
\q1 “ ‘M bahke tumu ntiingetib ewame re 
\q1 á gbo-a mbang, song tuungu mbang bum-a.’ 
\p  
\v 28 “N kp-n tongo re, Nne awohng awohng limm, no ma jꞌjol go njini nyia no gbale sehnge Jon.\f + \fr 7:28 \ft Luk 1:15\f* Wo, nne no sahb rꞌrede, no kun etul bi Esowo, á gbale sehnge ye.”\f + \fr 7:28 \ft Mat 13:17\f* 
\p  
\v 29 “Ane kpee, a abakokatak ba wuk-e no, bo ba taame re, Esowo lohko li go etingitingi, tib eji bo ma bel ewohngalahb ji Jon. 
\p  
\v 30 “Bab Farisi, a atꞌtibi ba atahm tꞌten ji Esowo toobo re á lim ka bo, eji ki kor bo re bo bel ewohngalahb jio ji Jon. 
\p  
\v 31 “Anv, m bahke koko ane ba li anv gara jen? Bo li renan?  
\v 32 Bo li ana abonse ba ma lohng song ji go elatahkgur kpi mbene lim. Egom jindiki tong egom jehko re, 
\q1 “ ‘Wahr ebwor afiri ka-n, 
\q1 ḿ bahnem. 
\q1 Wahr ebling aling, 
\q1 wahn tobem ling fvfo.’ 
\m  
\v 33 Eji Jon ji nwohngalahb ba no, á joom li abred, fere jo wo amahm, ń jo tongo re, ‘Á kpi ebi etohko go ege atahng.’  
\v 34 Wo anv, Mmon no nne ebba, kpꞌlehke, fere jo wꞌwo, ń fere jo bungu re, ‘Nyehnen nlehke ebno noa! Á li nwokamahm, a ntem no abakokatak, a ntem no aneb abꞌbi.’ 
\p  
\v 35 “Nne lꞌkpur nsol nyi aneb elkahne kpo lim, owo á bahke tob kahn ana elkahne li no.”\f + \fr 7:35 \ft Ef 5:15; Kol 2:3\f* 
\s1 Ana Jisos jolo go etahk Saimon, nne a Farisi 
\p  
\v 36 Nne a Farisi awohng kehm tiingi Jisos re á song li nsol a ne. Jisos kehm jeke go etahk nne a Farisi noo, song ji go ekpꞌkuru nsol alehke.  
\v 37 Nnenkal awohng jolo ejahbe jio, no jolo nne abiafem. Eji á sebe kahn re Jisos noa, kpꞌlehke nsol go etahk nne a Farisi noo, owo á kehm koko elom akehng tahm a ji,  
\v 38 song yiimi go njahm a Jisos, edi ji Jisos bumu akpade. Á jo lꞌling, abonngo jo toongo wohngo Jisos go akpade. Owo á kehm koko alv esi enye dohk-e akpade, fere sod akpade enye, kehm yaange akehng mao, wohng-e go akpade. 
\p  
\v 39 Eji nne a Farisi no tiingi Jisos nyehne ano, á kehm bungu atahng atahng re, “Li re nne noa lohko li nnyehnamahr, kehn á jol kahne nne no nnenkal noo li no, no kp-e kooro abo, fere kahn elkohn elkpin ni á kpo lim, tibre á li nne abiafem.” 
\p  
\v 40 Owo Jisos kehm bungu re, “Saimon, n kpi ejum ji n kp-a tongo.” 
\p Á kehm faange re, “Aa, ntꞌtibi, tong-m me!” 
\p  
\v 41 Owo Jisos kehm bungu re, “Ane abal jolo go, ba bele nne no kpo bong ane akpohko mbong. Nne noko bel-e mbong a mpon atahl awubu, noko bel-e mbong a mpon eltahl.  
\v 42 Eji bo ki bel ejumjum ji bo bahke koko gal mbong nyio, á kehm yake ka bo. Tong-m, go ellong ane abal baa, nne awo, nne noo bahk-e jo ga kor?” 
\p  
\v 43 Owo Saimon kehm faange re, “Me m bum re, nne no á ga yake ka-e wo.” Jisos kehm bungu tong-e re, “Wobfaange go nseenge.” 
\p  
\v 44 Á kehm keebe seenge nnenkal noo, kehm bungu tong Saimon re, “Wobnyehn nnenkal noaa? Eji m ba yel go ega ekpꞌkpa, me a kaam alahb re men n ru akpade. Wo, ye ma-m ru akpade go ege abonngo, fere ko alv enye dohk-m.  
\v 45 M-e a sodem nnyo. Jol ye ka tiki rahke akpade enyame go elsodo, eji n tiki yel a.  
\v 46 Akehng, m-e a kakem go esi, wo, ye ma-m wohngo akehng go akpade.  
\v 47 Owo wahnge n kp-a tongo re, Abiafem enye nya li gbalee, me n tahm ka-e, tibre á kpi egburu elkoro sehng.”\f + \fr 7:47 \ft Mat 22:36-37\f* 
\p  
\v 48 Á kehm tongo nnenkal noo re, “Abiafem enya me n tahm ka-a.”\f + \fr 7:48 \ft Luk 5:20-24\f* 
\p  
\v 49 Ane bako ba tob ji ekpꞌkuru nsol alehke jio kehm kehme elbungu atahng atahng re, “Ebga! Anv, ye nne awo no kpo tahm ka nne go ege abiafem?” 
\p  
\v 50 Owo Jisos kehm tongo nnenkal noo re, “Song go eyebatahng! Eltaame ena ni ma-a tahre.”\f + \fr 7:50 \ft Rom 10:9-10\f* 
\c 8  
\s1 Anebkal ba jo toono Jisos 
\p  
\v 1 Eji ma jol ano, Jisos kehm jo jen yannge ajahbe ajahbe ajahbe, jo bung alum Esowo, fere jo tiingi nnoobo etib bi etul bi Esowo. Abatꞌtoono ebe, ewubu ane abal, jolo a ne o,  
\v 2 a anebkal bandiki ba á kame bo abi atohko yehke, fere lim bo nob ayam ebo. Meri ji bo jo lung-e re Meri ji lohng go Magdala tob woomo go ellong ane bao, ye ji á kam-e abi atohko na asehma yehke,  
\v 3 go Joanna nkal a Kusa, Kusa ji jolo ntubesi no alokeltum ba jolo go nlaaga Herod, go Susanna, a anebkal gbalee bako ba jo kak Jisos, a abatꞌtoono ebe ebo go nsol nyi bo bele no.\f + \fr 8:3 \ft Mak 15:40-41; Luk 16:9\f* 
\s1 Elgan ni li bada mbahmgbe 
\r (Mat 13:1-9; Mak 4:1-9) 
\p  
\v 4 Eji ellong ane gbalee kpi nlohngo nlohngo go ajahbe ajahbe ajahbe, ba kono edi ajehng goji Jisos, owo á kehm tubu bo elgan nia re, 
\p  
\v 5 “Nne jolo go, no tahme re á song wohngo amohk nti enye go ege egbe. Eji á jo wohngo, nyandiki fooro gbo go mbang. Ane ba kadde sehng. Nruk ba suudu mele. 
\p  
\v 6 “Nyandiki gbo noongo go ndi nyi jolo atal atal. Amohk nti nyao gulu elmahnge, fere kpo, waange, tibre ndi waange sehng. 
\p  
\v 7 “Nyandiki gbo kuumu go elkob akpiri, mahng. Akpiri kehm gbale, bulu akohdo nti nyao. 
\p  
\v 8 “Nyako gbo noongo go nnooba ndi, kehm mahnge, gbal, kab akab, etasok ajehng ajehng nkab atahl alon alon.” 
\p Eji Jisos ma bung ano, á kehm rabe re, “Nne no kpi atung, nong, á wuk!” 
\s1 Ana Jisos lennge elgan nia 
\r (Mat 13:10-23; Mak 4:10-20) 
\p  
\v 9 Abatꞌtoono Jisos kehm-e bahbe ana elgan nia lohngo no.  
\v 10 Owo Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Bo ma-n ka elkahne nio ni nsol nyi li ka etul bi Esowo, nyi Esowo behre no. Egom ane bako kpo wuk ngaane ngaane, eji ‘bo lꞌseenge na seenge, kꞌnyehn, fere wuk na wuk, kꞌkahn ana lohngo no.’ 
\p  
\v 11 “Ana wo elgan nia lohngo no. Amohk nti nyao, alum Esowo nya.\f + \fr 8:11 \ft 1 Pit 1:23\f* 
\p  
\v 12 “Amohk nti nya gbo noongo go mbang lohngo ana ane ba kpo wuk alum Esowo. Nnehm ba yehke alum nyao go bo a ntim, eji bo lꞌkꞌtaame, fere bel eltahre.\f + \fr 8:12 \ft Elt 24:24-27; 2 Kor 3:14-16\f* 
\p  
\v 13 “Amohk nti nya gbo noongo go ndi nyi li atal atal lohngo ana ane ba lꞌwuk alum Esowo. Bo ko go eyebatahng. Alohk bo nehm bel. Bo kpo toono Esowo mmongare ntiil. Elgaare lꞌba, bo yak-e.\f + \fr 8:13 \ft Hib 10:32-39\f* 
\p  
\v 14 “Amohk nti nya gbo kuumu elkob akpiri lohngo ana ane ba ma wuk alum Esowo. Atꞌtiiri nya njini nyia, ekor afang, a ekor nsol nyi njini kpo lim, nsol nyi nyi kpo ra yel go bo a ntim, song bulu alum Esowo tv, akab nehm kul.\f + \fr 8:14 \ft 2 Tim 4:10\f* 
\p  
\v 15 “Amohk nti nya gbo noongo go nnooba ndi lohngo ana ane ba ma wuk alum Esowo, fere ko, kuuru go bo anoobo ntim nya enehm abehng abehng ki wob, soro asi, jo kab akab.\f + \fr 8:15 \ft 1 Kor 15:10\f* 
\s1 Etꞌrekahng ji wob go nla ekpꞌkuru 
\r (Mak 4:21-25) 
\p  
\v 16 “Nnene limm, no ma nyꞌnyaale etꞌrekahng, rod ejeere konngo, jol rod, kak go nla ekpꞌkuru. Á bahke rodo na, kunu go ejum ji bo kpo kunu etꞌrekahng, eji ane ba kpꞌyele ekpꞌkpa lꞌjo nyehn ellennge nio.\f + \fr 8:16 \ft Mat 5:15-16\f* 
\v 17 Tibre ejum ajehng ajehng limm, ji bo behre no, ji lꞌkꞌjol gbuul. Jol ejum ajehng ajehng limm, ji li go mbiiri, ji lꞌkꞌlohng gbuul, ane fere kahn.\f + \fr 8:17 \ft Mat 10:26; Rom 2:16\f* 
\p  
\v 18 “Jo kunen ekpu ana ń kpo wuk nsol.\f + \fr 8:18 \ft Jon 5:47; Elt 7:51\f* Nne awohng awohng no kpi no, bo bahk-e kake na budu. Nne awohng awohng no ki kpi, jio ji á tiri no re á kpꞌkpi, bo bahk-e taare na.”\f + \fr 8:18 \ft Luk 19:11-26\f* 
\s1 Nnyehn Jisos, a abonanyehn Jisos 
\r (Mat 12:46-50; Mak 3:31-35) 
\p  
\v 19 Nnyehn Jisos, a abonanyehn Jisos kehm bake. Bo tikem ma rehng goji Jisos tib ellong ane.  
\v 20 Owo ane bao kehm-e tongo re, “Nne, a abonane, bo baa, yim go elatahk kpꞌsebe re bo nyehn-a.” 
\p  
\v 21 Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Ane ba lꞌwuk alum Esowo, fere jo lim, bo ba li babnnee, a abonanee.” 
\s1 Ana Jisos nyame nfeb, a ebuku 
\r (Mat 8:23-27; Mak 4:35-41) 
\p  
\v 22 Efung abehng Jisos kehm yele go egbang, a abatꞌtoono ebe, kehm tongo bo re, “Nong, wahr siiren rehng egbuk eto jehko.” Owo bo kehm soro tahm.  
\v 23 Eji bo jo fing asongo, Jisos kehm gboko ellu. Owo egburu nfeb kehm ba kehme ellimi go eto jio, alahb kehm kehme elkimi yel egbang, ba elruru. Bo jolo efin efin ngare nyio. 
\p  
\v 24 Owo abatꞌtoono ebe kehm ba kpir-e, kehm-e nyahme re, “Nsoo, nsoo, e kpꞌtane na ao!” 
\p Jisos kehm mehle yiimi, kehm nyame nfeb, a ebuku ji jo lim nsahm nsahm. Kehm rahke, edi naange soom.  
\v 25 Jisos kehm bungu tong bo re, “Anv, eltaame enahne nꞌna me?” 
\p Owo bo kehm kehme elfahle, fere jo kpo bo esi. Bo kehm kehme elbungu atemtem re, “Anv, ye elkohn nne awoe, no kpo bung tong nfeb, a ebuku, wuk-e?” 
\s1 Ana Jisos limi nne no bele abi atohko, á nob 
\r (Mat 8:28-34; Mak 5:1-20) 
\p  
\v 26 Bo kehm song rehng go Gerasa ji jolo egbuk eto jehko. Galili egbuk jehka.  
\v 27 Eji Jisos wahre go egbuk, nne awohng lohngo go nla ejahbe, kehm ba wan-e. 
\p Nne noo bele abi atohko ekidi eblab. Á jo jene ebun ebun. Á joom kang etahk, á jo kange edi ji alahm akvne jolo no.  
\v 28 Á nyehne kan Jisos a, á kehm rabe, gbo-e go alata, fere jo bung wahre wahre re, “E li nfem anyi awahr a na, Jisos ji Mmon Esowo bi gbale sehng? N kp-a gboongo re, wo ki-m kak erem.”\f + \fr 8:28 \ft Jems 2:19\f* 
\v 29 Tibre Jisos tohko tong esabsab etohko jio re á lohng nne noo. Nkpel tvv etohko jio jo yehk-e. Jol eji ane jo kak-e kak agbekobo go abo, a akpade akpade, fere jo baab-e, á jo kiimi na agbekobo nyao, ebi etohko jio jo yehk-e kak go elka emahng. 
\p  
\v 30 Owo Jisos kehm-e bahbe re, “Mbing enya mee?” 
\p Á kehm faange re, “Egom.” Tibre abi atohko gbalee woom-e go atahng. 
\p  
\v 31 Abi atohko nyao kehm gboongo Jisos re, á kꞌtong bo, bo je song yel go nrabbe elbing.\f + \fr 8:31 \ft Ell 20:1-3; 2 Pit 2:4\f* 
\p  
\v 32 Ngare nyio ellong akuk gbalee jo li nsol ona go nkpe ewong. Abi atohko nyao kehm gboongo Jisos re á lub yake bo, bo song yel akuk nyao go atahng. 
\p Jisos kehm yake bo.  
\v 33 Owo abi atohko nyao kehm lohngo nne noo, song yel akuk go atahng. Akuk nyao kpee kehm beke, song fooro egbunggbung aya, yel alahb tan. 
\p  
\v 34 Eji ane ba jo baabe akuk nyao nyehne ano, bo kehm beke, song tooro go etahk, a abon ajahbe ba jolo o.  
\v 35 Ane bao kehm lohngo ba re bo ba nyehn ejum ji ma lim. Eji bo ba kpiri Jisos, bo kehm tob ba nyehn nne no abi atohko lohng-e no, jehk go alata nya Jisos sange sange. Á ma kak nsol go ngubjing kpee. Owo bo kehm kehme elfahle.  
\v 36 Ane ba nyehne ana ngbokesahl nyio ma nob, bo kehm song tooro tong ane bako. 
\p  
\v 37 Ane kpee ba lene ejang bio bi Gerasa kehm gboongo Jisos re á tahm o song.\f + \fr 8:37 \ft Mat 6:24; 19:22\f* Tibre bo jo fahle sehng. Owo Jisos kehm song yel egbang re á feere kehnge. 
\p  
\v 38 Nne no abi atohko lohng-e no kehm gboongo Jisos re, “Nong, me n jol a na!” 
\p Jisos kehm-e tongo re á song,\f + \fr 8:38 \ft Jon 20:17\f* fere bung re,  
\v 39 “Feere song kehnge, wo song tong ane ana ji Esowo ma lim ka-a.” Owo nne noo kehm tahme, song tooro tong ejahbe jio kpee bade egburu ejum ji Jisos ma lim ka-e. 
\s1 Mmon a Jairus, a nnenkal no kooro Jisos ebo go ege a nsubu 
\r (Mat 9:18-26; Mak 5:21-43) 
\p  
\v 40 Eji Jisos feere no, ba rehng egbuk eto jehka, ane kehm-e jo gbaame. Tibre bo ji, jo sik-e. 
\p  
\v 41 Owo nne awohng kehm lohngo ba, no bo jo lung-e re Jairus ji jolo ntubesi etahk ero, ba gbo jamme Jisos alahng, fere gboong-e re, á lub je go ege etahk.\f + \fr 8:41 \ft Jon 12:42\f* 
\v 42 Tibre á bele mmon mmon awohng no nkal, no ma kang ewubu a nnya ebal. Á noongo go emel elkv. 
\p Eji Jisos jo jen mbang mbang asongo, ellong ane jo fahd-e na fahd kak. 
\p  
\v 43 Nnenkal awohng jolo o, no alung jo lohng-e go nnahb go ewubu a nnya ebal. Á rannge akpohko nya á bele no kpee, ka abalimakahm. Jol nnene we tikem ma lim, á nob.  
\v 44 Owo á kehm jeere kohlo Jisos go njahm, fere koor-e go ege esꞌsili nsubu.\f + \fr 8:44 \ft Jon 19:38\f* Tvtv o, alung eme kehm soro kimi. 
\p  
\v 45 Jisos kehm bahbe re, “Nne awo ma-m kooro a?” 
\p Eji ane kpee ma ten, Pita kehm bungu re, “Nsoo, ellong ane ni kpꞌjene a na, ni ni kp-a sehme.” 
\p  
\v 46 Owo Jisos kehm kpe bung re, “Nne ma-m kooro. Tibre me n kahn re, nsahm ma-m tele lohng.” 
\p  
\v 47 Eji nnenkal noo sebe kahn re, á nehm ma biiri, á kehm lohngo kpꞌkahme abake, ba gbo jamm-e alahng, kehm tooro go esamahr ane kpee, ana ji wahnge á koor-e no, fere tong ana á soro nob ngare nyꞌnehm o. 
\p  
\v 48 Owo Jisos kehm bungu re, “Mmon ewame, eltaame ena ni ma-a lim, a ma nob. Song go eyebatahng!”\f + \fr 8:48 \ft Luk 7:50\f* 
\p  
\v 49 Eji Jisos kpi mbungu mbungu, nne awohng kehm lohngo etahk ntubesi ero noo, ba tong-e re, “Mmon ewa ebkpo. Ka kpe gbiingi ntꞌtibi mbol mbol.” 
\p  
\v 50 Eji Jisos wuku ano, owo á kehm-e faange re, “Ka kpe fahl, taame na taame!\f + \fr 8:50 \ft Jon 20:29\f* Á bahke nobo.” 
\p  
\v 51 Eji á ba rehng etahk jio, á taamem re nnene kpe yel ekpꞌkpa, sehngem Pita, Jon, a Jems, go nde mmon, a nnyehn, bo ba, á taame no bo yel. 
\p  
\v 52 Nne awohng awohng jo ji ndon ndon, fere jo ling. 
\p Owo Jisos kehm bungu re, “Kana kpe ling, mmon noa ka kpo, á kpꞌlale na.” 
\p  
\v 53 Bo kehm-e elwolo, tibre bo jo kahne kpee re, mmon noo ebkpo.\f + \fr 8:53 \ft Elt 17:32\f* 
\v 54 Jisos kame kan ane bao yehke, á kehm jabbe mmon noo go ebo, kehm rabe re, “Mmon, mehl!” 
\p  
\v 55 Etohko mmon noo kehm soro feere ba yel-e, á soro mehl tvtv. Owo Jisos kehm tongo bo re, bo ka mmon noo nsol alehke, á li.  
\v 56 Nde, a nnyehn, kpo bo esi sehng. Owo Jisos kehm tongo bo re, bo kꞌtong nne awohng awohng ji ma lim. 
\c 9  
\s1 Ana Jisos tumu abatꞌtoono ebe 
\r (Mat 10:5-15; Mak 6:7-13) 
\p  
\v 1 Jisos kehm lungu abatꞌtoono ebe, ewubu ane abal, tv edi ajehng, fere ka bo nsahm nyi bo bahke jo kam ane abi atohko kpee yehke, fere jo lim ane, bo nob ayam ebo.  
\v 2 Owo á kehm tumu bo re, bo song tiingi ane etib bi etul bi Esowo, fere lim ane, bo nob ayam ebo.  
\v 3 Á kehm tongo bo re, “Eljen ni ḿ bahke tahme, kana rod ejum ajehng ajehng fili, ana ebti efilibo, a abam, a nsol alehke, a akpohko. Kana fili nsubu ebal ebal!\f + \fr 9:3 \ft Luk 22:35\f* 
\v 4 Etahk ajehng ajehng ji bo lꞌvvr-n, jolen o, tete wahn tahm ejahbe jio.\f + \fr 9:4 \ft Elt 16:15\f* 
\v 5 Ejahbe ajehng ajehng ji tohk-n vvrv, tahmen ejahbe jio, wahn kum ebtohko go egahne akpade. Ebtohko bio bi bahke jolo ana ntianse nyi bahke jo bung tob bo.”\f + \fr 9:5 \ft Elt 13:51\f* 
\p  
\v 6 Abatꞌtoono bao kehm tahme, jo yannge ajahbe ajahbe ajahbe, jo tiingi nnoobo etib, fere jo lim ane edi ajehng ajehng, bo nob ayam ebo. 
\s1 Ana ala teele Herod 
\r (Mat 14:1-12; Mak 6:14-29) 
\p  
\v 7 Eji Herod ji jolo ntul no Galili wuku nsol kpee nyi jo lim, owo ala kehm jo teel-e, tibre ane bandiki jo bungu re, “Jon ji nwohngalahb ebnyahme go elkv.”  
\v 8 Ane bandiki bungu re, “Elaija wo ma lohng ba.” Ane bandiki bungu re, “Nnyehnamahr awohng noko no jolo go nkꞌkula ngare wo ma feere ba jol go elkpin.” 
\p  
\v 9 Herod bungu re, “Jon, m m-e kim esi, wo anv, nne awo n kpꞌkpeke wuk elkohn nsol ana nyia bada ne?” 
\p Owo á kehm jo gare ana á bahke nyehne Jisos.\f + \fr 9:9 \ft Luk 23:8\f* 
\s1 Ana Jisos le ellong ane tvv (5,000) 
\r (Mat 14:13-21; Mak 6:30-44; Jon 6:1-14) 
\p  
\v 10 Eji abatiingetib ma feere, bo kehm ba tong Jisos ejum ajehng ajehng ji bo ma lim. Á kehm koko bo bo, tahm a bo go ejahbe ji bo jo lung re Betsaida.  
\v 11 Eji ane wuku ano, owo bo kehm-e toono. Á kehm gbaame bo, fere bung a bo bade etul bi Esowo. Ane ba jo yam, á lim bo, bo nob. 
\p  
\v 12 Ngare nyi njul yahke ba ellahme, owo abatꞌtoono ebe, ewubu ane abal kehm bake ba tong-e re, “Tong ane baa, bo song go ajahbe nya li kpidi kpidi, a abon ajahbe bako, eji bo lꞌting nsol alehke li, fere ting adi nyao bo bahke kange. Tibre tahm edi jia rehng go ajahbe ekidi kpꞌlabe.” 
\p  
\v 13 Owo Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Wahnfono antahng kaan bo nsol alehke, bo li.”\f + \fr 9:13 \ft Jon 21:15; Mat 24:45\f* 
\p Bo kehm faange re, “E kpi abon abred na alon, kunu abon nsahre na abal ba ba. Anv, a kpꞌsebe re wahr tahm song gunu nsol alehke, ba ka elkohn ellong ane ana niaa?”\f + \fr 9:13 \ft Jon 16:14-15\f* 
\v 14 Tibre aneblum ba jolo o, jolo ejum ane atahltahl nkpel ewubbal atahl awubu (5,000). 
\p Owo Jisos kehm tongo abatꞌtoono ebe re, “Nong, ane baa ji agꞌgabe agꞌgabe, ellong anehng anehng jo jol ane atahl abal ane awubu.” 
\p  
\v 15 Abatꞌtoono ebe kehm limi ano, ane bao kpee ji ndi. 
\p  
\v 16 Owo Jisos kehm rodo abon abred bao na alon, kunu abon nsahre abal, kpiidi amahr enye go elbung, kak Esowo saam, bakke, ka abatꞌtoono ebe, eji bo lꞌsong bak ellong ane bao. Bo kehm song bak bo. 
\p  
\v 17 Ane bao li kpee wohngo. Abatꞌtoono ebe kehm taare erik ji ane bao li no sa, ruru ewubu ejeere ebbal. 
\s1 Ana Pita bungu bada Jisos 
\r (Mat 16:13-19; Mak 8:27-29) 
\p  
\v 18 Efung abehng bi Jisos jo kak ero antahng, abatꞌtoono ebe kehm ba kpir-e. Jisos kehm bahbe bo re, “Anv, ane kpo bung renan bada name? Me n li elkohn nne awo?” 
\p  
\v 19 Bo kehm faange re, “Ane bandiki kpo bung re, wo Jon ji nwohngalahb wo. Ane bandiki re, wo Elaija wo. Ane bandiki re, nnyehnamahr awohng noko no jolo mahne mahne wo ma nyahme.”\f + \fr 9:19 \ft Jon 6:14; 7:12,26-27,40-43\f* 
\p  
\v 20 Owo Jisos kehm bahbe bo re, “Anv, wahn kpo bung renan bada name? Me n li elkohn nne awo?” 
\p Pita kehm faange re, “Wo li Mesaya nyi Esowo tum-a no.” 
\p  
\v 21 Jisos kehm rehke bo, fere bung a bo tꞌtahne re, bo kꞌtong nnene. 
\s1 Ana Jisos bungu bade elkv ene 
\r (Mat 16:20-28; Mak 8:30-38) 
\p  
\v 22 Owo Jisos kehm bungu tong abatꞌtoono ebe re, “Mmon no nne bahke nyehne erem gbꞌgbal. Anebkul nfam, atubesi abalimajom, a atꞌtibi ba atahm bahk-e tene, fere wul-e. Lꞌkang nfung era, á nyahme go elkv.”\f + \fr 9:22 \ft Luk 18:31-34\f* 
\v 23 Owo á kehm bungu tong ane kpee re, “Nne no lꞌseb re á toon-m, nong á ten elne tv-m, fere rod ekros eje efung abehng abehng, jo toon-m.  
\v 24 Nne awohng awohng no kpꞌsebe re á tahre elkpin ene, á bahke tane na elkpin ene. Nne awohng awohng no lꞌtane elkpin ene tib go egame esi, á bahke tahre na elkpin ene.\f + \fr 9:24 \ft Luk 17:32-33; Jon 12:25\f* 
\v 25 Nsehng anyi nne bahke lehke, jol afi á gbo afang nya njini nyia kpee, fere tane elkpin ene, afi á yake elne ka go?  
\v 26 Tibre nne awohng awohng no lꞌbe ndon, ten-m, afi jolo alum enyame, fvfo, Mmon no nne bahke tob be-e ndon, á lꞌba go ege ellub, a ellub ni Nde, a abarebare enjel.\f + \fr 9:26 \ft Rom 1:16\f* 
\v 27 Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Egom jindiki ji yim a, nehm kpo, tete bo nyehn etul bi Esowo go amahr.”\f + \fr 9:27 \ft Luk 9:32\f* 
\s1 Ana Jisos yaange ngubjing 
\r (Mat 17:1-8; Mak 9:2-8) 
\p  
\v 28 Bomo ngare nyi Jisos bungu alum nyao, eji ma kang nfung enehkeni, owo á kehm rodo Pita, Jon, a Jems, wahr a bo go ewong re á song kak ero. 
\p  
\v 29 Eji á jo kak ero, esamahr ebe kehm yaange. Nsol nyi á kake no kehm bare, fere jo nyꞌnyane. 
\p  
\v 30 Owo ane abal kehm soro lohng ba kehme elbungu a ne, noko jolo Moses, noko jol Elaija.\f + \fr 9:30 \ft Mak 12:27\f*\fig Ana Jisos yaange ngubjing|alt="Transfiguration of Jesus" src="WA03858b.tif" size="col" loc="Luk 9:30" ref="9:30" \fig* 
\v 31 Bo ba go ellub ba bung a Jisos bade elkv ni á yahke ba elkpoko go Jeusalem, eji á lꞌgohro lim ji Esowo toobo no bum-e. 
\p  
\v 32 Wo gana, Bab Pita ebgbo ellu kpꞌlale.\f + \fr 9:32 \ft Mak 14:37\f* Eji bo ma nyahme, bo kehm nyehne Jisos a ellub ene, fere nyehn ane abal ba yiimi a ne ona. 
\p  
\v 33 Eji ane bao yahke tahm, owo Pita kehm tongo Jisos re, “Nsoo, nꞌnob re wahr jol a. Nong, wahr si nkpatahk era, behko bꞌba, behko bi Moses, behko bi Elaija.” Jol á kahnem ji á jo bꞌbung. 
\p  
\v 34 Eji á kpi mbungu mbungu, ekparesemsem kehm tahle, ba bulu bo. Bo kehm kehme elfahle, eji bo woomo go ekparesemsem. 
\p  
\v 35 Bo kehm wuku ellum go atahng ekparesemsem re, “A wo li akor-m mmon ewame, jo wuken ye!”\f + \fr 9:35 \ft Luk 3:22\f* 
\p  
\v 36 Eji ellum nio ma mal, bo nyehne Jisos ntahngtahng. Bo belle na belle. Ngare nyio bo tikem tong nne awohng awohng ejum ajehng ajehng ji bo nyehne no. 
\s1 Ana Jisos limi mmonse no bele ebi etohko, á nob 
\r (Mat 17:14-18; Mak 9:14-27) 
\p  
\v 37 Etoono efung behko eji bo ma badde go ewong, ellong ane tvv kehm ba kpiri Jisos. 
\p  
\v 38 Nne awohng go ellong ane bao kehm rabe re, “Ntꞌtibi, n kpa gboongo! Nyehn mmon ewame ana! Ye ntahngtahng wo n kpi-e no.  
\v 39 Ebi etohko kpo yehk-e. Ngare anyehng anyehng nyi á lꞌyehk-e, á soro biingi tvtv, fere sok-e, tete nfahl jo tub-e nnyo, fere jo jahr-e. Kpo riidi kehm-e yake abo.  
\v 40 Me n gboongo abatꞌtoono eba re bo kam-e yehke. Bo maam lim.” 
\p  
\v 41 Owo Jisos kehm faange re, “Jen ji wahnge wahn ane ba li anv kil taame? Ń kpo fere soodo! Anv, m bahke kange renan a nahne, fere jo tib-n, ń kehm kahne? Ko mmon ewa ba a ne!” 
\p  
\v 42 Eji mmon noo jo jen abake, ebi etohko jio kehm-e soro yehke tub go ndi, á soro gbo ngboko. 
\p Owo Jisos kehm nyame esabsab etohko jio, fere lim mmon noo, á nob, fere yak-e ka nde. 
\p  
\v 43 Ane kpee kehm kpoko bo esi, eji bo nyehne egburu nsahm nyi Esowo. 
\s1 Ana Jisos kpe bung bade elkv ene 
\r (Mat 17:22-23; Mak 9:30-32) 
\p Eji kpi nkpoko nkpoko ane bao kpee esi bade ejum ajehng ajehng ji Jisos ma lim, owo á kehm tongo abatꞌtoono ebe re,  
\v 44 “Wuken alum nyaa, wahn kak go egahna ntim! Tibre Mmon no nne, bo yahk-e ba elyake kak ane go abo.” 
\p  
\v 45 Bo kahnem ana alum nyao lohngo no. Tibre á lenngem bo, eji bo lꞌkꞌkahn ana lohngo no.\f + \fr 9:45 \ft Luk 18:34; Mak 4:13; Jon 8:27; 10:6\f* Bo jo fꞌfahl a ye bahb ana alum nyao lohngo no. 
\s1 Nne awo ga gbal? 
\r (Mat 18:1-5; Mak 9:33-37) 
\p  
\v 46 Abatꞌtoono Jisos kehm kehme nfaabe lim bada nne no ga gbal go bo ellong. 
\p  
\v 47 Eji Jisos sebe kahn ji bo jo tir go bo a ntim, owo á kehm koko mmonse, á ba yiimi kohl-e,  
\v 48 kehm tongo bo re, “Nne awohng awohng no lꞌko mmonse ana noa tib go egama mbing, á ko me. Nne no lꞌko me, á ko nne no tum-m no.\f + \fr 9:48 \ft Mat 10:40\f* Tibre nne no lꞌga rede go egahne ellong, ye wo li njꞌjoka nne.” 
\s1 Nne awo li nne ewahne? 
\r (Mak 9:38-40) 
\p  
\v 49 Jon kehm bungu re, “Nsoo, wahr ebnyehn nne no kpꞌkame ane abi atohko yehke go ega mbing. E m-e sahde, tibre wa á kpehme toono ana wahr.” 
\p  
\v 50 Owo Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Kana ye kpe sahde, tibre nne no tohk-n ko ekv, ye nne ewahne wo.”\f + \fr 9:50 \ft Fil 1:15-18; Jon 10:16\f* 
\s1 Ejahbe ji tene Jisos 
\p  
\v 51 Eji afung nya bo bahke rodo Jisos tahm a ne go ejahbetul Esowo ma kabbe, á kehm bobo eltim ene re á tahm go Jeusalem.\f + \fr 9:51 \ft Fil 2:8; Luk 13:33\f* 
\v 52 Á kehm tumu ane, bo gbo-e mbang, song rehng go ejahbe Samaria ajehng re bo song toobo nsol bum-e.\f + \fr 9:52 \ft Jon 4:4\f* 
\v 53 Ane ba jolo ona we koom, tibre bo kahne kpee re, á jo tahme go Jeusalem.\f + \fr 9:53 \ft Jon 4:9\f* 
\p  
\v 54 Eji abatꞌtoono ebe Jems, a Jon nyehne ano, owo bo kehm bahbe re, “Ntul, anv, a kpꞌsebe re wahr biri agun lohng go ejahbetul Esowo tv boa, ana Elaija limi noa?”\f + \fr 9:54 \ft Mat 10:14\f* 
\p  
\v 55 Owo Jisos kehm keebe, kehm nyame bo re, “Anv, ń nehme kahn elkohn etohko ji ń kpi noa?”\f + \fr 9:55 \ft Mat 5:44\f* 
\p  
\v 56 “Tibre Mmon no nne baam re á ba rannge elkpin ane, á ba na re ane bel eltahre.”\f + \fr 9:56 \ft Jon 3:17; 12:47\f* Owo bo kehm sehnge, song rehng ejahbe jehko. 
\s1 Nong, akvne kpa akvne kak 
\r (Mat 8:19-22) 
\p  
\v 57 Eji bo jo jen go mbang asongo, nne awohng kehm tongo Jisos re, “M bahk-a toono, je edi ajehng ajehng ji a fi no.” 
\p  
\v 58 Owo Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Akpangang kpi abing, nruk kpi ntahk. Wo, Mmon no nne, edi ellohko esi ajehng ajehng á kpimm.”\f + \fr 9:58 \ft 1 Pit 2:11\f* 
\p  
\v 59 Owo Jisos kehm tongo nne noko re, “Tahm toon-m!” Á kehm-e faange re, “Nsoo, nong me n tohko gbo mbang song kpa nsoo kak.” 
\p  
\v 60 Jisos kehm-e tongo re, “Nong, akvne kpa akvne ebo kak.\f + \fr 9:60 \ft Ef 2:1; Kol 3:1-2\f* Wo, song, wo song tiingi etib bio bi etul bi Esowo.” 
\p  
\v 61 Owo nne noko kehm kpe bung re, “Ntul, m bahk-a toono. Nong, me n tohko gbo mbang song tong ane ebame re me n fio.”  
\v 62 Owo Jisos kehm-e tongo re, “Nne awohng awohng no ma rod elu eje, bom egbe abahme, fere jo keebe go njahm, á kpeem fuumu re á kuumu etul bi Esowo.”\f + \fr 9:62 \ft Luk 17:32\f* 
\c 10  
\s1 Ana Jisos yehke ane atahl ara ane awubu tum 
\p  
\v 1 Eji ma jol ano, owo Jisos kehm yehke ane atahl ara ane awubu bako, tum bo ane abal abal re,\f + \fr 10:1 \ft Mak 6:7\f* bo gbo-e mbang song rehng ejahbe ajehng ajehng, a edi ajehng ajehng ji yefono antahng yahke ba eljeke. 
\p  
\v 2 Tib á tongo bo re, “Egbe ji elkpake jia gbalee. Abalimeltum li ntiil. Owo fvfo nobo re wahn gboongo nfono egbe, á tum abalimeltum tv go ege egbe, bo song kpa.\f + \fr 10:2 \ft Jon 4:35-38\f* 
\v 3 Songen, n kp-n tumu ana abon ejoro re wahn song go ellong agabe.\f + \fr 10:3 \ft Elt 8:32\f* 
\v 4 Kana fili akpohko, a abam!\f + \fr 10:4 \ft Luk 22:35\f* Kana kak akpaketa! Kana yange, kak nne awohng awohng nnyo go mbang!\f + \fr 10:4 \ft Kol 4:5\f* 
\p  
\v 5 “Etahk ajehng ajehng ji ń lꞌyange, jo kaken aneb etahk bao nnyo re, ‘Nong, elkoono jol etahk jia!’  
\v 6 Nne lꞌfere jol o, no kpꞌsebe elkoono, elkoono enahne bahke jolo a ne, tohko jol ano elkoono enahne bahke feere ba tob-n.  
\v 7 Jolen etahk jꞌnehm ona, wahn jo li, fere jo wo ejum ajehng ajehng ji bo lꞌka-n. Tibre nlokeltum fꞌfuumu re á bel eltuuru ene.\f + \fr 10:7 \ft 1 Kor 9:9-15\f* Kana jo yaange ntahk nyindiki jol! 
\p  
\v 8 “Ejahbe ajehng ajehng ji ń lꞌje, bo lꞌvvr-n, jo liin ejum ajehng ajehng ji bo ka-n no.  
\v 9 Limen aneb ayam, bo nob ejahbe jio, wahn fere tong ane bao re, ‘Etul bi Esowo ma-n kabbe.’ 
\p  
\v 10 “Ejahbe ajehng ajehng ji ń lꞌje, bo tohk-n vvrv, tahmen song go afak nya li ejahbe jio, wahn jo bung re,  
\v 11 ‘Ebtohko bi ejahbe ejahne bi ma-r laake go egahre akpade, e kpꞌkumu tv-n. Ejum jia ji nobo re wahn kahn ji li re, Etul bi Esowo ebkabbe.’ 
\p  
\v 12 “N kp-n tongo re, Efung elam bio, elam nehm ga bib a anebe Sodom ana bahke bibi a ejahbe jio. 
\p  
\v 13 “Eyuu a nahne, wahn anebe Korasin! Eyuu a nahne, wahn anebe Betsaida! Li re Taya abola Saidon nyehne akpokosi ana nya ḿ ma nyehn, kehn bobgbo ndon wuku wuku, kak agbajake nsol, fere ji go atong.\f + \fr 10:13 \ft Mat 11:21-23\f* 
\v 14 Efung elam bio, elam nehm ga bib a aneb Taya, a Saidon ana bahke bibi a nahne! 
\p  
\v 15 “Wahn anebe Kapenium, bo ma-n mehl wahre rehng go ejahbetul Esowo.\f + \fr 10:15 \ft Mat 8:5-10\f* Bo bahke fere rod-n, ro kak go ellulagun. 
\p  
\v 16 “Nne no lꞌwuk-n, á wuku me. Nne no lꞌten-n, á tene me. Nne no lꞌten me, á tene nne no tum-m no.”\f + \fr 10:16 \ft Mat 10:40\f* 
\s1 Ana ane atahl ara ane awubu bao feere no kehnge 
\p  
\v 17 Ane atahl ara ane awubu bao feere kehnge go eyebatahng, fere jo bung re, “Ntul jol abi atohko wob-r na go elwo tib go ega mbing.” 
\p  
\v 18 Owo Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Me n nyehn nnehm ma fooro go ejahbetul Esowo gbo ana emangedu.\f + \fr 10:18 \ft Jon 12:31\f* 
\v 19 M ma-n ka nsahm nyi ḿ bahke jo jade enyo, a enang go akpade, fere ka-n nsahm nyi gbale sehnge nsahm kpee nyi Nnekv kpi no. Ejumjum limm, ji bahk-n jo lim go mbang anyehng anyehng.\f + \fr 10:19 \ft Mak 16:18\f* 
\v 20 Kana jo geere tib abi atohko wob-n go elwo. Jo geeren, tibre abing enyahne, bobnyon go ejahbetul Esowo.”\f + \fr 10:20 \ft Ell 3:5\f* 
\s1 Ana eyebatahng gbale Jisos 
\r (Mat 11:25-27; 13:16-17) 
\p  
\v 21 Ngare nyio Jisos kehm bele eyebatahng go etohko, kehm bungu re, “N kp-a tehke Nsoo, wo ji li Ntul no ejahbetul Esowo, a ndi, tibre a behre nsol nyia re akahnkahn ane, a anebe ngbere kꞌnyehn, a ma fere lennge ka abonbili. O nsoo, ano wo kor-a no go ega eltim.\f + \fr 10:21 \ft 1 Kor 1:27-29\f* 
\v 22 Nsoo ebyake ejum ajehng ajehng kak-m go ebo.\f + \fr 10:22 \ft Mat 28:18\f* Nnene nehme kahn nne no Mmon li no, sehngem Nsoo ntahngtahng wo kpꞌkahne. Nnene nehme tob kahn nne no Nsoo li no, sehngem Mmon wo kpꞌkahne, a nne no Mmon bahke lennge Nsoo ka-e.” 
\p  
\v 23 Jisos kehm keebe, kehm bungu tong abatꞌtoono ebe ngare nyi bo jolo bo bo re, “Elfuulu li ka ane ba kpꞌnyehne nsol nyi wahn kpꞌnyehne.\f + \fr 10:23 \ft 1 Jon 1:1-4\f* 
\v 24 Tibre n kp-n tongo re, Abanyehnamahr gbalee, a atul jo sebe re bo nyehn ji ń kpꞌnyehne, jol bo nyehnem. Bo jo sebe re bo wuk ji ń kpꞌwuku, jol bo tikem wuk.”\f + \fr 10:24 \ft 1 Pit 1:10-12\f* 
\s1 Elgan ni li bada nne a Samaria 
\p  
\v 25 Ntꞌtibi no atahm awohng kehm lohngo ba re á ba gare Jisos. Owo á kehm bungu re, “Ntꞌtibi, m bahke limi renan, kehm bele elkpin ni li go njinanjini?” 
\p  
\v 26 Jisos kehm-e bahbe re, “Anv, jen ji bo nyono go atahm? Jen ji a kpo lꞌlung?” 
\p  
\v 27 Owo á kehm faange re, “Esowo Ntul ewa bahke jo kor-a eltim eltim ena, etohko etohko eja, eko eko eja, a ntir a ntir enya. Nne ebjing ewa jo kor-a ana ebjing eba.”\f + \fr 10:27 \ft Rom 13:8-10\f* 
\p  
\v 28 Jisos kehm-e tongo re, “Wobfaange go nseenge. Jo lim ano, a bahke bele elkpin.” 
\p  
\v 29 Ntꞌtibi noo sebe re á tib re, ye etingi nne ji. Owo á kehm bahbe Jisos re, “Nne awo li nne ebjing ewame?” 
\p  
\v 30 Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Nne awohng lohngo go Jeusalem, jo tahm go Jeriko. Eji á jo tahm, á kehm song kpiri awajv. Bo kehm-e yehke nsol nyi á kake no, fere dv-e, tab-e tub, á sa noongo o ana nkvne. 
\p  
\v 31 “Wo ana, ejum jo jol, nlimajom awohng jo sehnge mbang nyio. Eji á ba nyehn nne noo nong no, á kehm gbake eje, sehng nkpe a mbang nyehko tahm.\f + \fr 10:31 \ft Mat 12:7\f* 
\p  
\v 32 “Ano wo fvfo nne no kpo lim eltum go etahk Esowo kehm tob ba rehng edi jio, ba nyehn nne noo, tob gbake eje, sehng nkpe a mbang nyehko tahm eje. 
\p  
\v 33 “Nne a Samaria awohng no jo tahm eljen, kehm tob ba rehng eji nne noo.\f + \fr 10:33 \ft Jon 4:9; 8:48\f* Eji á nyehn-e no, ndon kehm-e gbale go eltim.\f + \fr 10:33 \ft Mat 9:36\f* 
\v 34 Á kehm jeere, song kpir-e, fere kak-e akehng go alok, a alahb avain, gba-e, kehm-e rodo kunu go ege a nnyam, tahm a ne, song rehng go etahk ajehng. Owo á bohng-e no.  
\v 35 Etoono efung behko, á kehm yehke nsiring ewubu, ka nfontahk noo, kehm bungu re, ‘Jo kpur-e. Akpohko anyehng anyehng nya a lꞌkpe rannge budu, n lꞌba, m bahke feere a nya ka-a.’\f + \fr 10:35 \ft 1 Pit 5:2-4; Ell 22:12\f* 
\p  
\v 36 “Anv, ane ara baa, nne awo a tiri re, á jolo nne ebjing a nne no awajv dv-e no?” 
\p  
\v 37 Owo ntꞌtibi no atahm noo kehm faange re, “Nne no á fil-e ndon wo.” 
\p Jisos kehm-e tongo re, “Song, wo tob song lim ano!” 
\s1 Mata abola Meri 
\p  
\v 38 Eji Jisos, a abatꞌtoono ebe jo jen go mbang asongo, á kehm song rehng ejahbe ajehng. 
\p Owo nnenkal awohng no bo jo lung-e re Mata kehm-e vvrv, kak go etahk.  
\v 39 Mata bele mmonannyehn no bo jo lung-e re Meri, ji jii kohlo Ntul a Jisos, jo wuungu atung go ege alum.\f + \fr 10:39 \ft Jon 11:1; 12:2-3\f* 
\v 40 Mata jo dehke na dehke, eji á jo lam nsol ka bo, tib eltum gbale sehng. Owo á kehm bake, ba tong Jisos re, “Ntul, anv wa nehme lub, eji n kpꞌloko eltum nia antahng, Meri kil-m ebo kaka? Tong-e, á ba kak-m ebo!” 
\p  
\v 41 Owo Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Mata, a kpꞌtiiri nsol gbalee nyi kp-a gbiingi go eltim.  
\v 42 Ejum ajehng ji li ji tahne tahne.\f + \fr 10:42 \ft Mat 6:33; Rom 14:17\f* Meri wo ma yehke ji ga nob, ji bo lꞌki-e ma tiki taare.” 
\c 11  
\s1 Bade ero akake 
\r (Mat 6:8-13; 7:7-11) 
\p  
\v 1 Efung abehng Jisos jolo edi ajehng, jo kak ero. Eji á ma kak mal, ntꞌtoono ewe awohng kehm bungu tong-e re, “Ntul, tib-r ana e bahke jo kak ero, ana Jon tibi abatꞌtoono ebe.” 
\p  
\v 2 Owo Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Ń lꞌkehme ero kak, jo bungen re, 
\q1 “Nsoo, nong, mbing enya jol saang! 
\q1 Yake etul eba ba! 
\q1  
\v 3 Jo ka-r nsol alehke nyi lꞌbiingi a nahre go efung efung. 
\q1  
\v 4 Jo tahm ka-r go egahre abiafem! 
\q1 Tibre wahrfono antahng kpo tob tahm ka nne awohng awohng no lim-r abiafem. 
\q1 Ka lim, e yel go elgaare!” 
\p  
\v 5 Owo Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Li re nne awohng ewahne bahke jeke, song kpiri nte ewe nlum atv, kehm-e tongo re, ‘Mbi, bong-m abon abred na ara,  
\v 6 tibre nte ewame awohng eblohng ba eljen go egame etahk. Ejum alehke ajehng ajehng n kpimm, ji m bahk-e kake.’ 
\p  
\v 7 “Fono, nne no wob ekpꞌkpa bahke faange re, ‘Ka ma kpe gbiinga, mbutahk li ta taa, abon ebame nong a name ga edilnonga, n nehm ma mehl ba ka-aa?’ 
\p  
\v 8 “N kp-n tongo re, jol afi á tahmem ba ka-e tib eji á li nte ewe, á bahke tahme ba ka-e ana á kpꞌsebe tib go elgbiingi ni á kp-e gbiingi.\f + \fr 11:8 \ft Luk 18:1-8\f* 
\p  
\v 9 “Owo wahnge n kp-n tongo re, wahn bahb, ḿ bahke bele. Seben, ḿ bahke nyehne. Kahden, bo bahke lennge mbu ka-n.  
\v 10 Tibre nne awohng awohng no lꞌbahb, á bahke bele. Nne no lꞌseb, á bahke nyehne. Nne no lꞌkahd, bo bahke lennge mbu ka-e. 
\p  
\v 11 “Li re nne awohng ewahne li nde nne, mmon ewe lꞌbahb-e re á ka-e ebred, anv, á bahk-e kake eltala? Afi á lꞌbahb-e re á ka-e nsahre, á bahke bobo nnyo ka-e?  
\v 12 Afi á lꞌbahb-e re á ka-e ejenkok, á bahk-e kake nnang?  
\v 13 Anv, wahn ji li na abi ane, ń lꞌmal ka abon ebahne nsol nyi nno, lꞌlim renan Nsoo no li go ejahbetul lꞌkꞌka ane ba bahb-e no Etingi Etohko?”\f + \fr 11:13 \ft Mak 11:24\f* 
\s1 Jisos, a ntul a nnehm 
\r (Mat 12:22-30; Mak 3:20-27) 
\p  
\v 14 Jisos kehm kame nne no jolo nkamme ebi etohko yehke. Eji ebi etohko jio ma lohng nne noo, nne noo kehm kehme elbungu. Owo kehm kpoko ellong ane bao esi. 
\p  
\v 15 Egom jindiki kehm kehme elbungu re, “Á kpo kam ane abi atohko yehke tib go nsahm nyi Belsebul ntul a nnehm ka-e no.” 
\p  
\v 16 Egom jehko jo sebe re bo gar-e. Owo bo kehm-e tongo re á tib elliingi ni bahke lohngo go ejahbetul Esowo.\f + \fr 11:16 \ft Mak 8:11\f* 
\p  
\v 17 Jisos kꞌkahn ntir atahng abo,\f + \fr 11:17 \ft Jon 2:25\f* owo á kehm tongo bo re, “Ejahbe ajehng ajehng ji lꞌyab, jol ebo ebo, bahke rannge na, afi fere jol nlaaga, nlaaga nyio bahke tane.  
\v 18 Anv, ejahbetul ji nnehm lꞌyab, ejahbetul eje bahke limi renan kehm yiimi? Tibre wahn kpo bung re, n kpo kam ane abi atohko yehke go nsahm nyi ntul a nnehm.  
\v 19 Lꞌjol re n kpo kam ane abi atohko yehke go nsahm nyi ntul a nnehm, anv, nsahm anyi abon ebahne kpo ko, jo kam bo yehke? Owo wahnge bo bahke jolo ane ba bahk-n lame. 
\p  
\v 20 “Wo, lꞌfere jol re n kpꞌkame ane abi atohko yehke go nsahm nyi Esowo, lohngo re etul bi Esowo bi ma badde ba tob-n.  
\v 21 Etahntahn nne lꞌfili ntahme go ebo, jo baabe etahk eje, ejum ajehng ajehng eje nehm ran esi.  
\v 22 Etahntahn nne ji tahne sehng-e lꞌba, ba nok a ne, fere ga-e, á bahk-e taare ntahme enye nyi á kpo tir re, nyi nyi bahk-e kake ebo, fere kpu nsol enye tahm a nyi song bak.\f + \fr 11:22 \ft Kol 2:15\f* 
\p  
\v 23 “Nne no ki li ka me, ye nnekv ewame wo. Nne no tohk-m tob elkpuku bum edi ajehng, á kpꞌfare na faade. 
\s1 Ana esabsab etohko kpo feere 
\r (Mat 12:43-45) 
\p  
\v 24 “Eji esabsab etohko ma lohng nne, á kpo song yannge go adi nya kpꞌwaange,\f + \fr 11:24 \ft Jon 7:38-39\f* jo seb edi ji á bahke reke ekv.\f + \fr 11:24 \ft Mak 5:12\f* Á tohko ting edi ajehng ajehng, á bahke bungu re, ‘M bahke feere go egame etahk ji n tahme sa.’ 
\p  
\v 25 “Á lꞌfeere ba, ba nyehn, etahk jio bo ma feenge, fere tuungu ejum ajehng ajehng bum go nseenge.  
\v 26 Owo á bahke feere song ko atohko nyako na asehma nya sabe sehnge yefono. Bo feere ba lene o. Nne noo bahke kpe sab na sehng ana wuku wuku á jolo no.”\f + \fr 11:26 \ft 2 Pit 2:20; Jon 5:14\f* 
\s1 Nnenkal no tehke Meri nnyehn Jisos 
\p  
\v 27 Eji Jisos ma bung ano, nnenkal awohng go ellong ane bao kehm bungu re, “Elfuulu li a nnenkal no jel-a no, fere yab-a.” 
\p  
\v 28 Jisos kehm faange re, “Elfuulu ga li ka ane ba wuku alum Esowo, fere jo lim.”\f + \fr 11:28 \ft Luk 8:21\f* 
\s1 Ana ane bahbe Jisos re á lim nkpokosi 
\r (Mat 12:38-42) 
\p  
\v 29 Eji ellong ane jo kpe ba budu, Jisos kehm kehme elbungu re, “Ane ba li anv, abi ane ba. Bo kpꞌsebe re bo nyehn nkpokosi.\f + \fr 11:29 \ft 1 Kor 1:22\f* Nkpokosi anyehng anyehng limm, nyi bo bahke nyehne, sehngem nkpokosi ana nyi Jona nyi bo bahke nyehne.  
\v 30 Ana Jona jolo elliingi ka aneb Ninive, ano wo fvfo Mmon no nne bahke tob jol elliingi ka ane ba li anv. 
\p  
\v 31 “Go efung elam bio, ntul a nnenkal no Seba bahke mehle yiimi, ka ane ba li anv ebi. Tibre á lohngo nlaabambang ejahbe, ba goji Solomon re á ba wuk elkahne ene.\f + \fr 11:31 \ft Mat 8:11\f* Wo anv, ejum jia, ji gbale sehnge Solomon.\f + \fr 11:31 \ft Mak 1:7\f* 
\p  
\v 32 “Go efung elam bio, anebe Ninive bahke mehle yiimi, ka ane ba li anv ebi. Tibre bo gbꞌgbo ndon go bo abiafem, eji bo wuku alum Esowo nya Jona bungu no. Nyehnen, a wo li ejum ji gbale sehnge Jona. 
\s1 Ellennge ni ngubjing 
\r (Mat 5:15; 6:22-23) 
\p  
\v 33 “Nnene limm, no ma nyꞌnyaale etꞌrekahng, fere rod song behr, jol rod ejeere konngo. Á bahke rodo na, kunu go ejum ji bo kpo kunu etꞌrekahng, eji ane ba kpꞌyele ekpꞌkpa lꞌjo nyehn. 
\p  
\v 34 “Elmahr ena li ana etꞌrekahng ka ngubjing enya. Elmahr ena lꞌjol saang, ngubjing enya kpee bahke jolo ellennge.\f + \fr 11:34 \ft Jon 1:47\f* Elmahr ena lꞌfere jol abꞌbi, ngubjing enya kpee bahke gboko ejannge.\f + \fr 11:34 \ft Elt 8:21\f* 
\p  
\v 35 “Jo kunu ekpu, eji ellennge ni wob-a go atahng lꞌkꞌfere gbo ejannge.\f + \fr 11:35 \ft Ef 5:8-10\f* 
\v 36 Ngubjing enya kpee lꞌjol ellennge, kꞌbel nkpohko anyehng anyehng nyi kpi ejannge, owo ngubjing enya bahke jolo ellennge ellennge kpee ana etꞌrekahng kpꞌyake tub-a.”\f + \fr 11:36 \ft Jon 3:10-21; 8:12\f* 
\s1 Ana Jisos jo wa Bab Farisi eyuu 
\r (Mat 23:1-36; Mak 12:38-40) 
\p  
\v 37 Eji Jisos kpi mbungu mbungu, nne a Farisi awohng kehm-e tongo re á song li nsol a ne. Owo á kehm yele ekpꞌkpa, song ji go ekpꞌkuru nsol alehke.\f + \fr 11:37 \ft Luk 7:36; 14:1\f* 
\v 38 Nne a Farisi noo kehm-e kpoko esi, eji á nyehne re, Jisos ruum akidi, kehm kehme nsol li.\f + \fr 11:38 \ft Mat 15:2\f* 
\p  
\v 39 Owo Ntul a Jisos kehm-e tongo re, “Wahn Farisis, ń kpo ru njahm a nkob, a njahm ekpingi. Go atahng, abꞌbi nya ma rur, a nsol ejv.\f + \fr 11:39 \ft Luk 17:20-21\f* 
\v 40 Wahn agboolo nya! Ye ji limi njahm elatahk sang tob lim atahnga?  
\v 41 Yaren akpak ka nsol nyi wob go egahne akob, a nkpingi, ejum ajehng ajehng ejahne bahke bare.\f + \fr 11:41 \ft Luk 19:8-9\f* 
\p  
\v 42 “Eyuu a nahne, wahn Farisis! Wahn kpo ka eltahme go asahkesahke nsol ana nkambe, a alamaje, a anyane nyako kpee, fere jo gbake elam, a elkoro ni Esowo bum go nkpe. Limen nsol ebal ebal! Kana gbake ejum ajehng, bum go nkpe! 
\p  
\v 43 “Eyuu a nahne, wahn Farisis! Go egahne ekpꞌkpa ero, kpo kor-n re wahn jo ji go mbuksong. Go are, kpo kor-n re ane jo gong na, kak-n nnyo.\f + \fr 11:43 \ft Luk 20:46\f* 
\p  
\v 44 “Eyuu a nahne! Ń li ana alahm nya bo kil nyehne, ane kpꞌkadde sehng, jol bo nehme kahn re, bobfere jol ane ba ki kpe li saang.” 
\p  
\v 45 Owo ntꞌtibi atahm na awohng kehm-e faange re, “Ntꞌtibi, alum nya a kpꞌbungu a, a kp-r suku nao!” 
\p  
\v 46 Jisos kehm bungu re, “Eyuu a nahne, wahn atꞌtibi ba atahm fvfo! Ń kpo si ane elsol ni nnen ni kpo riidi elsolo, jol wahnfono antahng, ń kpehme tohko gꞌgare elmehle. 
\p  
\v 47 “Eyuu a nahne! Wahn ba li ane ba kake alahm nya anyehnamahr Esowo go nsement, ba babnso ejahne wulu no.  
\v 48 Eji ḿ ma lim ano, ebtib re, wahn ebtaame tv ji babnso ejahne limi no. Tibre bo ba wulu bo. Wahn ma rod alahm ebo kpꞌkake nsement. 
\p  
\v 49 “Owo wahnge Elkahne ni Esowo bungu re, ‘M bahke tumu abanyehnamahr, fere tum abatiingetib tv bo. Bandiki, bo bahke wulu bo. Bandiki, bo bahke nohko bo,’  
\v 50 eji alung ma abanyehnamahr kpee ba bo wulu no, bomo ngare nyi njini bomo no lꞌtuunu ane ba li anv,\f + \fr 11:50 \ft Elt 7:52\f* 
\v 51 bomo goji Ebel tete ba rehng goji Sekaraya ji bo wul-e go elka elka ni edi njom alimi, a etahk Esowo. Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Ane ba li anv, Esowo bahke bo bahb bada nsol nyia kpee. 
\p  
\v 52 “Eyuu a nahne, wahn atꞌtibi ba atahm? Wahn ba ma rod egbokoro jio ji etahk elkahne. Wahnfono yelem. Ń kpo kpan ane ba jol yele.” 
\p  
\v 53 Eji Jisos ma tahm edi jio, owo atꞌtibi ba atahm, a Bab Farisi kehm-e kehme alum jamme, fere jo bahb-e abahbe gbalee bada nsol tvv,  
\v 54 fere jo baab-e go ege alum nnyo, eji bo lꞌbob-e. 
\c 12  
\s1 Ayist nya Bab Farisi 
\r (Mat 10:26-27) 
\p  
\v 1 Eji ellong ane gbalee ma ba rur edi ajehng, bo ruru sehng, fere jo kadde atem go akpade, owo Jisos kehm gboko mbang tong abatꞌtoono ebe re, “Jo gberen ayist nyao nya Farisis, nya li alum abal abal.\f + \fr 12:1 \ft Mat 16:6,12\f* 
\v 2 Ejumjum limm, ji bo bulu no, ji bo lꞌkꞌlennge. Ejumjum limm, ji bo behre no, ji lꞌkꞌjol gbuul.  
\v 3 Ejum ajehng ajehng ji ḿ bungu go ejannge, bo bahke wuku ngara njul. Ji ḿ bungu awꞌwa go nkimi, bo bahke kuumu go aro ntahk, tooro wahre wahre. 
\s1 Nne awo fuumu re nne fahl-e 
\r (Mat 10:28-31) 
\p  
\v 4 “Ate ebame wahn, n kp-n tongo re, Kana jo fahl ane ba kpo wul ngubjing, ba lꞌkꞌma kpe lim ejumjum budu.  
\v 5 M bahk-n tibi nne no fuumu re wahn fahl-e. Jo fahlen ye jio ji kpi nsahm nyi á bahke ma ro nne kak ellulagun ngare nyi ngubjing ma kpo. N kp-n tongo re, ye wo nobo re wahn fahl-e.\f + \fr 12:5 \ft Ell 20:10\f* 
\p  
\v 6 “Nne li ma gunu nruk elon go are, ka mpene ebal. Jol tvtv ona, abehng abehng limm, bi Esowo m-e yini.  
\v 7 Alv enyahne nya li go egahne esi, Esowo ebfange kpee.\f + \fr 12:7 \ft Luk 21:18\f* Owo nobo re wahn kꞌjo fahl. Tibre wahn ba ga gbal sehnge nruk, jol afi bo ruru renan. 
\s1 Bada ntianse ayiimi ka Jisos go esamahr ane 
\r (Mat 10:32-33; 12:32; 10:19-20) 
\p  
\v 8 “N kp-n tongo re, Nne awohng awohng no lꞌyiim-m ntianse go esamahr ane, Mmon no nne bahk-e tob yiimi ntianse go esamahr enjel nyi Esowo.  
\v 9 Nne no lꞌten-m go esamahr ane, Mmon no nne bahke tob ten-e fvfo go esamahr enjel nyi Esowo.  
\v 10 Nne awohng awohng no lꞌbung ellum tob Mmon no nne, á bahke ma bel eltahmeka.\f + \fr 12:10 \ft 1 Jon 1:7-9\f* Nne no lꞌbung ebi tob Etingi Etohko, á nehm bel eltahmeka.\f + \fr 12:10 \ft 1 Jon 5:16-17; Jon 16:7-9\f* 
\v 11 Bo lꞌko-n, tahm a nahne go ntahk ero, afi jolo go esamahr atubesi, afi bo fere kak-n esub, kana jo tiiri bade ana ḿ bahke faange, jol kana jo tiiri ana ḿ bahke bungu.  
\v 12 Tibre Etingi Etohko bahk-n tibi ngare nyio ji ḿ bahke bungu.” 
\s1 Elgan ni li bade egboolo efange nne 
\p  
\v 13 Nne awohng go ellong ane bao kehm bungu tong Jisos re, “Ntꞌtibi, ba tong mmonannee, wahr baange nsol nyi e li elkv me!” 
\p  
\v 14 Owo Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Mbi, nnene limm, no tong-m re me n jo lam alam, fere jo bak-n nsol nyi ḿ ma li elkv.”\f + \fr 12:14 \ft Jon 3:17\f* 
\p  
\v 15 Á kehm bungu tong bo ane kpee re, “Jo kunen ekpu, wahn jo gbere elnahne, eji ń lꞌkꞌjo baare amahr enyahne go nsol ane re wahn jo bel na bel bel bel budu. Tibre nsol gbalee nyi nne kpi no sang li elkpin ene.”\f + \fr 12:15 \ft 1 Tim 6:9-10\f* 
\p  
\v 16 Owo á kehm tubu bo elgan re, “Efange nne ajehng jolo gona, ji egbe eje sahb lꞌlak.  
\v 17 Á kehm bahbe elne re, ‘Anv, m bahke limi renan? Ebuungu ejame gbalem, ji m bahke lake eblu ebame.’  
\v 18 Owo á kehm bungu re, ‘Ana wo m bahke limi. M bahke kpe nyange ebuungu ejame. Owo m bahke lake eblu ebame, a nsol nyehko gona kpee.  
\v 19 Owo m bahke kehm bungu tong elname re, Me n li efa sehng. M bahke jehke, re ekv, bel elkpin, jo li na li li li, fere jo wo, bel eyebatahng. Tibre me m bel nsol gbalee nyi bahk-m biingi go nnya tvv.’ 
\p  
\v 20 “Esowo kehm-e tongo re, ‘Wo egboolo jia, lela atv bo bahke bake, ba ko elkpin ena. Nsol nyi a ma kuuru bum elna, nne nondiki wo bahke ba ting ko.’\f + \fr 12:20 \ft Hib 9:27\f* 
\p  
\v 21 “Ano wo tob li ka nne no lꞌkpu nsol afang luk elne, no ki gbo afang nya Esowo.”\f + \fr 12:21 \ft 1 Tim 6:17-19\f* 
\s1 Esowo kpꞌkahne ji nne kpꞌsebe 
\r (Mat 6:25-34) 
\p  
\v 22 Jisos kehm bungu tong abatꞌtoono ebe re, “Ana wo wahnge n kp-n tongo re, wahn kꞌjo tiiri bada nsol alehke nyi ḿ bahke jo li, a nsol nyi ḿ bahke jo kak go egahna ngubjing.  
\v 23 Elkpin ni ga gbal sehnge nsol alehke. Ngubjing ga gbal sehnge abomo. 
\p  
\v 24 “Nyehnen nruk! Bo kpehme bahm. Bo kpehme kpa. Abuungu, bo kpimm, jol bo kpehme kak go ayake. Esowo bi kpo le bo. Anv, wahn sang ga gbal sehnge nruka?  
\v 25 Nne awo ewahne no bahke kpe ma budu abon nnya go ege elkpin, eji á kpꞌtiiri ana?  
\v 26 Eji ń lꞌkꞌma lim mmonsꞌsohko ejum ana noo, jen ji wahnge ń kpꞌtiiri bada nsol nyehko? 
\p  
\v 27 “Nyehnen ana atꞌtul nkpad kpo gbal go emahng! Bo kpehme nyennge, lim eltum. Bo kpehme jamme nsol, kak elbo. Wo, n kp-n tongo re, jol Solomon go ege ellub, á liibem ana etꞌtuul ajehng go ellong atꞌtuul nyao.  
\v 28 Ana Esowo kpo liibi ajele nya li go emahng, nya kpo kpin lela lela, behna bo jahm fi, jen ji wahnge á lꞌki-n tob liibi, wahn ji kpꞌkahn taame ntiil? 
\p  
\v 29 “Ano wo fvfo nobo re wahn kꞌjo sahb sꞌseb nsol nyi ḿ bahke jo li, fere jo wo.\f + \fr 12:29 \ft 1 Tim 6:6-9\f* Kana jo tiiri!  
\v 30 Tibre ane baka baka ba ki nyi Esowo ba kpo lim ano. Nso ejahne kpꞌkahne re, ń kpꞌsebe nsol nyia.  
\v 31 Ga nob re wahn gbo mbang seb etul bi Esowo. Nsol nyehko kpee á bahk-n budu.\f + \fr 12:31 \ft Kol 3:2\f* 
\s1 Afang nya ejahbetul 
\r (Mat 6:19-21) 
\p  
\v 32 “Kana kpe fahl, wahn mmoblong ejoro! Tibre koro Nso ejahne re wahn tob ji go eti etul eje.\f + \fr 12:32 \ft Luk 22:29-30\f* 
\p  
\v 33 “Gungen nsol nyi ń kpi no, wahn rod akpohko ka akpak.\f + \fr 12:33 \ft Luk 18:22\f* Belen abon abam akpohko ba lꞌkꞌtiki kul, wahn fere gbo afang nya ejahbetul Esowo, nya lꞌki-n mal go abo, nya li edi ji nwajv anyehng anyehng lꞌkꞌma rehng, etan lꞌkꞌma wo.  
\v 34 Tibre edi ji nsol afang enya li no, owo eltim ena bahke jolo.\f + \fr 12:34 \ft Fil 3:20\f* 
\s1 Alokeltum ba kpꞌsiki nde ebo 
\p  
\v 35 “Tooben ebjing, wahn gbaange agbaange go egahne ebun!\f + \fr 12:35 \ft 1 Pit 1:13\f* Taben av atꞌrekahng enyahne wahre!\f + \fr 12:35 \ft Mat 25:1-13\f* 
\v 36 Jolen ana ane ba kpꞌsiki nde ebo re á kehnge elkak elbal ba, eji á lꞌfeere ba kahd, bo lꞌlennge ka-e. 
\p  
\v 37 “Elfuulu li ka alokeltum ba lꞌkꞌlal ngare nyi nde ebo bahke bake.\f + \fr 12:37 \ft Jon 14:3\f* Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, á bahke tongo bo re bo ji ekpꞌkuru nsol alehke. Á bahke gbaange egbaange eje, fere jo loko bo.  
\v 38 Á li ma ba nlum atv. Á li ma ba nkpese efungfu. 
\p “Elfuulu li ka alokeltum bao ba, á lꞌba nyehn bo, bo ma toobo ebjing.  
\v 39 Jia ji nobo re wahn kahn. Tibre nfontahk kahne kahn ngare nyi nwajv kpꞌbake, kehn á jol baabe etahk eje, kꞌtaame nwajv lahm etahk eje yel.\f + \fr 12:39 \ft 1 Tes 5:2\f* 
\p  
\v 40 “Wahn fvfo, tooben ebjing, tibre Mmon no nne bahke bake ngare nyi ń kil tiri re á kpꞌbake.” 
\s1 Nkakesehk a nlokeltum, a ebi nlokeltum 
\r (Mat 24:45-51) 
\p  
\v 41 Pita kehm-e bahbe re, “Ntul, elgan nia, a tubu tong wahra, afi nne awohng awohng?” 
\p  
\v 42 Owo Ntul a Jisos kehm faange re, “Li ka ekahnkahn nlokeltum no kpi ekakesehk, no nde bahke yake alokeltum bako, kak go ege ebo re á jo le bo ngare.\f + \fr 12:42 \ft 1 Pit 5:2-4; Elt 20:28\f* Nne awo li elkohn nlokeltum ana noa?  
\v 43 Eyebatahng bahke jolo a nlokeltum noo, no nde lꞌba, á bahke ba kpir-e, á kpꞌlimi ano.  
\v 44 Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, á bahke yake nsol enye kpee kak-e go ebo.\f + \fr 12:44 \ft Mat 25:21\f* 
\p  
\v 45 “Nlokeltum noo lꞌfere bung go ege eltim re, ‘Nsoo eblaange elbake,’ á lꞌbom alokeltum bako go eldohko, fere jo li, jo wo, fere jo buumu,  
\v 46 owo nde nlokeltum noo bahke bake efung bi á kil ekpu kunu re á bahke bake, ngare nyi á kil elkahne. Nde noo bahk-e boomo, kiimi akv akv akv, fere tuur-e eltuuru nꞌnehm ana ni á bahke tuuru ane ba ki taame tv-e. 
\p  
\v 47 “Nlokeltum no kahne ji nde sebe re á lim, kꞌtoobo ebjing, fere lim, bo bahk-e sahb dꞌdv.\f + \fr 12:47 \ft Jems 4:17; Jon 9:41\f* 
\p  
\v 48 “Nlokeltum no ki kahn ji nde sebe re á lim, á lꞌfere lim nsol nyi fuumu re bo dv-e, ye, bo we nehm ga dv. 
\p “Nne awohng awohng no bo m-e ka nsol gbalee, bo bahke sebe nsol gbalee go ege abo.\f + \fr 12:48 \ft Ef 4:7\f* Nne no bo ma yake nsol gbalee kak-e go ebo, ye wo, bo bahke koko gbalee go ege.\f + \fr 12:48 \ft Mat 25:20,22\f* 
\s1 Jisos kpo lim ane yab 
\r (Mat 10:34-36) 
\p  
\v 49 “M ba re me m ba kono agun go njini. Kor-m kor re, kehn agun nyao bom ellulu.\f + \fr 12:49 \ft Elt 2:3\f* 
\v 50 Ewohngalahb jia, ji m bahke tohko bel, ji ji ma-m gba area. Bahke jolo anaana tete mal.\f + \fr 12:50 \ft Jon 12:27\f* 
\v 51 Anv, ń kpꞌtiri re, eji m ba njini nyia, n ko elkoono ba a nia? N kp-n tongo re, elkoono sang wahnge m ba no. M ba, eji ane lꞌyab.\f + \fr 12:51 \ft Rom 12:18; Jon 7:43; 9:16\f* 
\v 52 Bomo anv asongo ane alon lꞌjol nlaaga anyehng, abal bahke yabe jol ebo ebo, ane ara bako jol ebo ebo.  
\v 53 Nde nne bahke woomo njahm nyehko, mmon ewe woomo njahm nyehka. Nnyehn nne bahke woomo njahm nyehko, mmon ewe woomo njahm nyehka. Nnyehn nne bahke woomo njahm nyehko, nkal a mmon woomo njahm nyehka.” 
\s1 Ana nne bahke kahne ngare 
\r (Mat 16:2-3) 
\p  
\v 54 Jisos kehm tob bung tong ellong ane bao re, “Ń lꞌnyehn ekparesemsem ma tahl go erede nfam kpꞌbake, ń kpo bung tvtv re, ‘Elahb yahke ba elnake.’ Lohko na fvfo.  
\v 55 Nfeb lꞌkehme ellimi nyi lohng go elka emahng, ń kpo bung re, ‘Ewannge yahke ba.’ Lohko ba fvfo. 
\p  
\v 56 “Wahn aneb alum abal abal ba! Ń kpo mal seenge elbung abola ndi, fere kahn ana ji bahke jolo. Jen ji wahnge ń lꞌkꞌma kahn ngare nyi li anv?\f + \fr 12:56 \ft Luk 19:42,44; Elt 17:30; 1 Tes 5:1; 1 Jon 2:18\f* 
\p  
\v 57 “Jen ji wahnge wahnfono antahng kil ebtiki kahn ji kpꞌnobo?  
\v 58 Nnekv ewa lꞌfere ko-a, tahm a na go esub, nok, eji a lꞌtoobo a ne ngare nyi ń kpeke li go mbang, eji á lꞌki-a tohng, tahm a na goji nlamalam, nlamalam faak-a, kak mbehresi go ebo, mbehresi ko-a song kak ngbekobo.  
\v 59 N kpa tongo re, a nehm tiki lohng ona, tete a gohro gal mbong enya kpee mal, jol ederi ajehng ajehng nehm sa.”\f + \fr 12:59 \ft Mat 5:25-26; 18:34; 2 Tes 1:9\f* 
\c 13  
\s1 Yaangen mbang enyahne 
\p  
\v 1 Ngare nyio ane jolo o, ba tongo Jisos bade ana Pailet wulu aneb Galili, eji bo jo lim njom ka Esowo. 
\p  
\v 2 Owo Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Anv, ń kpꞌtiri re, anebe Galili bao ba ga jol aneb abiafem sehnge anebe Galili bako kpeea, tib eji bo nyehne erem bioa?\f + \fr 13:2 \ft Mat 10:28; Jon 9:2\f* 
\v 3 Eꞌee! N kp-n tongo re, ń tohko yaange mbang enyahne, ḿ bahke tob kpo kpee ana ane bao.\f + \fr 13:3 \ft Jon 5:14\f* 
\p  
\v 4 “Anv, elku ane ara ba kpo go Siloam, eji enyong gbo bulu bo mee? Anv, ń kpꞌtiri re, bo ba ga jol abi ane sehnge ane bako kpee ba lene go Jerusalema?  
\v 5 Eꞌee! N kp-n tongo re, ń tohko yaange mbang enyahne, ḿ bahke tob kpo kpee ana ane bao.” 
\s1 Elgan ni li bade eti ji ki kab akab 
\p  
\v 6 Jisos kehm tubu bo elgan nia re, “Nne awohng bele eti ji bo kpo lung re efig go ege etahngga. Á kehm bake ba seb akab. Á tingem nkab anyehng anyehng.\f + \fr 13:6 \ft Mat 21:19\f* 
\v 7 Owo á kehm tongo nne no jo lim eltum go etahngga jio re, ‘Nyehnee, nnya era nyia, nyi n kpo ba, ba kpur akab go eti jia, jol n ka tiki bel. Gbahk eti jia tub, tibre yim na yim a mbol mbol.’ 
\p  
\v 8 “Owo á kehm-e faange re, ‘Nsoo, nong tohko kpe jol elya nia ni ni. M bahke kpake kpee sennge, fere kak akpake elu, a ajele.\f + \fr 13:8 \ft 2 Pit 3:9\f* 
\v 9 Owo e bahke nyehne, joare bahke kabe akab. Tohko fere kab, wo kehm gbahke tub.’ ”\f + \fr 13:9 \ft Luk 21:24; Rom 11:25; Mat 24:32\f* 
\s1 Ana Jisos limi nnenkal, á nob efung Esabat 
\p  
\v 10 Efung Esabat abehng Jisos jo tibi go etahk ero ajehng.  
\v 11 Nnenkal awohng jolo o, no bele ebi etohko ji bum-e eyam, bi ma kang elku a nnya era. Nnenkal noo fehde na fehd, á joom kpe ma tanne etannetanne. 
\p  
\v 12 Eji Jisos nyehn-e no, á kehm-e lungu tv elne, kehm-e tongo re, “Nnenkal, ngubjing enya ebfannge!”  
\v 13 Jisos kehm-e kunu abo, nnenkal noo soro tanne tvtv, fere jo tehk Esowo. 
\p  
\v 14 Ntubesi etahk ero noo, atahng kehm-e rake, tib eji Jisos ma lim nne, á ma nob efung Esabat. Á kehm kehme ane tong re, “Li nfung erakera nyi ane bahke jo lim eltum. Jo baan afung nyao, wahn jo ba nob ayam enyahne, go efung Esabat sang.” 
\p  
\v 15 Owo Ntul a Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Wahn aneb alum abal abal ba! Wahn ane kpee, wahn sang kpo fannge efong ebahne, a ebvankang ebahne go ntahk nyi bo kpo wooma, tahm a bo go alahb efung Esabata?\f + \fr 13:15 \ft Luk 14:5\f* 
\v 16 Nyehnen nnenkal noa no li mmon no Ebraham, no nnehm gba-e no go elku a nnya era. Nobem re á for go eyam bia efung Esabata?”\f + \fr 13:16 \ft Mak 3:4; Kol 2:16\f* 
\p  
\v 17 Alum nya Jisos faange no kehm riki anebekv ebe ndon, bo ane kpee. 
\p Wo, ellong ane bako kpee jo bele na eyebatahng tib go agburu nsol nya á ma lim. 
\s1 Elgan ni li bada mmohk asia 
\r (Mat 13:31-32; Mak 4:30-32) 
\p  
\v 18 Owo Jisos kehm bungu re, “Anv, etul bi Esowo li renan? M bahke koko gara jen?  
\v 19 Li ana mmohk asia nyi nne rodo, song bahm go ege etahngga. Kehm gbale egburu elrahn.\f + \fr 13:19 \ft Jon 12:24\f* Nruk kehm bake, ba si ntahk ebo ona.”\f + \fr 13:19 \ft Mat 13:4; Elt 20:29-30\f* 
\s1 Elgan ni li bade ayist 
\r (Mat 13:33) 
\p  
\v 20 Jisos kehm kpe bung re, “Anv, m bahke koko etul bi Esowo gara jen?  
\v 21 Li ana ayist,\f + \fr 13:21 \ft Mat 16:6,12\f* nya nnenkal ko song behr go ebam aflawa na ebra, tete semme kpee,\f + \fr 13:21 \ft Ell 2:18--3:6\f* fere tung.” 
\s1 Nfiidifiida mbutahk 
\r (Mat 7:13-14,21-23) 
\p  
\v 22 Eji Jisos jo tahm go Jeusalem, á jo sehnge go ajahbe ajahbe, fere jo tib ane. 
\p  
\v 23 Nne awohng kehm-e bahbe re, “Nsoo, anv, abon amohk ane abik abik ba bahke bele eltahra?” 
\p Owo Jisos kehm faange bo re,  
\v 24 “Jo noken, eji ń lꞌsehng go nfiidifiida mbutahk.\f + \fr 13:24 \ft Fil 3:12; Jon 10:7\f* Tibre n kp-n tongo re, ane gbalee bahke gare re bo sehng yel, bo nehm ma sehng. 
\p  
\v 25 “Nfontahk lꞌsi mꞌmehl, bam mbu, ḿ bahke yiimi go mbutahk, jo kahd, fere jo bung re, ‘Nsoo, lenng-r mbu!’ Owo á bahk-n kehm faange re, ‘N nehme kahn edi ji ń lohng no ba.’\f + \fr 13:25 \ft Mat 25:11-12\f* 
\p  
\v 26 “Owo ḿ bahke kehme elbungu re, ‘E jo li nsol a na, fere jo wo. A jo tibi go egahre ejahbe.’\f + \fr 13:26 \ft Mat 24:39\f* 
\p  
\v 27 “Á bahke bungu re, ‘N kp-n tongo re, N nehme kan edi ji ń lohng no ba. Wahn abi ane baa, tahm-m wahn go esamahr!’ 
\p  
\v 28 “Go elatahk wo ḿ bahke jo ling, fere jo kono amahn go esi, ń lꞌnyehn Ebraham, Aisik, Jekob, a abanyehnamahr kpee go ejahbetul Esowo, wahnfono antahng fere sa elatahk.\f + \fr 13:28 \ft Mat 8:11-12\f* 
\v 29 Ane bahke lohngo go ejang njini abehng abehng ba ji, jo li nsol go ejahbetul Esowo. 
\p  
\v 30 “Egom jindiki ji kahle njahm bahke fere gbo mbang. Egom jindiki ji gbo mbang fere kahle njahm.”\f + \fr 13:30 \ft Rom 11:25-26\f* 
\s1 Ana Jeusalem jo kor Jisos 
\r (Mat 23:37-39) 
\p  
\v 31 Ngare nyꞌnehm ona aneb Farisi bandiki kehm ba kpiri Jisos, kehm-e tongo re, “Lohng a, song! Tibre Herod kpꞌsebe re á wul-a.”\f + \fr 13:31 \ft Mak 3:6; Luk 12:1\f* 
\p  
\v 32 Owo Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Songen, wahn song tong ekpangang jio re, ‘N kpꞌkame ane abi atohko yehke, fere lim ane, bo nob ayam ebo. N kpꞌlimi lela, lim behna, lꞌbiingi nfung era, n gohro lim mal.’\f + \fr 13:32 \ft Jon 17:4; 2 Tim 4:7\f* 
\v 33 M bahke tahme eljen ename asongo lela tete rehng behna, a etoono efung behko. Tibre nnyehnamahr, bo bahk-e tiki wul go Jeusalem, edi jindiki sang.\f + \fr 13:33 \ft 1 Tes 2:14-15\f* 
\p  
\v 34 \fig Ana nkok kpo walle abon|alt="A hen sitting on the chicks" src="lb00061c.tif" size="col" loc="Luk 13:34" ref="13:34" \fig*“Wahn Jeusalem, ń kpo wul abanyehnamahr, fere tuubu ane ba Esowo tumu tv-n atal. Nkpel tvv n jo gare re me n lung-n tv elname ana nkok abon kpo lung abon ebe, fere walle bo. Wahn korem elbake! 
\p  
\v 35 “Anv, etahk ejahne bahke sake nehme nehme.\f + \fr 13:35 \ft Luk 21:20-24\f* Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, me ń nehm kpe tiki nyehn tete ḿ bung re, ‘Elfuulu li a nne no kpꞌbake go mbing nyi Ntul.’ ” 
\c 14  
\s1 Ana Jisos limi nne eyam, á nob 
\p  
\v 1 Efung Esabat abehng Jisos kehm tahme song li nsol go etahk ntubesi a nne a Farisi awohng. Owo bo jo baab-e. 
\p  
\v 2 Nne awohng no gbo eyam ebyeenge kehm bake goji Jisos. 
\p  
\v 3 Owo Jisos kehm bahbe atꞌtibi ba atahm, a Bab Farisi re, “Anv, ntahm enyahre tꞌtaame re nne jo lim ane, bo nob efung Esabata, afi?”\f + \fr 14:3 \ft Mak 3:4; Gal 5:22-23\f* 
\p  
\v 4 Bo kehm belle. 
\p Owo Jisos kehm rodo nne eyam noo, lim-e, á nob, fere yak-e, á song.  
\v 5 Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Anv, nne awo ewahne no mmon ewe, afi nfong enye bahke gboko yel elbing alahb ni kpꞌrahbe, á kꞌsong yehk-e efung Esabata?”\f + \fr 14:5 \ft Mat 12:11; Luk 13:15\f* 
\p  
\v 6 Jol bo we maam faange ejumjum. 
\s1 Alum nya Jisos bungu tong ane ba bo tob tiingi bo elkak 
\p  
\v 7 Jisos nyehne kan ana ane ba bo tob tiingi bo elkak fvfo ma song yehke adi nji nya li wahre wahre,\f + \fr 14:7 \ft Mat 23:6\f* owo á kehm tubu bo elgan re,  
\v 8 “Nne lꞌtiing-a elkak elbal, ka song ji edi nji ji li wahre wahre. Fundiki nne no ga gbal sehnge wo, nfono elkak tꞌtob tiing-e fvfo.  
\v 9 Lꞌjol ano, nne no tiingi wahn ane abal abal bahke bake, ba tong-a re, ‘Tahm ka nne noa, á ji!’ Ndon bahk-a kehme elfili re wo fere song ji go nredereda nji. 
\p  
\v 10 “Bo lꞌtiing-a elkak, song ji go nredereda nji, eji nfono elkak lꞌba, á bahke ba tong-a re, ‘Mbi, mehl, wo ba ji ga nwahrewahra nji.’ Owo a bahke bele ellub go esamahr ane kpee ba jehk a na go ekpꞌkuru jio. 
\p  
\v 11 “Tibre nne awohng awohng no lꞌrod elne bum wahre wahre, bo bahk-e rede na. Nne no lꞌrede elne, bo bahk-e rodo, bum wahre wahre.”\f + \fr 14:11 \ft Luk 18:14; Fil 2:8-9\f* 
\s1 Alum nya Jisos tongo nne no tiing-e no 
\p  
\v 12 Owo Jisos kehm tob bung a nne no tiing-e no re, “A lꞌtiingi ane re bo ba li nsol, afi jolo elkak, ka jo tiingi ate eba, jol abonane, jol nnahb enya, a aneb nkontahk eba ba li afang ane. Tibre bo fvfo bo bahk-a tob tiingi. A lꞌlim ano, wobbel eltuuru ena tvtv go ejum ji a limi no.  
\v 13 Ga nob re a lꞌtiingi ane elkak, wo jo tiingi akpak, a abanne, a awakamahr.  
\v 14 A bahke bele elfuulu, tibre bo nehm ma tob lim ka-a.\f + \fr 14:14 \ft Luk 6:34-35\f* Esowo bi bahke limi ka-a efung bio bi atingi ane bahke nyahme go elkv.”\f + \fr 14:14 \ft Jon 5:29\f* 
\s1 Elgan ni li bade egburu elkak 
\r (Mat 22:1-10) 
\p  
\v 15 Eji nne awohng no woomo go ellong ane ba tob ji ekpꞌkuru jio a Jisos wuku ano, owo á kehm-e tongo re, 
\p “Elfuulu li ka nne no bahke lehke nsol go ejahbetul Esowo.”\f + \fr 14:15 \ft Ell 22:2\f* 
\p  
\v 16 Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Nne awohng jolo go, no limi egburu elkak, tiingi ane gbalee.  
\v 17 Eji afung elkak ma rehng, á kehm tumu nlokeltum ewe re á song tong ane ba á tiingi bo re bo ba.\f + \fr 14:17 \ft Jon 6:36; 7:37\f* Tibre bobtoobo ejum ajehng ajehng bum. 
\p  
\v 18 “Bo ane kpee kehm kehme ellaange kunu go nsol. Ngbokambang a nne kehm tongo nlokeltum noo re, ‘N gunu nfong ewubu, n yahke tahm song wuungu bo. Lub wuk ana n kp-a gboongo titi.’  
\v 19 Owo nne noko kehm kpe bung re, ‘N gunu edi egbe. M bahke tahme song nyehn. Lub wuk ana n kp-a gboongo titi.’  
\v 20 Nne noko kehm tob kpe bung re, ‘Me n ko nkal, owo wahnge n lꞌkꞌma ba.’\f + \fr 14:20 \ft Mak 4:19\f* 
\p  
\v 21 “Nlokeltum noo kehm feere song tong nde. 
\p “Nfono elkak noo, atahng kehm-e rake. Á kehm tongo nlokeltum ewe re, ‘Foomo song go afak ejahbe, wo song ko akpak, fere ko abanne, a awakamahr ba a bo.’\f + \fr 14:21 \ft Ef 2:11-12\f* 
\p  
\v 22 “Eji nlokeltum noo je feere, á kehm ba tong nde re, ‘Nsoo, ana a bungu no, me n lim. Eyake jia, kpeke li, ji ane bahke kpe ji.’ 
\p  
\v 23 “Nde kehm tongo nlokeltum noo re, ‘Song go abang ebud, a abang ekulugbe, wo jo fanne ane, eji bo lꞌba, ba yel, ane lꞌrur go egame ekpꞌkpa.’  
\v 24 Tibre n kp-n tongo re, Nne awohng awohng go ellong ane ba bo tiingi bo nehm tiki li elkak ename.”\f + \fr 14:24 \ft Luk 13:28\f* 
\s1 Nne awo li etingitingi ntꞌtoona Jisos? 
\r (Mat 10:37-38) 
\p  
\v 25 Ellong ane gbalee jo jene a Jisos. Owo á kehm keebe, kehm tongo bo re,  
\v 26 “Nne awohng awohng no lꞌba go egame, á nehm ma jol ntꞌtoono ewame, tohko jol re á ko nde ekv, a nnyehn, a nkal ewe, a abon ebe, a abonanyehn, a elkpin ene fvfo.  
\v 27 Nne no tohko sol ekros eje, tahm toon-m, á nehm ma jol ntꞌtoono ewame.  
\v 28 Nne awohng ewahne lꞌseb re á si enyong, á bahke tohko gbo mbang ji, gabe ana bahk-e kimi ekun, joare akpohko enye bahk-e biingi, á si kpee mal.  
\v 29 Á tohko lim ano, fundiki á bahke bumu nnahb ekahme nyi nyi, á nehm kpe ma soro asi. Ane kpee ba lꞌnyehn, bo bahk-e kehme elnyoko re,  
\v 30 ‘Nne noa ana bomo etahk go elsehke, á kpeem ma gohro si mal.’\f + \fr 14:30 \ft Mat 13:20-21; 10:22; 1 Kor 1:8\f* 
\p  
\v 31 “Ntul no kpi nsoja atahltahl nkpel eltahl, no yahke tahm re á song nok ebta a ntul noko no kpꞌbake re á ba nok a ne, no kpi nsoja atahltahl nkpel atahl abal, á bahke tohko gbo mbang ji kpee, toobo, joare á li ma yiimi, nok a ntul noko.\f + \fr 14:31 \ft Ell 2:16; 19:11-16\f* 
\v 32 Joare á nehm ma yiimi a ne, á bahke tumu ane tv ntul noko, eji á kpeke li go fee re bo song bahb-e ji á bahk-e kake, bo kehm koono.\f + \fr 14:32 \ft Hib 3:13; Mat 5:25\f* 
\p  
\v 33 “Ano wo fvfo, nne awohng awohng ewahne no tohko yake ejum ajehng ajehng ji á kpi no, á lꞌkꞌma jol ntꞌtoono ewame. 
\p  
\v 34 “Akang kpꞌyebe. Elyebe akang lꞌlohng, a bahke limi renan, akang kehm kpe yebe?\f + \fr 14:34 \ft Mat 5:13; Mak 9:50\f* 
\v 35 Jol nehm nob ka ndi, jol nehm nob re nne ko kak go abangenahb nti. Ane kpo sale na elkohn akang nio wohng go. Nne no kpi atung, nong, á wuk.” 
\c 15  
\s1 Njoro nyi tane no 
\r (Mat 18:12-14) 
\p  
\v 1 Abakokatak, a aneb abiafem jo jeere kohlo Jisos, eji bo lꞌjo wuk-e. 
\p  
\v 2 Bab Farisi, a atꞌtibi ba atahm jo memme re, “Nne noa kpo ko aneb abiafem, fere jo li nsol a bo.”\f + \fr 15:2 \ft Luk 5:30-32\f* 
\p  
\v 3 Owo wahnge Jisos kehm tubu bo elgan re,  
\v 4 “Anv, nne ewahne awohng lꞌbel ejoro atahl alon, anyehng lꞌtan, á nehm tahm ejoro behko sa go elka emahng, song seb nyi tane no tete á nyehn-ea?\f + \fr 15:4 \ft Luk 19:10\f* 
\v 5 Á lꞌnyehn-e, á bahk-e rodo, kunu go ebahk, fere jo geere. 
\p  
\v 6 “Á lꞌba rehng etahk, á bahke lungu ate ebe, a aneb nkontahk ebe, fere tong bo re, ‘Tob-m wahn elgeere, tibre me n nyehn njoro enyame nyi tane no.’ 
\p  
\v 7 “N kp-n tongo re, Eyebatahng bahke ga gbal go ejahbetul Esowo, nne abiafem awohng lꞌgbo ndon,\f + \fr 15:7 \ft Luk 19:8\f* sehnge atingitingi ane gbalee ba kil sebe re bo gbo ndon.\f + \fr 15:7 \ft Mat 3:9; 21:32\f* 
\s1 Nsiring nyi tane no 
\p  
\v 8 “Li re nnenkal kpi nsiring ewubu, anyehng kehm ba tan-e, anv, á nehm nyaale etꞌrekahng, fere feenge ekpꞌkpa, jo seb bem bem bem tete á nyehna?\f + \fr 15:8 \ft Luk 19:10; Ell 3:1-2; Hib 3:13\f* 
\p  
\v 9 “Á lꞌnyehn, á bahke lungu ate ebe, a aneb nkontahk ebe, tong bo re, ‘Ba tob-m wahn elgeere, tibre me n fere nyehn nsiring nyi tan-m no.’ 
\p  
\v 10 “N kp-n tongo re, Ano wo fvfo enjel nyi Esowo kpo bel eyebatahng, nne abiafem awohng lꞌgbo ndon.”\f + \fr 15:10 \ft Ef 3:10\f* 
\s1 Mmon elwur 
\p  
\v 11 Owo Jisos kehm bungu re, “Nne awohng jolo go, no bele abon ba nlum na abal.  
\v 12 Nkalla kehm tongo nde re, ‘Nsoo, ka-m ejang nsol nyi bahke jolo nyꞌnyame.’ Owo nde noo kehm bake abon ebe na abal nsol enye. 
\p  
\v 13 “Gaam kang, mmonkalla noo kehm kpuku nsol kpee nyi á bele no, tahm go nlaabambang ejahbe.\f + \fr 15:13 \ft Jon 21:18\f* Owo á song li akpohko enye go mbang elwur kpee mal.\f + \fr 15:13 \ft 1 Kor 6:19\f* 
\v 14 Eji á ma fad akpohko enye kpee mal, owo njal kehm bake go ejahbe jio, jol nyi nse sang. Á kehm sake abo abo. 
\p  
\v 15 “Á kehm tahme, song wu laake nfono ejahbe awohng. Á kehm-e tumu re á song, jo song baabe akuk.\f + \fr 15:15 \ft Rom 6:20-21\f* 
\v 16 Jol-e koro re, á jo li nsol nyi akuk kpo li. Jol nnene jolem no jo ka-e.\f + \fr 15:16 \ft 1 Pit 2:2\f* 
\p  
\v 17 “Eji á ma fere gbo ntir, owo á kehm bungu re, ‘Ane kpee ba nsoo kpo lak bo eltum, bo kpi nsol alehke gbalee, jol sehnge ana nyi bo kpꞌsebe. Wo, me n jehk ana, kpꞌkpoko njal.  
\v 18 M bahke tahme, song kpiri nsoo, fere tong-e re, Nsoo, me n lim abiafem bade Esowo, fere tob lim bada na.\f + \fr 15:18 \ft 2 Kor 7:10\f* 
\v 19 Me n kpeem fuumu re bo jo lung-m re mmon ewa. Tob lak-m, me n tob jol nlimeltum ewa.’ 
\p  
\v 20 “Owo á kehm mehle, feere goji nde. Jol á gaam kabbe go etahk nde, nde kehm-e nyehne. Ndon kehm-e fili, á kehm beke, song bing-e, fere sod-e nnyo. 
\p  
\v 21 “Owo mmon noo kehm-e tongo re, ‘Nsoo, me n lim abiafem bade Esowo, fere lim bada na. N kpeem fuumu re bo jo lung-m re mmon ewa.’ 
\p  
\v 22 “Nde kehm lungu alokeltum ebe, kehm tongo bo re, ‘Song koon ekpawobo ji nno a nno ba a ji, wahn ba kak-e. Tob kaken ye ebil go ebo, wahn fere kak-e akpaketa go akpade.  
\v 23 Song koon mmon a nfong no sahb jꞌjok, wahn ba wul, wahr limen elkak, fere bel eyebatahng.\f + \fr 15:23 \ft Ef 3:20\f* 
\v 24 Tibre mmon ewame noa kpꞌkpo, wo anv, yebfere jol go elkpin.\f + \fr 15:24 \ft Ef 2:4-5\f* Á tꞌtan. Anv a, m m-e nyehn.’ 
\p “Owo bo kehm soro bom elkak nio go ellimi. 
\p  
\v 25 “Ngbokambang a mmon jolo go egbe. Eji á jo kehnge abake, ba kabbe go nkpe etahk, á kehm wuku ase nya bo jo kub, fere jo bahn.  
\v 26 Á kehm lungu nlokeltum awohng, kehm-e bahbe re, ‘Ase nyao lohngo rejen?’ 
\p  
\v 27 “Owo á kehm-e faange re, ‘Mmonanne wo ma feere kehnge. Nso ma wul mmon a nfong no joko jok. Tibre yebfere bel mmon ewe nob nob. Ejumjum we limem.’ 
\p  
\v 28 “Eji á ma wuk ano, atahng kehm-e rake. Á kehm tene elyele go ekpꞌkpa.\f + \fr 15:28 \ft Luk 15:2\f* 
\p “Owo nde kehm lohngo ba gboong-e. 
\p  
\v 29 “Á kehm faange nde re, ‘Nnya tvv nyi m ma-a loko. Ngare anyehng anyehng n kpo lim ajehng ajehng ji a tong-m no. Jol me, a ka kꞌka mbul re me n ko lim elkak ka ate ebame.  
\v 30 Wo anv, eji mmon ewa noa ma ba, no ma rannge akpohko enya eji á jo noongo abajenasꞌsa, ye wo, a ma wul mmon a nfong no joko jok ka-e.’ 
\p  
\v 31 “Owo nde kehm-e faange re, ‘Mmon ewame, wo li a name ngare anyehng anyehng. Nsol kpee nyi li nyꞌnyame, tob li nyꞌnya fvfo.  
\v 32 Fꞌfuumu re wahr lim elkak, fere bel eyebatahng. Tibre mmonanne noa kpꞌkpo, anv, yebfere jol go elkpin. Á tꞌtan, anv a, m m-e nyehn.’ ” 
\c 16  
\s1 Nkimfahnga nlokeltum 
\p  
\v 1 Jisos kehm kpe bung tong abatꞌtoono ebe re, “Efange nne ajehng jolo gona, ji bele nlokeltum. Ane kehm song tong-e re, nlokeltum noo kpꞌfade akpohko enye. 
\p  
\v 2 “Owo nde noo kehm-e lungu, kehm-e bahbe re, ‘Jen ji wahnge n kpꞌwuku nsol ana nyia bada na? Ko awer ba a nya, nya a kpo nyon nsol enyame nyi n yake kak-a go ebo. Tibre a nehm kpe tiki jol nlokeltum ewame.’ 
\p  
\v 3 “Owo nlokeltum noo kehm bungu go ege eltim re, ‘Anv, m bahke limi renan, eji nsoo yahk-m yehke go egame eltum? Eko n gaam kpi, ji m bahke jo bahm egbe. Ndon kp-m fili re me n jo gboongo na nsol.  
\v 4 Anv, me n kahn ji m bahke limi, eji n lꞌbel ane ba bahk-m koko, n lene tob bo ngare nyi nsoo ma-m yehke go eltum.’ 
\p  
\v 5 “Owo á kehm lungu ane kpee, ba bele nde abong, kehm tongo ngbokambang re, ‘A kpi nsoo mbong rejen?’  
\v 6 Á kehm faange re, ‘Nsang akehng atahl alon.’ Nlokeltum noo kehm-e tongo re, ‘Rod nwer a mbong enya, wo ji elwaare, nyon nsang atahl abal a nsang ewubu.’ 
\p  
\v 7 “Owo á kehm bahbe noko re, ‘Anv, wo, mbong enya li rejen?’ Á kehm-e faange re, ‘Ebam nkohl atahl alon.’ Nlokeltum noo kehm-e tongo re, ‘Rod nwer a mbong enya, wo nyon ebam atahl ani.’ 
\p  
\v 8 “Owo nde kehm tehke nkimfahnga nlokeltum ewe noo, tib go elwake ni á ma wake. Tibre abon ba njini nyia ba kpꞌgaka wake go bo a ntum sehnge abon ba ellennge.\f + \fr 16:8 \ft Ef 5:15-17\f* 
\p  
\v 9 “N kp-n tongo re, Roden afang nya ki li nyanyahne, wahn ko lim etem, eji afang lꞌmal, bo lꞌko-n kak go ntahk nyi li go njinanjini.\f + \fr 16:9 \ft Luk 14:14; Mat 6:20; 19:21\f* 
\v 10 Nne no lꞌbel ekakesehk go mmojum no nse, á tob kpi ekakesehk go egburu ejum. Nne no kil ma lim mmojum no nse go etingitingi, á kpehme ma tob lim egburu ejum go etingitingi. 
\p  
\v 11 “Eji ń ki ma lim nsol nyi njini nyia go ekakesehk, bahke limi renan, bo kehm yake atingitingi afang kak-n go egahne abo?  
\v 12 Eji ń ki bel ekakesehk go nsol nyi ki li nyꞌnyahne, nne awo me, no bahk-n kake ji bahke jolo jꞌjahne?\f + \fr 16:12 \ft Luk 19:16-17\f* 
\p  
\v 13 “Nlokeltum awohng awohng limm, no bahke ma loko nde na ebal. Noko, á bahk-e koko ekv, noko jo kor-e. Tohko jol ano á bahke lake nde noko, fere jo daange noko. Ń nehm ma loko Esowo, fere jo loko akpohko.” 
\s1 Ajoobo alum nya Jisos bungu no 
\r (Mat 11:12-13; 5:31-32; Mak 10:11-12) 
\p  
\v 14 Eji Bab Farisi wuku nsol nyio, bo kehm-e kehme elnyoko, tibre akpohko jo koro bo sehng.\f + \fr 16:14 \ft Mat 23:14\f* 
\p  
\v 15 Owo Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Wahn li ane ba kpo tib elnahne go esamahr ane re, wahn li atingitingi ane. Wo, Esowo kpꞌkahne ntim enyahne. Tibre nsol nyi ane kpo tehk, nyi nyi li nsol eltehb go esamahr Esowo.\f + \fr 16:15 \ft 1 Kor 1:27-29\f* 
\p  
\v 16 “Atahm nya Moses, a alum nya abanyehnamahr nyono no jolo ka ngare nyio nyi mahne mahne tete ba rehng ngare nyi Jon ji nwohngalahb. Bomo ngare nyio, owo bo kehme eltiingi nnoobo etib bi li bade etul bi Esowo. Nne awohng awohng no lꞌlim go nsahm, á bahke ma kuumu.\f + \fr 16:16 \ft Mat 15:21-28; Luk 18:3-8\f* 
\p  
\v 17 “Elbung abola ndi tohkem rꞌriidi re tan. Jol nrꞌrohka ntahm anyehng anyehng nehm tiki range.\f + \fr 16:17 \ft Mak 13:31\f* 
\p  
\v 18 “Nne awohng awohng no lꞌten nkal ewe, fere ko noko, yeblim erehbe. Nne no lꞌbaange nnenkal no nlum ewe m-e yehke elbal, eblim erehbe.” 
\s1 Efange nne, a Lasaros 
\p  
\v 19 “Efange nne ajehng jolo gona, ji jo liibi nsol nyi jo sahb kꞌkim ekun, fere jo lim egburu elkak efung abehng abehng. 
\p  
\v 20 “Nne awohng tob jolo ona, no bo jo lung-e re Lasaros, ji jolo nkpak. Ngubjing enye jolo alok alok. Á jo kono eljehke go mbutahk efange nne jio.  
\v 21 Á jo sebe re á jo kpiimi akahb elang li, nya jo fooro ekpꞌkuru efange nne jio gbo, eji á lꞌwohngo. Ebv jo lohngo ba lahb-e alok.  
\v 22 Toono o nkpak nyio ba kpo. Babenjel kehm ba sol-e, song bum-e, á ji kohlo Ebraham. 
\p “Efange nne jio kehm tob kpo. Bo kpa-e kak.  
\v 23 Eji á woomo go ellulagun, jo nyehn erem, á kehm tabe esamahr ebe, kehm nyehne Ebraham go fee, fere nyehn Lasaros jehk kohl-e.\f + \fr 16:23 \ft Mat 25:42,45-46; Hib 9:27\f* 
\v 24 Owo á kehm rabe re, ‘Nso Ebraham, nong, me n fil-a ndon! Lub tum Lasaros, á song behde ebnyohkobo ebe go alahb, ba behd-m go ebliki, eji ebliki ebame lꞌlub naang-m. Tibre n kpꞌnyehne erem sehng go agun nyaa.’\f + \fr 16:24 \ft Ell 20:10; 21:8\f* 
\p  
\v 25 “Owo Ebraham kehm-e faange re, ‘Mmon ewame, buumu re, ngare nyi a jolo go elkpin, a bele anoobo nsol, Lasaros bele asabsab nsol. Wo anv, bo m-e kak eltim, wo noa, kpi erem nyehn.  
\v 26 Wo gana, elka elka ni wahr a nahne, egburu edamme jia, ji nnene lꞌkꞌma sehng ga egahre, ba rehng go egahne, fvfo ji nnene lꞌkꞌtob ma sehng go egahne, ba rehng ga egahre.’ 
\p  
\v 27 “Owo efange nne jio kehm bungu re, ‘Nsoo, n kp-a gboongo re, wo lub tum Lasaros tv go etahk nsoo,  
\v 28 eji á lꞌsong rehke abonanee. Tibre n kpi abonanee na alon, tohko jol ano, bo bahke tob ba, ba nyehn erem ebnohko edi jia.’ 
\p  
\v 29 “Owo Ebraham kehm faange re, ‘Bo kpi awer nya Moses, a nya abanyehnamahr, nong, bo jo wuk.’\f + \fr 16:29 \ft Jon 5:46\f* 
\p  
\v 30 “Efange nne jio kehm tene re, ‘Eꞌee nso Ebraham, nne lꞌlohng akvne, fere song kpiri bo, bo bahke gboko ndon.’ 
\p  
\v 31 “Ebraham kehm-e tongo re, ‘Bo tohko fere wuk alum nya Moses, a nya anyehnamahr, afi nne nyahme na go elkv, bo nehm taame.’ ”\f + \fr 16:31 \ft Jon 11:44-46; Mat 28:11-14\f* 
\c 17  
\s1 Bade abiafem 
\r (Mat 18:6-7,21-22; Mak 9:42) 
\p  
\v 1 Jisos kehm bungu tong abatꞌtoono ebe re, “Nsol nyi kpo lim nne gbo yel abiafem bahke tiki ba. Eyuu a nne no bahke wahnge re ba!  
\v 2 Ga nob re bo kahn-e eltal go emel, tub-e kak alahb, sehnge re á lim mmonse awohng go ellong abonse baa, á gbo yel abiafem.\f + \fr 17:2 \ft Mak 14:21\f* 
\p  
\v 3 “Jo gberen elnahne! 
\p “Mmonanne lꞌlim abiafem, jo rehk-e. Á lꞌgbo ndon, tahm ka-e.\f + \fr 17:3 \ft Mat 18:15-17\f* 
\v 4 Á lꞌsood-a nkpel esehma efung abehng, fere ba gboong-a nkpel esehma re, ‘Ndon ma-m fili!’ tahm ka-e.” 
\s1 Bade eltaame 
\p  
\v 5 Owo abatiingetib kehm tongo Ntul a Jisos re, “Lim eltaame enahre gbal!”\f + \fr 17:5 \ft Mat 8:10; 15:28\f* 
\p  
\v 6 Ntul a Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Li re ń kpi eltaame ni se ana mmohk asia, kehn ń li ma bung tong etaamenti bia re, ‘Mehl, wo song yiimi go aya!’ kehn bahk-n wuku.\f + \fr 17:6 \ft 1 Jon 5:4\f* 
\s1 Ji li ka nlokeltum re á lim 
\p  
\v 7 “Li re nne awohng ewahne kpi nlokeltum no kpo bahm egbe, tohko jol ano á kpo baabe ebul. Á lꞌkehnge egbe ba, nde kpo tong-e tong rea, ‘Ba elwaare, wo ba ji ekpꞌkuru li nsola?’ 
\p  
\v 8 “Eꞌee! Á bahk-e tongo na re, ‘Song lam nsol ka-m, wo fere toobo ebjing bi a bahk-m loko ngare nyi n kpi nsol li. N lꞌli mal, wo kehm tob li.’ 
\p  
\v 9 “Anv, á bahke kake nlokeltum ewe nnyo go nsol nyi á tong-e re á lima? 
\p  
\v 10 “Wahn fvfo, ń lꞌlim nsol kpee nyi bo tong-n re wahn lim, jo bungen re, ‘Wahr alokeltum baka baka ba. Wahr eblim ji li ka-r re wahr lim.’ ”\f + \fr 17:10 \ft 1 Kor 9:16\f* 
\s1 Ana Jisos limi aneb abili na awubu, bo nob 
\p  
\v 11 Eji Jisos je go Jeusalem, á sehnge go Samaria, a Galili.\f + \fr 17:11 \ft Luk 9:51; 13:22\f* 
\p  
\v 12 Eji á rehnge go ejahbe ajehng, aneb abili na awubu kehm ba wan-e. Bo yiimi go fee,  
\v 13 kehm rabe re, “Jisos nso ejahre, nong, wahr fil-a ndon!” 
\p  
\v 14 Eji Jisos nyehne bo, á kehm tongo bo re, “Songen, wahn song kpiri abalimajom, fere tib bo elnahne.” 
\p Eji bo jo jen asongo, bo kehme elnobo. 
\p  
\v 15 Nne awohng go bo ellong, eji á nyehne re yeblohko nob, á kehm feere abake, jo tehk Esowo wahre wahre,  
\v 16 kehm ba gbo go alata nya Jisos, kehm-e kake saam. Nne noo jolo nne a Samaria.\f + \fr 17:16 \ft Jon 4:9,39-41\f* 
\p  
\v 17 Owo Jisos kehm bungu re, “Anv, ane awubu sang nobo noa? Ane asehmwubu bako bana?  
\v 18 Nnene feerem ba re á ba tehk Esowoa, sehngem njenne nyia nyi nyi feere noa?”\f + \fr 17:18 \ft Kol 3:17; Ell 15:3-4\f* 
\p  
\v 19 Owo á kehm-e tongo re, “Mehl, wo song, eltaame ena eblim, wobnob.” 
\s1 Elbake ni etul bi Esowo 
\r (Mat 24:23-28,37-41) 
\p  
\v 20 Egom Farisi jindiki kehm bahbe Jisos re, “Ngare anyi etul bi Esowo bahke bake!” 
\p Owo Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Etul bi Esowo nehm ba go mbang nyi ane bahke nyehne.\f + \fr 17:20 \ft Jon 18:36\f* 
\v 21 Nne awohng awohng limm, no bahke bungu re, ‘Nyehn, bi gana!’ Jol, ‘Nyehn, bi gona!’ Tibre etul bi Esowo bia, wob-n go atahng.” 
\p  
\v 22 Owo á kehm tongo abatꞌtoono ebe re, “Ngare kpꞌbake nyi ḿ bahke sebe re efung abehng bi Mmon no nne kpir-n, jol wahn nehm kpiri.  
\v 23 Bo bahk-n jo tong re, ‘Nyehnen gona!’ Ane bako bahk-n jo tong re, ‘Nyehnen ga!’ Kana lohng je ona! Jol kana toono bo!  
\v 24 Ana emangedu kpo lim, lennge go elbung, rehng ejang abehng abehng, ano wo fvfo Mmon no nne bahke jolo go ege efung.  
\v 25 Á bahke gboko mbang nyehn erem gbalee. Ane ba li anv bahk-e tene.\f + \fr 17:25 \ft Luk 9:22\f* 
\p  
\v 26 “Ana jolo ngare nyio nyi Noa, ano wo fvfo bahke tob jol afung nyao nya Mmon no nne.  
\v 27 Ngare nyio ane jo li, fere jo wꞌwo. Aneblum jo ko akal, anebkal jo bal alum, tete rehng efung bio bi Noa yele go egbang. Owo nnyel kehm yele, ba wul bo kpee. 
\p  
\v 28 “Bahke jolo ana jolo ngare nyio nyi Lot. Bo jo li, fere jo wꞌwo, jo gunu, fere jo gꞌgungu, jo bahm ebgbe, fere jo si ntahk.  
\v 29 Efung bi Lot lohngo go Sodom, agun, a asalfa kehm kehme elnake go ejahbetul Esowo, ba wul bo kpee.\f + \fr 17:29 \ft 1 Tes 5:3\f* 
\p  
\v 30 “Ano wo bahke tob jol fvfo efung bi bo bahke lennge Mmon no nne tib.  
\v 31 Efung bio, nne no lꞌkuumu go ege ero etahk, á lꞌbadde, á kꞌtohko kpe ji, yel go ege ekpꞌkpa, song rod nsol enye. Ano wo fvfo tob li ka nne no li go ege egbe, á nehm tohko kpe feere go ege etahk. 
\p  
\v 32 “Buumen nkal a Lot!  
\v 33 Nne awohng awohng no lꞌgare re á tahre elkpin ene, á bahke tane na elkpin ene. Nne no lꞌtane elkpin ene, á bahke tahre na elkpin ene. 
\p  
\v 34 “N kp-n tongo re, atv mao ane abal bahke noongo go edilnong ajehng, noko, bo bahk-e rodo tahm a ne, noko sa.  
\v 35 Anebkal abal bahke jo gok nsol, noko, bo bahk-e rodo tahm a ne, noko sa.  
\v 36 Aneblum abal bahke jolo go egbe, noko, bo bahk-e rodo tahm a ne, noko sa.” 
\p  
\v 37 Owo abatꞌtoono ebe kehm-e bahbe re, “Nsoo, gan wo?” 
\p Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Edi ji ekpakv ejum li no, owo ntere kpo song rur.”\f + \fr 17:37 \ft Mat 24:21; Ell 16:14-16; 19:17-21\f* 
\c 18  
\s1 Elgan ni li bada nkalebun, a nlamalam 
\p  
\v 1 Jisos kehm tubu bo elgan, eji á lꞌtib bo ana bo bahke jo kak ero ngare anyehng anyehng, kꞌjo yini ekpu.\f + \fr 18:1 \ft Kol 4:2; 1 Tes 5:17\f* 
\v 2 Á bungu re, “Nlamalam awohng jolo go ejahbe ajehng, no ki jo fahl Esowo. Ane we joom lub. 
\p  
\v 3 “Nkalebun awohng tob jolo ejahbe jio, no gbake jo je go ege, jo song tong-e re, ‘Lam elam ejame nob nob, ji n kpi a nnekv ewame.’\f + \fr 18:3 \ft Mak 7:25-30\f* 
\p  
\v 4 “Á kehm tene. Kpe kang kan a, á kehm fere bung go ege eltim re, ‘Jol eji n kil jo fꞌfahl Esowo, ane kil jo lub-m,  
\v 5 tib eji nkalebun noa kp-m gbiingi sꞌsehng, m bahke lame elam eje nob nob, tohko jol ano á bahk-m gboro tib go elbake ni á kpo ba ngare anyehng anyehng.’ ”\f + \fr 18:5 \ft Luk 11:7-8\f* 
\p  
\v 6 Ntul a Jisos kehm bungu re, “Wuken ana ebi nlamalam noo bungu no.  
\v 7 Anv, Esowo nehm tob lam elam ji nno ka ane ba á yehke no, ba kpo gboong-e atv a njula? Anv, á bahke tohko laange, kehm kake bo eboa?\f + \fr 18:7 \ft Rom 10:13\f* 
\v 8 N kp-n tongo re, á bahke lame elam ji nno elwaare ka bo. Anv, Mmon no nne lꞌba, á bahke nyehne ane ba kpꞌtaame go njini nyiaa?” 
\s1 Elgan ni li bada nne a Farisi, a nkokatak 
\p  
\v 9 Jisos tob tubu elgan nia, tong ane ba jo bum elbo re, bo ba li go etingitingi, fere jo daange ane bako.\f + \fr 18:9 \ft Rom 10:3\f* 
\v 10 Á bungu re, “Ane abal je go etahk Esowo re bo song kak ero. Noko jolo nne a Farisi, noko jol nkokatak. 
\p  
\v 11 “Nne a Farisi kehm yiimi eje eje, jo kak ero re, ‘O Esowo, m ma-a kak saam, tibre n limm ana ane ba kpo v ejv, ba kil jo lim nsol go etingitingi. N limm ana ane ba kpo lim erehbe. M ma-a kak saam, tibre n limm ana nkokatak noo ona.  
\v 12 N kpo bade elname njal nkpel ebal go erahde. N kpo ka eltahme go ejum ajehng ajehng ji n lꞌbel.’\f + \fr 18:12 \ft Mat 23:23\f* 
\p  
\v 13 “Nkokatak yiimi eje go fee. Jol á tabem esamahr ebe, seenge go elbung. Á kohko na esi eje go ndi, kehm bungu re, ‘Esowo, nong, me n fil-a ndon, me nne abiafem wo.’ 
\p  
\v 14 “N kp-n tongo re, Nkokatak noa wo li eno go esamahr Esowo, kehm kehnge go etahk, nne a Farisi sang. Tibre nne awohng awohng no lꞌmehl elne wahre, bo bahk-e rede na. Nne no lꞌrede elne, bo bahk-e mehle na wahre.”\f + \fr 18:14 \ft 1 Jon 1:8-9\f* 
\s1 Ana Jisos fuulu abon ba nse 
\r (Mat 19:13-15; Mak 10:13-16) 
\p  
\v 15 Ane bandiki kehm koko abon ba nse, ba goji Jisos re á kooro bo abo. Eji abatꞌtoono Jisos nyehne ano, bo kehm nyame bo.  
\v 16 Owo Jisos kehm lungu bo tv elne, kehm bungu re, “Nongen, abon ba nse jo ba ga egame. Kana jo sahde bo! Tibre etul bi Esowo li ka nkohn nyia. 
\p  
\v 17 “Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, nne awohng awohng no tohko ko etul bi Esowo ana mmon no nse, á nehm tiki li.”\f + \fr 18:17 \ft Mat 18:3\f* 
\s1 Efange nne 
\r (Mat 19:16-30; Mak 10:17-31) 
\p  
\v 18 Ntubesi awohng kehm bahbe Jisos re, “Nnooba ntꞌtibi, m bahke limi renan, kehm bele elkpin ni li go njinanjini?” 
\p  
\v 19 Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Jen ji wahnge a kehm-m lꞌlung re nnooba nne fono? Nnene limm, no li nnooba nne, sehngem Esowo ntahngtahng bi li nnooba nne.  
\v 20 A kpꞌkahne atahm nya bungu re, ‘Ka jo lim erehbe! Ka jo wul nne! Ka jo v ejv! Ka jo yiimi ntianse efahnge! Jo kak nso, a nne!’ ” 
\p  
\v 21 Owo nne noo kehm faange re, “Atahm nyaa kpee m bomo elbumu ngare nyi n kpeke li ntiil.” 
\p  
\v 22 Eji Jisos wuku ano, á kehm bungu re, “Ebsa ejum ajehng ji a bahke gohro lim. Song gungu nsol kpee nyi a kpi no, wo ko akpohko nyao song ka akpak, owo a bahke bele afang go ejahbetul Esowo, wo fere tahm toon-m.”\f + \fr 18:22 \ft Mat 6:20\f* 
\p  
\v 23 Eji á wuku ano, á kehm kehme elguunu, tibre á fange sehng.\f + \fr 18:23 \ft 1 Tim 6:9-10,17; Jems 2:5\f* 
\p  
\v 24 Jisos nyehne kan re á kpꞌguunu, á kehm bungu re, “Bahke riidi sehng re afang ane kehm lehke etul bi Esowo.  
\v 25 Re efange nne kehm yele ejahbetul Esowo, ekamel bahke sehnge go mbang a nga.” 
\p  
\v 26 Ane ba wuku no kehm bahbe re, “Anv, nne awo me, no bahke kehm bele eltahre?” 
\p  
\v 27 Owo Jisos kehm faange re, “Ji nne kil ma lim, goji Esowo riidem.” 
\p  
\v 28 Pita kehm bungu re, “Nyehn, ana e ma tahm ntahk enyahre sa, kp-a toono.” 
\p  
\v 29 Owo Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Nnene limm, no ma tahm etahk eje sa, jol nkal ewe, jol abonanyehn, jol babnde, a abon ebe tib go esi ji etul bi Esowo,  
\v 30 no lꞌkꞌbel na gbalee budu eying jia ji anv, fere bel elkpin ni li go njinanjini eying ji kpꞌbake.”\f + \fr 18:30 \ft Luk 22:30\f* 
\s1 Ana Jisos gohro bung bade elkv ene 
\r (Mat 20:17-19; Mak 10:32-34) 
\p  
\v 31 Owo Jisos kehm rodo abatꞌtoono ebe, ewubu ane abal, tahm a bo go nkpohko, kehm song tong bo re, “Anv, e yahke tahm go Jeusalem. Go wo ejum ajehng ajehng ji abanyehnamahr Esowo nyono no bada Mmon no nne, bahke lohko lim ano go etingitingi.\f + \fr 18:31 \ft Luk 9:51\f* 
\v 32 Tibre bo bahk-e yake, kak ane ba ki li Jus go ebo. Bo bahk-e nyoko, fere son-e, fere so atel wohng-e.  
\v 33 Bo bahk-e dohko, fere wul-e. Lꞌkang nfung era, á nyahme go elkv.”\f + \fr 18:33 \ft Luk 9:22,44; Jon 2:19-21\f* 
\p  
\v 34 Abatꞌtoono ebe wukem ejum ajehng ajehng ji á bungu no. Lenngem bo, tibre bo bꞌbehr bo alum nyao.\f + \fr 18:34 \ft Mak 9:32\f* 
\s1 Ana Jisos limi nwakamahr, á nyehn 
\r (Mat 20:29-34; Mak 10:46-52) 
\p  
\v 35 Jisos kehm jene song kabbe go Jeriko. Nwakamahr anyehng ji o nkpe a mbang, jo gboongo nsol.  
\v 36 Eji á wuku ellong ane kpꞌsehnge, á kehm bahbe re, “Nenan ana?” 
\p  
\v 37 Bo kehm-e tongo re, “Jisos ji Nasaret wo kpꞌsehnge.” 
\p  
\v 38 Owo á kehm soro rabe re, “Jisos mmon no Devid, nong, me n lub fil-a ndon!” 
\p  
\v 39 Ane ba jolo esꞌsong kehm-e nyame re á rahke ewok. Á kehm kpe tuungu na, rabe wahre wahre re, “Mmon no Devid, nong, me n fil-a ndon!”\f + \fr 18:39 \ft Mat 15:25\f* 
\p  
\v 40 Jisos kehm yiimi, kehm tongo bo re, bo ko-e ba. Eji á ba rehng kabbe Jisos, owo Jisos kehm-e bahbe re,  
\v 41 “Anv, a kpꞌsebe re me n lim jen ka-a?” 
\p Á kehm faange re, “Nsoo, n kpꞌsebe re me n lub nyehn.” 
\p  
\v 42 Owo Jisos kehm-e tongo re, “Fere jo nyehn anv! Eltaame ena ebwahng, wobnob.”\f + \fr 18:42 \ft Luk 17:19\f* 
\p  
\v 43 Tvtv ona á kehm soro nyehn, fere tahm toon-e, jo ka Esowo ellub.\f + \fr 18:43 \ft Mat 8:15\f* 
\p Eji ane bako kpee nyehne ano, bo kehm kehme Esowo tehk. 
\c 19  
\s1 Jisos abola Sakeus 
\p  
\v 1 Jisos kehm rehnge go Jeriko, sehng asongo.  
\v 2 Nne awohng jolo o, no bo jo lung-e re Sakeus. Á jolo ntubesi abakokatak, fere fꞌfang.  
\v 3 Á jo sebe re á nyehn ana Jisos li no. We á joom nyehn, tib ellong ane gbale o sehng, ga fvfo á jolo nkpehrekahba nne.  
\v 4 Owo á kehm beke, gbo bo mbang, song wahr ekuntaake, eji á lꞌnyehn-e. Tibre Jisos jo ba elsehnge go mbang nyio. 
\p  
\v 5 Eji Jisos ba rehng edi jio, á kehm kpuru ero, kehm-e tongo re, “Sakeus, badde elwaare, tibre lela m bahke kange go ega etahk.”  
\v 6 Owo á kehm badde elwaare, ba vvr-e go eyebatahng. 
\p  
\v 7 Bo nyehne kan ano, bo kehm kehme elmemme ane kpee re, “Nne noa ebtahm re á song kang a nne no li na nne abiafem.”\f + \fr 19:7 \ft Luk 15:2\f* 
\p  
\v 8 Sakeus kehm mehle yiimi, kehm bungu tong Ntul a Jisos re, “Nsoo, m bahke yange nsol enyame, yehke ejang ka akpak. Nne awohng awohng no n nehm-e go ejum ajehng ajehng, m bahk-e gale nkpel eni budu.”\f + \fr 19:8 \ft Mat 3:8\f* 
\p  
\v 9 Owo Jisos kehm-e tongo re, “Lela eltahre ebba go etahk jia, tib eji á tob li mmon no Ebraham.\f + \fr 19:9 \ft Luk 13:16\f* 
\v 10 Tibre Mmon no nne ba re á ba seb, fere tahre jio ji ma tan.”\f + \fr 19:10 \ft 1 Tim 1:15\f* 
\s1 Elgan ni li bada ntul no tahme nlaabambang ejahbe 
\r (Mat 25:14-30) 
\p  
\v 11 Eji ane bao wuku nsol nyio, Jisos kehm tubu bo elgan. Tibre ngare nyio yebkabbe go Jeusalem, ane bao jo fere tir re, etul bi Esowo bahke soro ba tvtv.  
\v 12 Owo wahng ka á kehm bungu re, 
\p “Mmon a ntul awohng jolo go, no tahme nlaabambang ejahbe re á song li etul feere.\f + \fr 19:12 \ft Jon 14:3,28\f* 
\v 13 Re á kehm tahme, á lungu alokeltum ebe, ane awubu, ka bo mpon ewubu ewubu, kehm tongo bo re, ‘Roden akpohko nyaa, wahn jen are tete me n feere ba.’\f + \fr 19:13 \ft Mak 16:15; Elt 1:8\f* 
\p  
\v 14 “Ejahbe eje ko-e ekv, owo bo kehm tiingi etib tv-e re, bo nehme seb re á ba jol ntul abo.\f + \fr 19:14 \ft Jon 1:11\f* 
\p  
\v 15 “Eji á ma song li etul feere, á kehm ba lung alokeltum ebe, ba á ka bo akpohko re bo ba, eji á lꞌkahn ana bo ma li nsehng go are ma bo ma jen.\f + \fr 19:15 \ft 2 Kor 5:10\f* 
\p  
\v 16 “Ngbokambang a nlokeltum kehm bake, ba yiimi go ege esamahr, kehm bungu re, ‘Nsoo, mpon ewubu enya nyi a ka-m no eblim mpon atahl alon.’ 
\p  
\v 17 “Owo á kehm-e tongo re, ‘Woblim sehng, nnooba nlokeltum. Tib eji a ma bel ekakesehk go mmonsꞌsohka mmojum, a bahke jo fili ejahbe na ebwubu.’ 
\p  
\v 18 “Etoono nlokeltum noko kehm kpe lohng ba, ba bung re, ‘Nsoo, mpon ewubu enya nyi a ka-m no eblim mpon atahl abal a mpon ewubu.’ 
\p  
\v 19 “Owo á kehm-e tongo re, ‘A bahke jo fili ejahbe na eblon.’ 
\p  
\v 20 “Noko kehm kpe lohng ba, ba bung re, ‘Nsoo, nyehn mpon ewubu enya ga! N kake go egame afiafong, song bum go.  
\v 21 N jo fahl-a fahl. Tibre a li ebibbib nne sehng. A kpo rod nsol nyi ki li wo bumu no. A kpo kpa nsol nyi a ki bahm.’ 
\p  
\v 22 “Á kehm-e tongo re, ‘Wo ebꞌbi nlokeltum noa, m bahke koko alum nnyo enya lam-a. A kꞌkahn re, me ebibbib nne ji. N kpo rod nsol nyi n ki bum, fere kpa nsol nyi n ki bahm.  
\v 23 Jen ji wahnge a ki ka njenare akpohko enyame, kehn eji m ma feere ba, n jol ba ko, fere ko nsehng budu?’ 
\p  
\v 24 “Owo á kehm bungu tong ane ba yiimi ona re, ‘Taaren ye mpon ewubu nyio, wahn faake a nyi ka nne no kpi mpon atahl alon.’\f + \fr 19:24 \ft 2 Kor 6:1\f* 
\p  
\v 25 “Bo kehm-e tongo re, ‘Nsoo, á kpi mpon atahl alono!’  
\v 26 Á kehm faange re, ‘N kp-n tongo re, nne awohng awohng no lꞌbel, bo bahk-e kake na budu. Nne no ki kpi, jol ji á kpi no, bo bahk-e taare. 
\p  
\v 27 “ ‘Anebekv ebame bao ba kil sebe re me m ba jol ntul abo, song koon bo ba, wahn ba wul bo go egame esamahr.’ ” 
\s1 Ana Jisos yele go Jeusalem a egburu ellub 
\r (Mat 21:1-11; Mak 11:1-11; Jon 12:12-19) 
\p  
\v 28 Eji Jisos ma bung ano, á kehm soro asi asongo go Jeusalem. 
\p  
\v 29 Eji á ba rehng kohlo go Betfage, a Betani, ajahbe nya li go nnahb ewong ji bo kpo lung re Oliv, á kehm yehke abatꞌtoono ebe na abal tum.  
\v 30 Re á kehm tumu bo, á tongo bo re, 
\p “Songen go ejahbe ji li go egahna mbuksong. Ń lꞌsong rehng ejahbe jio, eji ń fi no, ḿ bahke nyehne mmon a mbvankang no bo kal-e kꞌkuumu, no bo tohk-e go eti. Fanngen ye, wahn ko-e ba a ne!  
\v 31 Nne awohng awohng no lꞌbahb-n re, ‘Jen ji wahnge ń kp-e fannge?’ faangen ye re, ‘Ntul wo kp-e sebe.’ ” 
\p  
\v 32 Ane ba Jisos tumu bo kehm lohko je, lohko song nyehn ana Jisos tongo bo. 
\p  
\v 33 Eji bo jo fannge mmon a mbvankang noo, owo afono mbvankang nyio kehm bahbe bo re, “Jen ji wahnge ń kpꞌfannge mbvankang nyio?” 
\p  
\v 34 Owo bo kehm faange re, “Ntul wo kp-e sebe.” 
\p  
\v 35 Bo kehm koko mbvankang nyio tahm a nyi goji Jisos, fere yehke nsol nyi bo kake no, yal mbvankang nyio go njahm, fere mehl Jisos jehke. 
\p  
\v 36 Eji mbvankang jo jen a ne asongo, bo kehme abomo ebo yal go mbang.  
\v 37 Eji á jo badde go ewong jio asongo, ngare nyi á ma kabbe go Jeusalem, ellong abatꞌtoono ebe gbalee kehm kehme elgeere, fere jo tehk Esowo wahre wahre tib go agburu akpokosi nya bo ma nyehn. 
\p  
\v 38 Bo jo bungu re, “Elfuulu li a ntul no kpꞌbake go mbing nyi Jehova. Elkoono jol go ejahbetul Esowo, ellub jol go ero!”\f + \fr 19:38 \ft Luk 2:14\f* 
\p  
\v 39 Egom Farisi jindiki ji woomo go ellong ane bao kehm-e tongo re, “Ntꞌtibi, nyam abatꞌtoono eba!” 
\p  
\v 40 Jisos kehm faange re, “N kp-n tongo re, Ane baa lꞌbelle, atal bahke kehme elrabe.”\f + \fr 19:40 \ft Mat 3:9; 1 Pit 2:5\f* 
\s1 Ana Jisos lingi Jeusalem 
\p  
\v 41 Eji bo ba rehng kohlo go Jeusalem, eji á ma nyehn yefono ejahbe, á kehm kehme ellingi re,\f + \fr 19:41 \ft Luk 23:28\f* 
\v 42 “N kpꞌsebe re wahn lub kahn lela ejum ji bahke koko elkoono ba a ni,\f + \fr 19:42 \ft Jon 16:33\f* wo anv, ń nehme ma nyehn.\f + \fr 19:42 \ft Mat 13:15\f* 
\v 43 Tibre afung nyao bahk-n kpiri, nya anebekv ebahne bahke bake, ba senng-n kak, fere kohk-n tv.  
\v 44 Bo bahke rannge ejahbe ejahne kpee, a ane kpee ba lene o. Jol eltal anehng anehng nehm kpe jol ni bahke sake kuumu a ntem egahne ejahbe.\f + \fr 19:44 \ft Luk 21:6\f* Tibre ń kahnem ngare nyi Esowo ba re á ba tahr-n.” 
\s1 Ana Jisos je go etahk Esowo 
\r (Mat 21:12-17; Mak 11:15-19; Jon 2:13-22) 
\p  
\v 45 Jisos kehm yange go etahk Esowo, song kehme ane bao kam, ba ji o, jo gungu nsol,  
\v 46 fere tong bo re, “Bo nyono go nwer Esowo re, Esowo bungu re, ‘Etahk ejame bahke jolo etahk ero akake.’ Wahn ebfere rod bum ana ebehre awajv.”\f + \fr 19:46 \ft 1 Kor 3:16-17\f* 
\p  
\v 47 Jisos jo tibi efung abehng abehng go etahk Esowo. Atubesi abalimajom, atꞌtibi ba atahm, a atubesi ane jo sebe re bo wul-e.  
\v 48 Jol bo tikem kahn mbang ana nyi bo bahke limi.\f + \fr 19:48 \ft Luk 22:53\f* Tibre ane kpee jo wuung-e atung sehng, eji ellum ene anehng anehng lꞌkꞌgbo ndi. 
\c 20  
\s1 Mbahbe nyi li bada nsahm nyi Jisos 
\r (Mat 21:23-27; Mak 11:27-33) 
\p  
\v 1 Efung abehng eji Jisos jo tib ane go etahk Esowo, fere jo tiingi bo nnoobo etib, owo atubesi abalimajom, a atꞌtibi ba atahm, a anebkul nfam kehm lohngo ba,  
\v 2 ba bahb-e re, “Tong-r, nsahm anyi a kpi no, nyi wahnge a kpo lim nsol ana nyia?\f + \fr 20:2 \ft Luk 6:19\f* Nne awo ka-a ka nsahm nyꞌnehm a?” 
\p  
\v 3 Owo á kehm faange bo re, “Me fvfo, m bahk-n tob bahb mbahbe. Tong-m wahn,  
\v 4 anv, ewohngalahb ji Jon lohng go ejahbetul Esowoa, afi lohng goji ane?” 
\p  
\v 5 Bo kehm kehme eltoobo atemtem re, “E lꞌtong re, ‘Lohng go ejahbetul Esowo,’ á bahke bungu re, ‘Jen ji wahnge ń ki taame tv Jon?’  
\v 6 E lꞌfere tong re, ‘Lohng goji ane,’ ane kpee bahk-r atal tuubu.” Tibre bo jo sahb kꞌkahn re, Jon jolo nnyehnamahr Esowo.\f + \fr 20:6 \ft Luk 3:15\f* 
\v 7 Owo wahnge bo kehm faange re, bo nehme kahn edi ji lohng no ba. 
\p  
\v 8 Jisos kehm tob tong bo re, “Ano wo fvfo n lꞌki-n tob tong nsahm nyi n kpi no, nyi wahnge n kpo lim nsol nyia.” 
\s1 Elgan ni li bade abayaame etahngga 
\r (Mat 21:33-46; Mak 12:1-12) 
\p  
\v 9 Jisos kehm tubu elgan nia tong ane re, 
\p “Nne awohng jolo go, no bahme avain go ege etahngga, fere rod yaame ane, kehm tahme eje song rehng go ejahbe jehko, kang go ekidi lꞌlab.  
\v 10 Ngare biingi kan a me, á kehm tumu nlokeltum ewe tv ane ba á yaame bo etahngga eje re bo song bong akab nti nyandiki go etahngga ba ka-e. Abayaame etahngga bao fere dv-e na, kam-e, á feere abo abo. 
\p  
\v 11 “Owo á kehm kpe tum nlokeltum noko. Ye fvfo, bo tob dv-e ano, fere son-e, kam-e, á feere abo abo.  
\v 12 Á kehm kpe bulu, kpe tum noko. Noa ana, bo bom-e elok, fere kam-e yake go.\f + \fr 20:12 \ft Mat 23:34\f* 
\p  
\v 13 “Owo nfono etahngga noo kehm bungu re, ‘Anv, m bahke limi renan abee? M bahke gohro tum akor-m mmon ewame. Fundiki á bahke bo lub.’\f + \fr 20:13 \ft Gal 4:4\f* 
\p  
\v 14 “Eji abayaame etahngga bao nyehn-e no, bo kehm kehme elbungu atemtem re, ‘Ye wo li nlehkelkv, nong, wahr wulen ye, eji etahngga jia lꞌfere jol jꞌjahre.’\f + \fr 20:14 \ft Rom 2:22\f* 
\v 15 Owo bo kehm-e yehke go etahngga jio, song wul-e. 
\p “Anv, jen ji nfono etahngga noo bahke bo lim?  
\v 16 Á bahke bake ba wul abayaame etahngga bao, fere faake etahngga jio ka ane bandiki.”\f + \fr 20:16 \ft Mat 22:7-9\f* 
\p Eji ane bao wuku ano, bo kehm bungu re, “Esowo kꞌtaame!” 
\p  
\v 17 Owo Jisos kehm seenge bo too, kehm bungu re, “Anv, edi nwer Esowo jia lohngo renan, ji bungu re, 
\q1 “ ‘Eltal ni asehketahk tene no, 
\q1 ni ni ma fere jol nnahb ekahme?’\f + \fr 20:17 \ft 1 Pit 2:4,6\f* 
\m  
\v 18 Nne awohng awohng no lꞌgbo go eltal nio, á bahke banne. Eltal nio lꞌfere gbo na, nyede nne, bahk-e wade na wade.” 
\s1 Mbahbe nyi li bade etak atahbe 
\r (Mat 22:15-22; Mak 12:13-17) 
\p  
\v 19 Atꞌtibi ba atahm, a atubesi abalimajom gare re bo bob Jisos ngare nyꞌnehm ona. Tibre bo jo kahne re, á tubu elgan nio bada bo. Fvfo, bo jo fꞌfahl ane.  
\v 20 Owo bo kehm-e kehme elbaabe, fere tum ane ba bo ka bo ngu, bo song kehme awak lim, are bo atingitingi ane ba, eji bo lꞌbob-e go ege alum nnyo, fere yak-e kak ntubesi ejahbe go ebo, eji á lꞌlam-e.\f + \fr 20:20 \ft Luk 11:54\f* 
\v 21 Bo kehm-e bahbe re, “Ntꞌtibi, e kpꞌkahne re, wo kpo bung, fere tib go nseenga nseenge. Wo kpehme rang nnene. A kpo lohko tib mbang nyi Esowo go etingitingi.  
\v 22 Anv, atahm enyahre tꞌtaame ka-r re wahr jo tahb etak ka ntul a Roma, afi taamem?” 
\p  
\v 23 Jisos kꞌkahn awak ebo. Owo á kehm tongo bo re,  
\v 24 bo tib-e nsiring, kehm fere bahb bo re, “Anv, esi jia ji nyehne ji? Mbing nyia nyi nyehne nyi?” 
\p Bo kehm-e faange re, “Nyi ntul a Rom nyi.” 
\p  
\v 25 Á kehm tongo bo re, “Kaan ntul a Rom ji li ka-e, wahn ka Esowo ji li ka Esowo.”\f + \fr 20:25 \ft Rom 13:1-7\f* 
\p  
\v 26 Bo we maam tiki bob go ellum anehng anehng go esamahr ane. Owo bo kehm belle, tib eji nfaange enye jo kpo bo esi. 
\s1 Mbahbe nyi li bade elnyahme go elkv 
\r (Mat 22:23-33; Mak 12:18-27) 
\p  
\v 27 Egom Sadusi jindiki kehm lohngo ba goji Jisos. Bo ba li ane ba kpo bung re, “Elnyahme go elkv limm.”\f + \fr 20:27 \ft Elt 23:8\f* 
\v 28 Bo kehm-e tongo re, “Ntꞌtibi, Moses nyono ntahm ka-r re, ‘Nne lꞌkpo, nkal ewe sa, eji á ki jel mmon awohng awohng, mmonannyehn nkvne bahke koko nnenkal noo, jel abon ka mmonannyehn no ma kpo.’ 
\p  
\v 29 “Jolo abonanyehn na asehma. Ngbokambang kehm koko nkal. Mmon awohng awohng á jelem, á kpo.  
\v 30 Etoono kehm tob ko nnenkal nonehm o, kehm kpoko.  
\v 31 Noko gona kehm kpe ko nnenkal nonehm o. Ano wo jolo a ane asehma bao kpee. Mmon awohng awohng bo jelem, kehm kpoko.  
\v 32 Esꞌkohro, nnenkal noo gohro kpo.  
\v 33 Go efung bi ane lꞌnyahme go elkv, á bahke jolo nkal a nyehne? Tibre bo ane asehma kpee ko-e ana nkal abo.” 
\p  
\v 34 Owo Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Ane ba li eying jia ji anv kpo ko akal, anebkal bal alum.  
\v 35 Ane ba fuumu re bo nyahme go elkv, fere jol go eying ji kpꞌbake nehm kpe jo ko akal, anebkal nehm kpe jo bal alum.  
\v 36 Bo nehm kpe jo kpo, tibre bobjol ana babenjel. Eji bo ma nyahme go elkv, bobfere jol abon ba Esowo.\f + \fr 20:36 \ft 1 Jon 3:1-2\f* 
\v 37 Elnyahme go elkv nia. Jol Moses tib-r tib, eji á nyono bade eti jio ji jo lul. Owo á lungu Jehova re, ‘Esowo bio bi Ebraham, a bi Aisik, a bi Jekob.’  
\v 38 Á limm Esowo bi akvne, á li Esowo bi ane ba li go elkpin. Tibre bo kpꞌkpini ka ye.”\f + \fr 20:38 \ft Luk 9:30; 16:23\f* 
\p  
\v 39 Atꞌtibi ba atahm bandiki kehm faange re, “Ntꞌtibi, a bungu go nseenge.”  
\v 40 Bo kpeem sahb bahb Jisos mbahbe anyehng anyehng. 
\s1 Mbahbe nyi li bada Mesaya 
\r (Mat 22:41-46; Mak 12:35-37) 
\p  
\v 41 Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Anv, jen ji wahnge bo kpo bung re, Mesaya mmon a Devid wo?  
\v 42 Tibre yefono Devid bungu go nwer a Saams re, 
\q1 “ ‘Jehova tongo ntul ewame re, Ji go egame ejang eboblum, 
\q1  
\v 43 tete me n lim anebekv eba etikunakpade eja.’ 
\m  
\v 44 Eji Devid lung-e re, ‘Ntul ewame’, anv, á kehm jolo mmon ewe renan?”\f + \fr 20:44 \ft Ell 5:5; 22:16\f* 
\s1 Ana Jisos rehke ane bade atꞌtibi ba atahm 
\r (Mat 23:1-36; Mak 12:38-40) 
\p  
\v 45 Jisos kehm tongo abatꞌtoono ebe go esamahr ane kpee re,  
\v 46 “Jo gberen atꞌtibi ba atahm, ba kpo kor bo re bo jo kak akpawobo yannge. Kpo kor bo re, ane jo gong, kak bo nnyo go are. Go ekpꞌkpa ero, afi jolo go nkak, kpo kor bo re bo jo ji adi nji nya ajꞌjok ane kpo ji.  
\v 47 Bo kpo taare akalebun ntahk ebo, fere jo kak alaabe aro go nnyo a nnyo. Elam ji bo bahke gbale sehng.”\f + \fr 20:47 \ft Luk 12:48; Jems 3:1\f* 
\c 21  
\s1 Ayare nya nkalebun ka no 
\r (Mak 12:41-44) 
\p  
\v 1 Jisos kehm tabe esamahr ebe, kehm nyehne afang ane kpꞌkake akpohko ayare ebo go elkohl akpohko ni jolo go etahk Esowo.  
\v 2 Á kehm tob nyehn nkpak a nkalebun kpꞌkake ederi ebbal.  
\v 3 Owo á kehm bungu re, “Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Nkpak a nkalebun noa wo ga ka sehnge bo ane kpee.  
\v 4 Egom jehko jo ka gbalee, jo sa bo gbalee go. Ye ji li nkpak kaa kpee ji á bele no, ji kehn á jol ma ko, gunu nsol alehke.”\f + \fr 21:4 \ft 2 Kor 8:1-3\f* 
\s1 Erem, a afemfem 
\r (Mat 24:1-14; Mak 13:1-13) 
\p  
\v 5 Egom ebo jindiki jo bungu bade etahk Esowo, ana bo liibi no go anoobo atal, a nsol nyi bo ko akpohko ayare gunu. Owo Jisos kehm bungu re,  
\v 6 “Bada nsol nyi ń kpꞌnyehne a, ngare kpꞌbake nyi eltal anehng anehng lꞌkꞌkpe sa kuumu a ntem. Bo bahke wake kpee wohng ndi.”\f + \fr 21:6 \ft Luk 19:43-44\f* 
\p  
\v 7 Bo kehm-e bahbe re, “Ntꞌtibi, anv, jia bahke limi ngare anyi? Ellingi ani bahke tibi re, yahke ba ellimi?” 
\p  
\v 8 Owo Jisos kehm faange re, “Jo kunen ekpu, eji bo lꞌki-n nehm. Tibre ane gbalee bahke bake go egama mbing, fere jo bung re, ‘Me wo a!’ fere bung re, ‘Ngare ebkabbe!’ Kana jo toono bo!  
\v 9 Ń lꞌwuk bada nta, fere wuk bade ana ane bahke kehme asi tab, fere jo ten atubesi ebo, kana jo fahl! Nsol nyio bahke tohko gbo mbang lim. Fvfo, lohngem re, esꞌkohro ji ma kabbe o.” 
\p  
\v 10 Jisos kehm kpe tong bo re, “Ejahbe ajehng ajehng bahke noko a njahm ejahbe nyehko. Ajahbe bahke jo nok atemtem.  
\v 11 Adi nyandiki, ndi bahke jo gbehke sehng. Njal bahke jolo, a ayam nya bahke jo sehnge ane. Amenngemennge nsol, a agburu nliingi bahke jo tib go elbung. 
\p  
\v 12 “Re nsol nyia kpee kehm limi, bo bahke jo bob-n, fere jo nohk-n, jo ko-n tahm a nahne go ntahk ero, fere jo kak-n go ngbekobo. Bo bahk-n jo ko tahm a nahne, song yiimi go esamahr atul, a atubesi tib go egama mbing.\f + \fr 21:12 \ft Luk 12:11\f* 
\v 13 Jia ji bahk-n limi, eji ń lꞌyiimi ntianse ka-m. 
\p  
\v 14 “Nong, ntim enyahne jo tahn-n, eji ń lꞌkꞌjo tiiri ana ḿ bahke faange, ngare kehm rehnge.\f + \fr 21:14 \ft Mat 10:19\f* 
\v 15 Tibre m bahk-n kake alum nya ḿ bahke bungu, fere ka-n elkahne, eji anebekv ebahne lꞌkꞌma faange, fere jo ten.  
\v 16 Jol babnso ejahne, a abonane ebahne, a nnahb enyahne, a ate ebahne bahk-n jabbe ka. Egom ejahne jindiki, bo bahke wulu na bo.\f + \fr 21:16 \ft Jon 16:1-3; Ell 2:10,13\f* 
\v 17 Ane kpee bahk-n koko ekv tib go egama mbing.  
\v 18 Jol ellv esi enahne anehng anehng limm, ni bahke tane.  
\v 19 Ń lꞌjo kpuumu, ḿ bahke tahre atohko enyahne.” 
\s1 Ana bo bahke rannge Jeusalem 
\r (Mat 24:15-21; Mak 13:14-19) 
\p  
\v 20 Ń lꞌnyehn nlong nsoja ma ba sennge Jeusalem kak, owo ḿ bahke kahne re, bahke gulu elrannge.  
\v 21 Nong, ane ba li go Judea be song go awong ngare nyio, ane ba li go Jeusalem tahm ejahbe jio song. Ane ba li go bo ebgbe, nong, bo kꞌkpe feere ba go Jeusalem.  
\v 22 Tibre afung nyao nya li afung elbongo, eji nsol kpee nyi bo nyono go nwer Esowo lꞌlohko jol go etingitingi. 
\p  
\v 23 Eyuu a anebkal ba bahke jolo ela, a ane ba bahke jo yab abon ngare nyio. Ndon bahke gbale sehng ejahbe jio. Erakatahng ji Esowo bahke gboko kuumu ane bao.  
\v 24 Bo bahke wulu bo go ekahngkahng. Egom jehko, bo bahke bobo bo, tahm abo, bo song jol aneb agbekobo go ejahbe ajehng ajehng ji li go njini. Ane baka baka bahke jo kadde Jeusalem go akpade akpade tete ngare abo biingi.\f + \fr 21:24 \ft Rom 11:25; Ell 11:2\f* 
\s1 Elbake ni Mmon no nne 
\r (Mat 24:29-31; Mak 13:24-27) 
\p  
\v 25 “Nliingi bahke jo tib go njul, fere jo tib go ebareka, a alonlo.\f + \fr 21:25 \ft Ell 6:12-13\f* Ane ba li go njini, ala bahke jo teele bo, eko fere jo tan bo. Bo nehm jo kahn ji bo bahke limi tib go ewahl ji agburu aya, a ebuku bahke jo wahl.  
\v 26 Ane bahke jo gbo elkv tib elfahle, eji bo kpꞌsiki nsol nyi kpꞌbake go njini kpee.\f + \fr 21:26 \ft Ell 6:15-16\f* Tibre atahm nya kpi elbung bahke range.  
\v 27 Owo bo bahke nyehne Mmon no nne kpꞌbake go ekparesemsem, a nsahm, a egburu ellub.\f + \fr 21:27 \ft Ell 19:11-16\f* 
\p  
\v 28 “Nsol nyio lꞌkehme ellimi, kpiiden asamahr enyahne go ero, wahn tab asi enyahne wahre, tibre eltahre enahne kpꞌkabbe abake.”\f + \fr 21:28 \ft 1 Tes 4:16-17\f* 
\s1 Elgan ni li bade efig 
\r (Mat 24:32-35; Mak 13:28-31) 
\p  
\v 29 Jisos kehm tubu bo elgan re, “Kpuren eti ji bo kpo lung re efig,\f + \fr 21:29 \ft Luk 13:6-9; Mat 21:19\f* a nti nyehko kpee.  
\v 30 Ń lꞌsoro nyꞌnyehn eji ma kehme elnyono, ḿ bahke kahne re, nnale yahke ba.  
\v 31 Mbang nyꞌnehm nyi, ń lꞌtob nyehn nsol nyio kpee kpꞌlimi, ḿ bahke kahne fvfo re, etul bi Esowo ebkabbe.  
\v 32 Etingitingi, n kp-n tongo re, Ane ba bahke jolo go elkpin ngare nyio nehm kpo tete nsol nyio kpee lim.  
\v 33 Elbung abola ndi bahke tane, alum enyame nehm tiki tan.\f + \fr 21:33 \ft Luk 16:17\f* 
\s1 Jo kunen ekpu 
\p  
\v 34 “Jo baaben elnahne, goji nkak alimi, a amahm awoko a atꞌtiiri nya elkpin nia lꞌki-n gbal go egahna ntim, eji efung bio lꞌki-n gbede na.\f + \fr 21:34 \ft Mak 4:19; Mat 6:31-33\f* 
\v 35 Tibre efung bio bahke gbede ane kpee ba li go njini, ana ntahmfuk nyi bo kpo saade konngo nsahre.\f + \fr 21:35 \ft 1 Tes 5:3\f* 
\v 36 Jo baaben ngare kpe kpe, wahn jo kak ero, eji ń lꞌbel eko ji ḿ bahke foro go nsol nyio kpee nyi bahke limi, wahn fere yiimi go esamahr bi Mmon no nne.”\f + \fr 21:36 \ft Mak 13:33\f* 
\p  
\v 37 Efung abehng abehng Jisos jo tibi go etahk Esowo. Atv lꞌbehde, á jo kono eljeke song kang go ewong ji bo kpo lung re Oliv.  
\v 38 Efungfu atv atv ane kpee jo lohngo ba go etahk Esowo re bo ba wuk-e. 
\c 22  
\s1 Ana bo jo lam kak Jisos 
\r (Mat 26:1-5; Mak 14:1-2; Jon 11:45-53) 
\p  
\v 1 Eji elkak ni bo jo li abred nya bo kil jo kak ayist ma kabbe, ni bo kpo lung re Pasova,  
\v 2 owo atubesi abalimajom, a atꞌtibi ba atahm jo seb mbang ana nyi bo bahke wulu Jisos. Fvfo, bo jo fꞌfahl ane. 
\s1 Ana Judas taame re á bahke gungu Jisos 
\r (Mat 26:14-16; Mak 14:10-11) 
\p  
\v 3 Ngare nyio nnehm kehm yele Judas ji bo jo lung-e re Iskariot, ji woomo go ellong abatꞌtoono Jisos, ewubu ane abal.\f + \fr 22:3 \ft Jon 13:2,27\f* 
\v 4 Owo Judas kehm tahme song kpiri atubesi abalimajom, a atubesi ane ba jo baabe etahk Esowo, fere toobo a bo ana á bahke jabbe Jisos ka bo.  
\v 5 Atahng yebe bo sehng, owo bo kehm taame re, bo bahk-e kake akpohko.\f + \fr 22:5 \ft 1 Tim 6:9\f* 
\v 6 Judas kehm taame, kehm kehme mbang seb nyi á bahke jabbe Jisos ka bo, eji ane bako ki li. 
\s1 Ana Jisos toobo ebjing bi elkak nio 
\r (Mat 16:17-25; Mak 14:12-21; Jon 13:21-30) 
\p  
\v 7 Owo efung kehm ba rehng bi elkak ni abred nya ki kpi ayist, bi bo jo wul abon ejoro ba Pasova.  
\v 8 Jisos kehm tongo Pita abola Jon re bo song toobo edi bum bo, ji bo bahke lehke elkak Pasova. Owo á kehm tumu bo tv. 
\p  
\v 9 Re bo kehm tahme, bo tohk-e bahb re, “Gan wo a kpꞌsebe re wahr song toobo bum?” 
\p  
\v 10 Owo á kehm faange bo re, “Wuungen atung! Ń lꞌyel go nla ejahbe, ḿ bahke wane nne no solo etulahb.\f + \fr 22:10 \ft Luk 19:30; Mat 17:27\f* Toonen ye, song go etahk ji á bahke yange,  
\v 11 wahn tong nfontahk re, ‘Ntꞌtibi kp-a bahbe re, Gan wo ekpꞌkpa li no, ji m bahke jehke, li elkak Pasova, a abatꞌtoono ebame?’  
\v 12 Á bahk-n tibi egburu ekpꞌkpa ajehng ji li go ero enyong ji bo ma jehke nti. Owo ḿ bahke toobo nsol kpee bum.” 
\p  
\v 13 Bo kehm lohko tahm, lohko song nyehn ejum ajehng ajehng ana Jisos tongo bo, kehm toobo nsol elkak Pasova bum. 
\s1 Nsol alehke nyi elbuumu Jisos 
\r (Mat 26:26-30; Mak 14:22-26; 1 Kor 11:23-25) 
\p  
\v 14 Eji ngare biingi no, á kehm song ji go ekpꞌkuru, a abatiingetib ebe.  
\v 15 Owo á kehm tongo bo re, “Jo kor-m sehng re me n li elkak Pasova nia a nahne, kehm nyehne erem.  
\v 16 Tibre n kp-n tongo re, N nehm kpe tiki li elkak nia, tete n li etingitingi elkak a nahne go ejahbetul Esowo.”\f + \fr 22:16 \ft Luk 13:29\f* 
\p  
\v 17 Owo á kehm rodo nkob, kak Esowo saam, kehm bungu re, “Koon, wahn wo, wahn ane kpee.  
\v 18 Tibre n kp-n tongo re, Bomo anv asongo n nehm kpe tiki wo alahb avain tete etul bi Esowo ba.” 
\p  
\v 19 Owo á kehm rodo ebred, kak Esowo saam, fere bakke, ka bo, kehm bungu re, “A wo li ngubjing enyame, nyi bo kp-n kake. Jo limen ana, eji ń lꞌjo buum-m.” 
\p  
\v 20 Eji bo ma li nsol mal, go mbang nyꞌnehm nyi á tob ka bo nkob, fere bung re, “Nkob nyia nyi li egbanngalung ji nfenfe tib go alung emame ma kpꞌfabe ka-n. 
\p  
\v 21 “Nyehnen, nne no kp-m gungu, á jehk a name ana go ekpꞌkuru.\f + \fr 22:21 \ft Jon 13:21-30\f* 
\v 22 Tibre Mmon no nne bahke kpoko ana Esowo toobo no. Eyuu a nne no kp-e gungu.”\f + \fr 22:22 \ft Mat 18:7\f* 
\p  
\v 23 Owo bo kehm kehme elbahbe atemtem re, “Nne awo go egahre ellong no bahke limi elkohn ejum ana jia?” 
\s1 Nne awo ga gbal? 
\r (Mat 20:25-28; Mak 10:42-45) 
\p  
\v 24 Owo nfaabe kehm gboko abatꞌtoono Jisos bada nne no bo bahk-e bumu ana nne no ga gbal go bo ellong.\f + \fr 22:24 \ft Luk 9:46-48\f* 
\p  
\v 25 Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Atul ba njini nyia kpꞌkpi nsahm nyi bo kpo fili ane ebo. Atubesi ane, bo kpo lung bo re, ‘Akubi!’  
\v 26 Ano sang bahke jolo go egahne. Ga nob re nne no ga gbal go egahne ellong jol ana mmonse. Ntubesi bahke jolo ana nlokeltum.  
\v 27 Anv, nne awo ga gbal, nne no jehk go ekpꞌkuru, afi nne no kp-e loko wo? No jehk go ekpꞌkuru sang ga gbal? Eji n li a nahne, n li ana nlꞌloko.\f + \fr 22:27 \ft Rom 15:8\f* 
\p  
\v 28 “Wahn ba li ane ba ma jol a name kpee go egame elgaare.\f + \fr 22:28 \ft Jon 11:16\f* 
\v 29 Ana nsoo ma-m ka ejahbe re me n fili, ano wo fvfo m ma-n tob ka,  
\v 30 eji ń lꞌjo li nsol ekpꞌkuru ajehng a name go egame ejahbetul, fere ji go nti etul, jo lam ewubu etꞌtohngo ebbal bi Israel.” 
\s1 Ana Jisos nyehne amahr bade ana Pita bahk-e tene 
\r (Mat 26:31-35; Mak 14:27-31; Jon 13:36-38) 
\p  
\v 31 Ntul a Jisos kehm bungu re, “Saimon, nnehm sebe re á ko nsahm nyi á bahk-n febe ana bo kpo febe arasi.\f + \fr 22:31 \ft 2 Kor 2:11; 1 Pit 5:8; Ell 2:10\f* 
\v 32 Me n kak ero ka-a, eji a lꞌkꞌgbo go egama mbang.\f + \fr 22:32 \ft Jon 17:9,15\f* Ngare nyi a ma fere gbo ndon, jo kak abonane eko!”\f + \fr 22:32 \ft Jon 21:15-17\f* 
\p  
\v 33 Owo Pita kehm-e faange re, “Ntul, me n toobo ebjing re me n je ngbekobo a na, jol afi elkv ni, m bahke kpoko a na.” 
\p  
\v 34 Jisos kehm bungu re, “Pita, n kp-a tongo re, Lela a bahke gbaame nkpel era re, me a nehme kahn, nkok kehm kuku.” 
\s1 Gungu mbomo ema, wo gunu ekahngkahng! 
\p  
\v 35 Jisos kehm bahbe bo re, “Ngare nyi n tum-n no, eji ń ki fili abon abam akpohko, fere fili abam efilibo, a akpaketa, ejum jia ji rin-n noa?” 
\p Bo kehm faange re, “Ejumjum wahr rinem.”\f + \fr 22:35 \ft Luk 9:1-6\f* 
\p  
\v 36 Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Anv, nne no lꞌbel mmombam akpohko, afi á bele ebam efilibo, nong, á fili. Nong, nne no ki kpi ekahngkahng gungu mbomo eme, song gunu.\f + \fr 22:36 \ft Ell 13:10; Ef 6:17\f* 
\v 37 Tibre n kp-n tongo re, Edi nwer Esowo ji bungu re, ‘Bo m-e fange kak go ellong abi ane’, bahke lohko jol go etingitingi. Tibre ji bo nyono bada name bahke lohko jol go etingitingi.” 
\p  
\v 38 Owo abatꞌtoono ebe kehm bungu re, “Ntul, nyehn akahngkahng na abal a!”\f + \fr 22:38 \ft Mak 9:32\f* 
\p Á kehm faange bo re, “Ebgbal.”\f + \fr 22:38 \ft Mak 14:41\f* 
\s1 Ana Jisos kake ero 
\r (Mat 26:36-46; Mak 14:32-42) 
\p  
\v 39 Jisos kehm lohngo tahm go ewong ji bo kpo lung re Oliv, ana á jo kono ellimi.\f + \fr 22:39 \ft Luk 21:37\f* Abatꞌtoono ebe tahm toon-e.  
\v 40 Eji á song rehng edi jio, á kehm tongo bo re, “Jo kaken ero, eji ń lꞌkꞌyel go elgaare.” 
\p  
\v 41 Á kehm jeere song rehng go esꞌsong ekidi labe ana nne bahke roko eltal song rehng. Owo á kehm jamme alahng, kehm kehme ero kak re,  
\v 42 “Nsoo, lꞌkor-a, fak-m nkob erem nyia! Ana koro me sang, ana koro wo wo.” 
\p  
\v 43 Owo enjel kehm soro lohng go ejahbetul Esowo ba kak-e eko.\f + \fr 22:43 \ft Mak 1:13; Hib 1:14\f* 
\v 44 Eji ala jo sahb teel-e teele, á kehm nyennge, jo kak ero. Nwuuru nyi á wuuru no, nyi jo toongo wohngo ndi jolo ana agburu atoongo alung. 
\p  
\v 45 Eji á mehle go edi ji á jo kak ero, á kehm feere goji abatꞌtoono ebe, song kpiri bo, bo kpꞌlale, tib ndon nyi jo fili bo. 
\p  
\v 46 Owo á kehm bahbe bo re, “Jen ji wahnge ń kpꞌlale? Tahmen, wahn kak ero, eji ń lꞌkꞌyel go elgaare.” 
\s1 Ana bo bobo Jisos 
\r (Mat 26:47-56; Mak 14:43-50; Jon 18:3-11) 
\p  
\v 47 Eji á kpi mbungu mbungu, ellong ane kehm soro lohng abake. Nne no bo jo lung-e re Judas ji woomo go ellong abatꞌtoono Jisos, ewubu ane abal, ye wo jo tib bo mbang. Eji bo ma rehng goji Jisos, Judas kehm jeere kohlo Jisos re á sod-e nnyo. 
\p  
\v 48 Owo Jisos kehm-e bahbe re, “Judas, anv, a bahke jabbe Mmon no nne ka go nnyo asoda?” 
\p  
\v 49 Eji abatꞌtoono Jisos nyehne ji yahke lim, owo bo kehm bahbe re, “Ntul, wahr ko akahngkahng enyahre, song nok a boa?”  
\v 50 Nne awohng go bo ellong kehm fohko ekahngkahng ebe, kpale nju nyi ntubesi abalimajom etung eboblum. 
\p  
\v 51 Owo Jisos kehm-e tongo re, “Ka kpe lim ano!” Á kehm rodo etung nne noo, feere a bi lak-e, á nob. 
\p  
\v 52 Jisos kehm bahbe atubesi abalimajom, a atubesi ane ba jo baabe etahk Esowo, a anebkul nfam ba ba re bo ba bob-e re, “Ń lohngo a akahngkahng, a atahmtahm atahmtahm ana ń kpꞌbake a nwajv boba?  
\v 53 N jo jolo a nahne go etahk Esowo efung abehng abehng, me ń lakem abo.\f + \fr 22:53 \ft Luk 21:37; Jon 7:30\f* A wo li ngare enyahne, a nyi atubesi ba ejannge.”\f + \fr 22:53 \ft Jon 8:20; 14:30-31; Ef 6:12; Kol 1:13\f* 
\s1 Ana Pita tene Jisos 
\r (Mat 26:57-58,69-75; Mak 14:53-54,66-72; Jon 18:12-18,25-27) 
\p  
\v 54 Owo bo kehm bobo Jisos tahm a ne go etahk ntubesi abalimajom. Jisos jo jene ekv, Pita jen ekv.  
\v 55 Bo kono agun go nlaaga nyio, ji sennge kak. Pita kehm tob song ji o a bo. 
\p  
\v 56 Eji nlokeltum no jolo nnenkal nyehne Pita jehk go agun, owo á kehm-e seenge too, kehm bungu re, “Nne noa fvfo tob jolo a ne!” 
\p  
\v 57 Owo Pita kehm gbaame re, “Nnenkal, me we n nehme kahn.” 
\p  
\v 58 Eji ma kpe ji mmongare ntiil, nne noko kehm-e tob nyehn, kehm bungu re, “A tob wob go bo ellong.” 
\p Owo Pita kehm tene re, “Eꞌee mbi, me sang.”\f + \fr 22:58 \ft Gal 2:11-12\f* 
\p  
\v 59 Eji ma kpe ji ejum awa anyehng, nne noko kehm kpe bung tꞌtahne re, “Etingitingi, nne noa tob jolo a ne fvfo, tibre ye nne a Galili wo.” 
\p  
\v 60 Owo Pita kehm faange re, “Mbi, n nehme kahn ji a kpꞌbꞌbung.” 
\p Tvtv ona eji á kpi mbungu mbungu, nkok kehm soro kuk. 
\p  
\v 61 Ntul a Jisos kehm soro keebe, seenge Pita.\f + \fr 22:61 \ft 2 Tim 2:13\f* Owo Pita kehm buumu ellum ni Ntul a Jisos bungu no tong-e re, “Re nkok kehm kuku lela, a bahk-m tene nkpel era.”\f + \fr 22:61 \ft Luk 22:34\f* 
\p  
\v 62 Pita kehm soro lohng ona, song kehme ellingi ndon ndon.\f + \fr 22:62 \ft 2 Kor 7:10\f* 
\s1 Ana bo jo nyok Jisos 
\r (Mat 26:67-68; Mak 14:65) 
\p  
\v 63 Ane ba jabbe Jisos kehm-e kehme elnyoko, fere jo dv-e.  
\v 64 Bo tob gba-e mbomo go esamahr, kehm-e bahbe re, “Nyehn amahr me! Anv, nne awo ma-a rum?”  
\v 65 Bo kpe bung alum nyako gbalee, nya bo jo su-e. 
\s1 Ana Jisos yiimi go esamahr elam 
\r (Mat 26:59-66; Mak 14:55-64; Jon 18:19-24) 
\p  
\v 66 Eji efungfu ma se, anebkul Jus, atubesi abalimajom, a atꞌtibi ba atahm kehm ba kono edi ajehng, kehm koko Jisos ba a ne go bo elam, kehm-e tongo re,  
\v 67 “Tong-r, joare wo wo li Mesaya!”\f + \fr 22:67 \ft Jon 10:24-25\f* 
\p Owo Jisos kehm faange bo re, “N lꞌtong-n anv, ń nehm taame.  
\v 68 N lꞌfere bahb-n na, ń nehm faange.\f + \fr 22:68 \ft Mak 11:29-33\f* 
\v 69 Bomo anv asongo, Mmon no nne bahke jehke go eboblum Esowo bi gbale sehng.” 
\p  
\v 70 Bo ane kpee kehm bahbe re, “Anv, wo wo li Mmon no Esowoa?” 
\p Jisos kehm faange bo re, “Me wo, ḿ bungu nseenge.” 
\p  
\v 71 Owo bo kehm bungu re, “Anv, e bahke kpe seb ntiansea? Wahrfono antahng ebwuk go ege a nnyo.” 
\c 23  
\s1 Ana Jisos yiimi go esamahr Pailet, nne a Rom no jo fili Juda 
\r (Mat 27:1-2,11-14; Mak 15:1-5; Jon 18:28-38) 
\p  
\v 1 Ellong ane bao kpee kehm tahme, ko Jisos song rehng a ne goji Pailet.  
\v 2 Owo bo kehm-e kehme ebi ka re, “E sebe kahn re, nne noa kpi ane ebahre rannge, fere jo sahd-r re wahr kꞌkpe tahb etak ka Ntul a Rom,\f + \fr 23:2 \ft Luk 20:22-26\f* fere jo bung re, ye wo li Kraist ji li ntul.”\f + \fr 23:2 \ft Jon 19:15\f* 
\p  
\v 3 Owo Pailet kehm-e bahbe re, “Anv, wo wo li ntul no Jusa?” 
\p Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Me wo, a bungu nseenge.” 
\p  
\v 4 Pailet kehm tongo atubesi abalimajom, a ellong ane bao re, “Ebi ajehng ajehng n nyehnem ji nne noa ma lim.” 
\p  
\v 5 Bo kehm kpe nyennge na, jo bung re, “Á kpo lim ntim ane jo jokko go ege eltibi.\f + \fr 23:5 \ft Jon 11:47-48; Elt 17:6\f* Á bomo go Galili, á ma yannge go Judea kpee, anv, á ma ba a.” 
\s1 Ana Jisos yiimi go esamahr Herod 
\p  
\v 6 Eji Pailet wuku ano, á kehm bahbe, joare Jisos nne a Galili wo.  
\v 7 Á kahne kan a re á lohng go ejahbe ji ntul a Herod kpꞌfili,\f + \fr 23:7 \ft Luk 3:1\f* á kehm-e tumu tv Herod ji jolo go Jeusalem ngare nyio. 
\p  
\v 8 Eji Herod nyehne Jisos, atahng yeb-e sehng. Tibre á bomo elsebe wuku wuku re á nyehn-e, tib eji á wuku bada ne.\f + \fr 23:8 \ft Luk 9:9\f* Á jo tob sebe re á nyehn nkpokosi nyindiki nyi á bahke limi.  
\v 9 Owo Herod kehm bahbe Jisos abahbe tvv, jol Jisos we tikem faange.\f + \fr 23:9 \ft Mat 7:6\f* 
\p  
\v 10 Atubesi abalimajom, a atꞌtibi ba atahm tob jolo ona fvfo. Owo bo jo ka-e ebi gbalee.  
\v 11 Herod, a nsoja enye bum Jisos daange daange daange, fere jo nyok-e, kehm-e kake ekpawobo ji nno a nno, ji jo nyane go amahr, kehm-e tumu tv Pailet.  
\v 12 Efung bio bi, Herod abola Pailet, bo fere jol go etem, tibre wuku wuku bo jolo go ekv. 
\s1 Ana bo lame elam kimi re bo bahke wulu Jisos 
\r (Mat 27:15-26; Mak 15:6-15; Jon 18:39-19:16) 
\p  
\v 13 Pailet kehm lungu atubesi abalimajom, a atubesi ane, a ane bako,  
\v 14 kehm tongo bo re, “Ń ko nne noa ba kak-m go ebo, no ḿ bungu re á kpi ane rannge. Eji m bahb-e abahbe go egahne esamahr, n nyehnem ebi ajehng ajehng ji á limi no, ji wahnge ń kp-e kake ebi.  
\v 15 Ano wo fvfo tob jol goji Herod, tib eji á feere a ne ba ka-m. Nne noa limem ejumjum ji fuumu re bo wul-e.  
\v 16 Owo wahnge m bahke tongo, bo dv-e, n fere yak-e, á song.”\f + \fr 23:16 \ft Elt 3:13\f* 
\p  
\v 17 Elkak Pasova anehng anehng Pailet jo yehke nne a ngbekobo awohng ka bo. 
\p  
\v 18 Ellong ane bao kpee kehm rabe nnyo nnyo amehng re, “Song a nne noo, wo song wul-e, wo yake Barabas ka-r.”\f + \fr 23:18 \ft Elt 3:14\f* 
\p  
\v 19 Barabas, bo kak-e ngbekobo tib eji á jo jokko ejahbe, fere wul nne. 
\p  
\v 20 Pailet jo sebe re á yehke Jisos yake, owo á kehm kpe bung a bo. 
\p  
\v 21 Bo kpe rabe na re, “Kum-e go ekros! Kum-e go ekros!” 
\p  
\v 22 Owo Pailet kehm kpe bahb bo go nkpel era re, “Anv, jen ji wahnge? Ebi aji á limi no? N nyehnem ebi ajehng ajehng ji á limi no, ji fuumu re bo wul-e. M bahke tongo bo dv-e, n fere yehk-e yake.” 
\p  
\v 23 Bo kehm kpe nyꞌnyennge na, jo rabe wahre wahre wahre re bo kum-e go ekros.\f + \fr 23:23 \ft Elt 21:36\f* Esꞌkohro elrabe ni bo jo gohro rabe kehm gake Pailet. 
\p  
\v 24 Owo á kehm kimi elam ana bo jo seb,  
\v 25 fere yehke nne no bo sebe no yake, no bo kak-e ngbekobo tib eji á jo jokko ejahbe, fere wul nne, kehm fere yehke Jisos ka, bo lim-e ana koro bo. 
\s1 Ana bo kumu Jisos go ekros 
\r (Mat 27:32-44; Mak 15:21-32; Jon 19:17-27) 
\p  
\v 26 Eji bo ko Jisos, jo tahm a ne, bo kehm song wane nne awohng no bo jo lung-e re Saimon, ji jolo nne a Sirin. Á lohngo go mmojahbe noko kpꞌtahme go Jeusalem. Bo kehm-e bobo, kun-e ekros re á sol, jo toono Jisos go njahm.  
\v 27 Ellong ane gbalee ba jo toono Jisos, a anebkal ba jo ling-e ndon ndon. 
\p  
\v 28 Owo Jisos kehm keebe, kehm tongo bo re, “Anebkal ba Jeusalem, ka ma wahn kpe ling! Lingen elnahne, wahn ling abon ebahne!  
\v 29 Tibre ngare kpꞌbake nyi bo bahke bungu re, ‘Elfuulu li ka agum anebkal, ba kala jꞌjel, bo ji kala yꞌyabe abon.’\f + \fr 23:29 \ft Luk 21:23\f* 
\v 30 Owo bo bahke kehme elbungu tong awong re, ‘Gboon bul-r!’\f + \fr 23:30 \ft Ell 6:16; 9:6\f* 
\v 31 Esowo lꞌlim eti mbir mbir ano, lꞌlim renan, á lꞌkꞌtob lim ekpakv eti ano?”\f + \fr 23:31 \ft 1 Pit 4:17\f* 
\p  
\v 32 Ane abal bako ba jolo abi ane, bo tob ko bo tahm a bo re bo tob song wul bo a Jisos. 
\p  
\v 33 Eji bo song rehng go edi ji bo jo lung re edi nkpakesi, owo bo kehm kumu Jisos go ekros, a abi ane bao fvfo, noko go ege ejang eboblum, noko go ege ejang ebobkal. 
\p  
\v 34 Jisos kehm bungu re, “Nsoo, tahm ka bo, tibre bo nehme kahn ji bo kpꞌlimi.”\f + \fr 23:34 \ft Elt 3:17; 7:60\f* 
\p Bo kehm tubu elfaange, eji bo lꞌkahn ana bo bahke baange nsol ebjing enye. 
\p  
\v 35 Ane yiimi ona, jo nyehn, eji atubesi Jus jo nyok-e re, “Á kpo tahre ane bako, nong, á tob tahre elne, joare ye wo li Kraist ji Esowo ma yehke.”\f + \fr 23:35 \ft Luk 4:23\f* 
\p  
\v 36 Nsoja tꞌtob nyok-e fvfo, owo bo kehm bake re bo ba ka-e amahm,  
\v 37 fere bung re, “Lꞌjol re wo wo li ntul no Jus, tahre elna!” 
\p  
\v 38 Bo tob nyono nwer lake kohlo go ege esi. Nwer nyio bo nyono go Grik, Latin, a Hibru re, 
\p “\sc A WO LI NTUL NO JUS\sc* .” 
\p  
\v 39 Ebi nne ajehng ji tob kpaake go ekros kohlo Jisos, kehm-e suku re, “Wo sang li Mesayaa? Tahre elna, wo tob tahr-r me!” 
\p  
\v 40 Noko kehm-e nyame re, “Anv, a nehme fahl Esowoa, eji bo ma tob kimi elam re bo wul-aa?  
\v 41 Wahr kpꞌnyehne erem bia go nseenge. Tibre e kpꞌbele eltuuru enahre ni fuumu re wahr bel go nsol nyi e limi no. Wo, nne noa, jol ebi ajehng ajehng á limem.” 
\p  
\v 42 Owo á kehm bungu tong Jisos re, “Buum-m, a lꞌba ji go ega eti etul.” 
\p  
\v 43 Jisos kehm-e faange re, “Etingitingi, n kp-a tongo re, Lela a bahke jolo a name go ejahbetul Esowo.”\f + \fr 23:43 \ft Ef 2:8\f* 
\s1 Ana Jisos kpo no 
\r (Mat 27:45-56; Mak 15:33-41; Jon 19:28-30) 
\p  
\v 44 Jolo ejum nkaranka ewubbal nyi efin, nyi ejannge gbo no ejahbe jio kpee, ji tete rehng nkaranka era nyi elgung.  
\v 45 Njul kpeem ya. Ekpiki ji tokko go etahk Esowo kehm yange ejang ebbal.\f + \fr 23:45 \ft Hib 6:19; 9:3; 10:20\f* 
\p  
\v 46 Owo Jisos kehm rabe wahre wahre wahre re, “Nsoo, me n yake etohko ejame kak go ega ebo.\f + \fr 23:46 \ft Elt 7:59\f*” Eji á ma bung ano mal, á soro kpo. 
\p  
\v 47 Ntubesi a nsoja nyehne kan ji ma lim, á kehm kehme Esowo tehk, fere bung re, “Etingitingi, nne noa lohko jol etingi nne.” 
\p  
\v 48 Ellong ane ba kame ba rur re bo ba nyehn ana bo bahke wulu Jisos, eji bo nyehne ji ma lim, bo kehm feere ebo kehnge ndon ndon.  
\v 49 Ane kpee ba kahne Jisos, a anebkal ba lohngo go Galili toon-e ba rehng o, bo yiimi ebo fee, jo nyehn nsol nyia.\f + \fr 23:49 \ft Luk 8:1-3\f* 
\s1 Ana bo kake Jisos go elahm 
\r (Mat 27:57-61; Mak 15:42-47; Jon 19:38-42) 
\p  
\v 50 Nne awohng jolo go, no bo jo lung-e re Josef ji lohng go ejahbe Jus ji bo jo lung re Arimatia. Á jolo nnooba nne, no jolo go etingitingi, fere jol ntul esub.  
\v 51 Á jo siki etul bi Esowo bi kpꞌbake.\f + \fr 23:51 \ft Luk 2:25-38\f* Owo wahnge á ki taame tv ntoobo ebo nyi bo toobo no, fere lim.\f + \fr 23:51 \ft Mak 3:6; 14:64\f* 
\v 52 Á kehm tahme song bahb Pailet, joare á bahke taame, á song fono ekv ji Jisos tahm a ji.  
\v 53 Owo á kehm song fono ekv ji Jisos, fere kpennge ekpowo, rod song kak go elahm bi á rahme go ekpartal, bi bo kala kꞌkak nne awohng awohng.  
\v 54 Jolo efung bi bo jo toobo ebjing bi Esabat yahke rehng. 
\p  
\v 55 Anebkal ba lohngo go Galili jo toono Jisos kehm tob ba nyehn elahm, fere nyehn ana bo kak-e no.  
\v 56 Owo bo kehm feere, ba toobo anyane, fere toobo akehng bum. Efung Esabat bo kehm jehke, re ekv, ana ntahm bungu no. 
\c 24  
\s1 Ana Jisos nyahme go elkv 
\r (Mat 28:1-10; Mak 16:1-8; Jon 20:1-10) 
\p  
\v 1 Ngbokambang efung go erahde, efungfu atv atv, bo kehm rodo anyane nya bo toobo no, tahm a nya go elahm.  
\v 2 Eji bo rehnge go, bo kehm song nyehn eltal nio ma bannge go nnyo elahm, noongo go nkpe.  
\v 3 Owo bo kehm maade yel, jol ekv ji Ntul a Jisos bo nyehnem. 
\p  
\v 4 Eji bo yim o, ma bil bo amahr, bo kehm soro nyehn ane abal yim kohlo bo, ba kake nsol nyi jo nyane.  
\v 5 Eji anebkal bao jo fahl, fere kohk asamahr go ndi, ane bao na abal kehm soro kehme elbungu a bo re, “Jen ji wahng ń kpꞌsebe nne a mbir mbir go ellong akvne?  
\v 6 Ana á limm. Yebnyahme. Buumen ana á tong-n no ngare nyi á kpeke li go Galili re,  
\v 7 ‘Mmon no nne, bo bahk-e yake, kak abi ane go ebo, bo kum-e go ekros, lꞌkang nfung era, á nyahme go elkv.’ ”\f + \fr 24:7 \ft Mat 17:22-23\f* 
\p  
\v 8 Owo anebkal bao kehm soro buumu alum enye,  
\v 9 kehm lohngo go elahm feere, song tooro nsol nyio tong abatꞌtoono ebe, ewubu a nne awohng, fere tob tong erik ane bako fvfo.  
\v 10 Anebkal ba tongo abatiingetib nsol nyia jolo Meri ji lohng go Magdala, Joanna, Meri nnyehn Jems, a anebkal bako ba tob jol a bo fvfo.\f + \fr 24:10 \ft Luk 8:2-3\f* 
\p  
\v 11 Abatiingetib, alum nya anebkal bao tongo bo jolo bo ana emongo. Bo taamem tv bo. 
\p  
\v 12 Pita kehm tahme, be song rehng go elahm, kehm song reme fahng, nyehn akpowo nya nya nong no. Owo á kehm feere kehnge, fere jo tir bade ji ma lim. 
\s1 Ana abatꞌtoono Jisos na abal jo tahm go Emmaus 
\r (Mak 16:12-13) 
\p  
\v 13 Efung bꞌnehm ona ane abal ba woomo go bo ellong lohngo jo tahm go ejahbe ji bo kpo lung re Emmaus ji jolo ejum mmal esehma, a lꞌtahm go Jeusalem.  
\v 14 Bo jo tubu eka atemtem bada nsol nyia kpee nyi ma lim. 
\p  
\v 15 Eji bo kpi mbungu mbungu atemtem, fere jo tiiri, yefono Jisos kehm lohngo ba kpiri bo, jo jen a bo.  
\v 16 Ngare nyio amahr ebo ka lennge, owo bo ki-e liingi.  
\v 17 Á kehm bahbe bo re, “Jen ji ń kpꞌbungu tong atemtem, eji ń kpꞌjene asongo ndon ndon?” 
\p  
\v 18 Owo nne awohng no bo jo lung-e re Kleopas kehm-e faange re, “Anv, wo ntahngtahng wo ga li njenne nyi li go Jerusalema, nyi kil kahne nsol nyi ma lim a afung nyaa?” 
\p  
\v 19 Á kehm bahbe bo re, “Nsol anyi?” 
\p Owo bo kehm-e faange re, “Nsol nyi ma lim Jisos ji Nasaret,” ji jolo nnyehnamahr no jo bung alum nya kpi nsahm, fere jo lim agburu akpokosi go esamahr Esowo, a esamahr bi ane kpee.\f + \fr 24:19 \ft Mat 21:11\f* 
\v 20 Atubesi abalimajom ebahre, a atubesi ebahre ba yak-e no ka re bo kimi elam ji bo bahk-e wulu. Owo bo kehm-e kumu go ekros.  
\v 21 Wahr jo kunu ekpu re, ye wo bahke fake Israel yake.\f + \fr 24:21 \ft Elt 1:6\f* Gana yebkpo! Lela nfung era nyi a, nyi nsol nyia limi no. 
\p  
\v 22 “Fvfo, ji ma-r kpe kpꞌkpo esi, anebkal bandiki ba wob go egahre ellong fungu efungfu atv atv, je go elahm,\f + \fr 24:22 \ft Luk 24:1-10\f* 
\v 23 ekv eje bo nyehnem. Bo kehm feere ba, ba bung re, bobnyehn nkpokosi ejum, eji bo nyehne enjel nyi tongo bo re, á noa go elkpin.  
\v 24 Egom jindiki ji woomo go egahre ellong kehm jeke go elahm, lohko song nyehn jang jang ana anebkal bao bungu no, sehngem yefono wo bo ki-e nyehn.”\f + \fr 24:24 \ft Jon 20:3-10\f* 
\p  
\v 25 Owo Jisos kehm tongo bo re, “Wahn agboolo ane baa, jen ji wahnge kpo riid-n go eltaame ejum ajehng ajehng ji anyehnamahr nyono no?  
\v 26 Tiki li re, Mesaya gbo mbang nyehn erem bia kpee, kehm yele go ege ellub.” 
\p  
\v 27 Owo Jisos kehm lennge adi nwer Esowo kpee nya bungu bada ne tong bo, bomo go awer nya Moses, a awer nya anyehnamahr kpee.\f + \fr 24:27 \ft Jon 1:45\f* 
\p  
\v 28 Bo kehm kabbe ejahbe ji bo fi no. Jo jolo are Jisos yahke sehng asongo.  
\v 29 Bo kehm-e gboongo re, “Ba kang a nahre, tibre elgung ebba, gana ejannge ebkehme elgboko.” 
\p Owo á kehm song yel ekpꞌkpa re á song kang goji bo.  
\v 30 Eji á ji ekpꞌkuru, jo li nsol a bo, owo á kehm rodo ebred, kak Esowo saam, bakke, ka bo.\f + \fr 24:30 \ft Luk 22:19\f* 
\v 31 Owo amahr ebo kehm soro lennge, bo kehm-e soro liingi. Á kehm soro lamme. 
\p  
\v 32 Owo bo kehm kehme elbungu, jo tong atemtem re, “Ano wo wahnge alum enye jo yall-r, eji á jo bung a nahre go mbang, fere jo lennge nwer Esowo tong-r.” 
\p  
\v 33 Owo bo kehm soro mehl tvtv, feere go Jeusalem, ba nyehn abatꞌtoono Jisos, ewubu a nne awohng ma ba kono edi ajehng, a ane ba tob jol a bo o fvfo,  
\v 34 ba jo bung re, “Ntul a Jisos eblohko nyahme go etingitingi. Saimon m-e nyehn.”\f + \fr 24:34 \ft 1 Kor 15:5\f* 
\p  
\v 35 Owo ane abal bao kehm tob tooro ana ji limi go mbang tong bo, ana bo liing-e no ngare nyi á bakke ebred. 
\s1 Ana Jisos ba kpiri abatꞌtoono ebe 
\r (Mat 28:16-20; Mak 16:14-18; Jon 20:19-23; Elt 1:6-8) 
\p  
\v 36 Eji bo kpi mbungu mbungu, yefono Jisos kehm soro ba lohng go bo elka, kehm bungu tong bo re, “Elkoono jol a nahne!” 
\p  
\v 37 Kehm mennge bo, bo kehm kehme elfahle, fere jo tir re, etohko ji bo kpꞌnyehne a.\f + \fr 24:37 \ft Mat 14:26\f* 
\p  
\v 38 Owo á kehm bahbe bo re, “Jen ji wahnge eko ma-n tan ana? Jen ji wahnge ń kpꞌfaabe go egahna ntim?  
\v 39 Nyehnen abo enyame, wahn nyehn akpade enyame fvfo, eji ń lꞌkahn re mefono antahng wo. Dam-m wahn, wahn nyehn. Tibre etohko, ngubjing kpimm, ana ḿ ma-m nyehn, n kpi no.”\f + \fr 24:39 \ft 1 Jon 1:1\f* 
\p  
\v 40 Á bungu kan ano mal, á kehm tibi bo abo enye, a akpade akpade.  
\v 41 Eji bo kala tiki taame tib go eyebatahng ji bo bele no, a esi ji jo kpo bo, owo Jisos kehm bahbe bo re, “Anv, ń kpꞌkpi ejum ajehng ajehng a, ji ellehka?” 
\p  
\v 42 Bo kehm-e kake ekv nsahre ji bo ma lam.  
\v 43 Owo á kehm taare li go bo esamahr.  
\v 44 Á kehm tongo bo re, “Alum enyame nya ana, nya n jo bung a nahne ngare nyi n kpeke li a nahne re, Ejum ajehng ajehng ji bo nyono bada name go atahm nya Moses, fere nyon go awer nya abanyehnamahr, a nwer a Saams bahke lohko jol go etingitingi.”\f + \fr 24:44 \ft Luk 24:27\f* 
\p  
\v 45 Owo á kehm lennge ntim ebo, eji bo lꞌkahn nwer Esowo,  
\v 46 fere tong bo re, “Ana wo bo nyono re, Mesaya bahke nyehne erem, lꞌkang nfung era, á nyahme go elkv,  
\v 47 bo fere tiingi ane kpee ba li go njini etib bi egbokondon, a bi eltahmeka go abiafem. Go Jeusalem wo, bo bahke bomo etib bio go eltiingi go ege a mbing.  
\v 48 Wahn ba li atianse go nsol nyia.  
\v 49 M bahke tumu ji nsoo nyame no tv-n.\f + \fr 24:49 \ft Jon 15:26; Elt 1:4-5; 2:1-4\f* Jolen ejahbe jia a, tete nsahm nyi bahke lohngo go ero, lohng ba tob-n.” 
\s1 Ana Jisos tahme go ejahbetul Esowo 
\r (Mak 16:19-20; Elt 1:9-11) 
\p  
\v 50 Owo á kehm rodo bo, tahm abo song rehng go Betani. Owo á kehm tabe abo enye wahre, fuulu bo. 
\p  
\v 51 Eji á jo fuulu bo, á kehm soro tahm bo sa. Nsahm nyi Esowo rod-e tahm a ne go ejahbetul Esowo. 
\p  
\v 52 Bo kehm feere go Jeusalem, a egburu eyebatahng.  
\v 53 Bo jo jolo go etahk Esowo ngare anyehng anyehng, jo tehk Esowo, fere jo kak-e saam.